Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.99,英文,,0,0,0,,My father hated lawyers all his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:42.80,英文,,0,0,0,,He wasn't a great guy, my old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:45.23,英文,,0,0,0,,He drank and beat up my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:47.10,英文,,0,0,0,,He beat me up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:49.15,英文,,0,0,0,,So you might think I became a lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:50.89,英文,,0,0,0,,just to piss him off,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:52.92,英文,,0,0,0,,but you'd be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:55.02,英文,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to be a lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:56.73,英文,,0,0,0,,ever since I read about the civil rights lawyers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.43,英文,,0,0,0,,in the fifties and sixties
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:00.83,英文,,0,0,0,,and the amazing uses they found for the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:03.07,英文,,0,0,0,,They did what a lot of people thought
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:04.77,英文,,0,0,0,,was the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:07.34,英文,,0,0,0,,They gave lawyers a good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:10.04,英文,,0,0,0,,And so I went to law school,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:11.91,英文,,0,0,0,,and it did piss my father off,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:13.84,英文,,0,0,0,,but he was pissed off anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:15.91,英文,,0,0,0,,In my first year, he got drunk one day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:16.98,英文,,0,0,0,,and fell of a ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:19.32,英文,,0,0,0,,manufactured by the company he worked for,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:21.85,英文,,0,0,0,,and he didn't know who to sue first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:24.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, he died a couple months after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:27.15,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:28.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, some of my classmates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.53,0:01:30.13,英文,,0,0,0,,they knew they were going straight from school
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:31.55,英文,,0,0,0,,into the top law firms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:34.26,英文,,0,0,0,,thanks mostly to their family connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:36.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, the only connections I had
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:38.82,英文,,0,0,0,,were made in the places where I tended bar for 3 years
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:40.05,英文,,0,0,0,,so I could pay my tuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:42.17,英文,,0,0,0,,And while I still had plans
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:45.15,英文,,0,0,0,,to shine the blazing light of justice into every dark corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:48.44,英文,,0,0,0,,what I really needed right now was a job,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:50.97,英文,,0,0,0,,because there are too many lawyers in Memphis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:57.69,英文,,0,0,0,,This city's infested with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.61,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:06.61,英文,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anything more embarrassing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.88,英文,,0,0,0,,than telling people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.95,0:02:11.28,英文,,0,0,0,,I work for a guy like Bruiser Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:16.99,英文,,0,0,0,,I mean, he's a lawyer, and they call him Bruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:19.66,英文,,0,0,0,,That's how desperate I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:20.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:22.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Shut the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:25.63,英文,,0,0,0,,No, not that. Not that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:28.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:29.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:32.27,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's make it my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.77,英文,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:38.54,英文,,0,0,0,,I really pity the poor FBI technician
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:40.35,英文,,0,0,0,,that's gonna have to extract the data
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:41.81,英文,,0,0,0,,from that conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:44.12,英文,,0,0,0,,Live sharks in a lawyer's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.12,英文,,0,0,0,,It's a joke. Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.82,英文,,0,0,0,,So, Prince,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:49.72,英文,,0,0,0,,is this the law student you were telling me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.96,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. I just finished
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.79,英文,,0,0,0,,my third year at Memphis state.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you use him around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:56.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Look, I'll vouch for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.83,英文,,0,0,0,,The boy needs a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:01.53,英文,,0,0,0,,He's tended bar at our clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:04.70,英文,,0,0,0,,This'll be a great place for you to work, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:06.44,英文,,0,0,0,,This'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:08.34,英文,,0,0,0,,A great place for you to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:10.17,英文,,0,0,0,,You can see what real lawyers do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:13.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, it ain't exactly a salaried position.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.31,英文,,0,0,0,,It isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.75,英文,,0,0,0,,I expect my associates to pay for themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:21.60,英文,,0,0,0,,generate their own fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.72,英文,,0,0,0,,Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:26.06,英文,,0,0,0,,How exactly does that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.16,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, Rudy, you draw $1,000 a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:32.20,英文,,0,0,0,,and you get to keep 1/3 of all the fees that you generate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, if you can't cover your draw
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:37.54,英文,,0,0,0,,at the end of each month, you owe me the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.32,英文,,0,0,0,,Sounds fair to me, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:43.11,英文,,0,0,0,,That's a hell of a deal, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.24,英文,,0,0,0,,You can make a lot of money this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:47.95,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you something, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.75,英文,,0,0,0,,That's the only way I operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.45,英文,,0,0,0,,And I'll get you a lot of good cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.60,英文,,0,0,0,,I have cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:55.72,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.39,英文,,0,0,0,,I have 2 cases right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.09,英文,,0,0,0,,One is a will
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.49,英文,,0,0,0,,that I'm drafting for an old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.16,英文,,0,0,0,,She's loaded, too. She's worth millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.55,英文,,0,0,0,,And then I have this other case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.75,英文,,0,0,0,,It's an insurance case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.70,英文,,0,0,0,,Great Benefit. You heard of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.90,英文,,0,0,0,,You got these clients signed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:14.11,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way to see 'em right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:15.84,英文,,0,0,0,,and they'll listen to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:17.51,英文,,0,0,0,,I helped 'em over at a law workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.21,英文,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm gonna have you talk
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.11,英文,,0,0,0,,to an associate of mine, Deck Schifflet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:24.75,英文,,0,0,0,,He used to work with these big insurance companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.55,英文,,0,0,0,,He handles all the high-powered stuff around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, Deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.79,英文,,0,0,0,,You got the paperwork on this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:34.76,英文,,0,0,0,,In my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.86,英文,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.77,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, good lookin'
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.47,英文,,0,0,0,,this is Deck Schifflet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:46.57,英文,,0,0,0,,This man will get you plugged in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.64,英文,,0,0,0,,What I want you to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:51.39,英文,,0,0,0,,I want you to draw up a lawsuit against this Great Benefit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:54.20,英文,,0,0,0,,and you put my name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.97,英文,,0,0,0,,We're gonna file it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:59.50,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy, you're gonna learn a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:02.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy, I'm glad you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.11,英文,,0,0,0,,You're making good choices already, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.34,英文,,0,0,0,,All right, well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.91,英文,,0,0,0,,OK, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Close the door on your way out now, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:10.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Law offices. May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.26,英文,,0,0,0,,This is an office, there's people in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.11,英文,,0,0,0,,If there's somebody in the office,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.32,英文,,0,0,0,,you can't have it, it's off limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.78,英文,,0,0,0,,This is the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:16.79,英文,,0,0,0,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:17.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.16,英文,,0,0,0,,So, are you an associate here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.76,英文,,0,0,0,,Sort of. Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.23,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm actually not a lawyer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:25.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Bruiser usually asks me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.40,英文,,0,0,0,,to review the insurance cases when they come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:29.83,英文,,0,0,0,,I used to work for specific mutual insurance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.53,英文,,0,0,0,,I got sick of that. I went to law school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:33.94,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, when did you finish law school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.20,英文,,0,0,0,,5 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.47,英文,,0,0,0,,See, I'm having a little trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.71,英文,,0,0,0,,with the bar exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.81,英文,,0,0,0,,I sat for it 6 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:40.81,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:41.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah. When do you take yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:42.84,英文,,0,0,0,,I take it in, like, 3 weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:43.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:44.88,英文,,0,0,0,,It's that hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.28,英文,,0,0,0,,Pretty rough, I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.55,英文,,0,0,0,,I took it a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.12,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm gonna take it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:51.05,英文,,0,0,0,,Anyway, this is Bruiser's law library.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.29,英文,,0,0,0,,If you want to get anything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:54.29,英文,,0,0,0,,out of the fridge or use the fridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.23,英文,,0,0,0,,you can put your name on stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.93,英文,,0,0,0,,They'll eat it anyway. Put that in for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Aw, it's only rice. What the hell. Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:01.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.47,英文,,0,0,0,,We made a mess here. Get that up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure, Deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:04.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.68,英文,,0,0,0,,So wait, what happens when you have to go to court?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.14,英文,,0,0,0,,I've actually gone a few times myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.17,英文,,0,0,0,,I haven't gotten caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.34,英文,,0,0,0,,There's so many lawyers here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:14.81,英文,,0,0,0,,it's impossible to keep up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:18.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Bruiser owns all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:20.05,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh. Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:22.38,英文,,0,0,0,,You can't call it a firm exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.45,英文,,0,0,0,,It's every man for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:25.92,英文,,0,0,0,,You'll learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.26,英文,,0,0,0,,What, are you moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:31.93,英文,,0,0,0,,Evicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Here's the policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.50,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:39.57,英文,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:42.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, this is the scratch-and-sniff armpit of the industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.97,英文,,0,0,0,,What are their grounds for denial?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:46.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:48.98,英文,,0,0,0,,They first denied it just on principle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:52.05,英文,,0,0,0,,and then they said that leukemia
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.18,英文,,0,0,0,,was a pre-existing condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:54.18,英文,,0,0,0,,and then they said
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:56.02,英文,,0,0,0,,leukemia wasn't covered in the policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.39,英文,,0,0,0,,I got 7 letters here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Have all the premiums been paid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.52,英文,,0,0,0,,According to Miss Black,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:01.99,英文,,0,0,0,,she paid every single one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.59,英文,,0,0,0,,The bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:07.43,英文,,0,0,0,,This is a typical debit insurance scam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.90,英文,,0,0,0,,The Blacks call it street-surance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.02,英文,,0,0,0,,So what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.77,英文,,0,0,0,,You sign 'em up. Sign 'em all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:18.37,英文,,0,0,0,,To J. Lyman Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.01,英文,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.09,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll help you on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:24.40,英文,,0,0,0,,All right. Well, thank you. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.10,英文,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more thrilling
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.95,英文,,0,0,0,,than nailing an insurance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.32,英文,,0,0,0,,Hi, Ms. Black. It's Rudy Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:52.17,英文,,0,0,0,,Remember? I'm handling your case
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:53.09,英文,,0,0,0,,against Great Benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.82,英文,,0,0,0,,I met you over at the Memphis state law workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:01.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Come in. I'm sorry about them crazy dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:02.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.07,英文,,0,0,0,,I thought you was a Jehovah's witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:06.07,英文,,0,0,0,,Where's Buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:07.81,英文,,0,0,0,,He's out in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Where's he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:12.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Buddy isn't going nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.08,英文,,0,0,0,,He ain't right in the head. War injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:17.05,英文,,0,0,0,,Korea. You know them metal detectors at the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.29,英文,,0,0,0,,He can walk through one buck naked,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.59,英文,,0,0,0,,and the thing would go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.68,英文,,0,0,0,,He's got a plate in his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:28.16,英文,,0,0,0,,That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:32.01,英文,,0,0,0,,How's Donny Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, good days and bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:34.98,英文,,0,0,0,,"Plate in head."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.79,英文,,0,0,0,,You want to meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.27,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:39.94,英文,,0,0,0,,Um, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:47.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Great Benefit first denied your claim last August
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:50.02,英文,,0,0,0,,when Donny Ray was diagnosed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:52.99,英文,,0,0,0,,Why'd y'all wait till now to consult a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:55.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Stupid, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.66,英文,,0,0,0,,I just kept writing 'em,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.62,英文,,0,0,0,,and they kept writing me back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:01.19,英文,,0,0,0,,and this here is the latest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:04.96,英文,,0,0,0,,Dear Mrs. Black,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.27,英文,,0,0,0,,on 7 prior occasions
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.30,英文,,0,0,0,,this company had denied your claim in writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:11.20,英文,,0,0,0,,We now deny it for the eighth and final time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:14.97,英文,,0,0,0,,You must be stupid, stupid, stupid."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:23.05,英文,,0,0,0,,Sincerely, Everett Lufkin, Vice President of Claims."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.65,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.37,英文,,0,0,0,,You're the lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.76,英文,,0,0,0,,Mom says nice things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:39.02,英文,,0,0,0,,She says you're suing those bastards over at Great Benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:42.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Gonna make 'em pay, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.14,英文,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.07,英文,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:46.77,英文,,0,0,0,,Hi, mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.01,英文,,0,0,0,,Hi, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:51.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, before we can file a claim,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.33,英文,,0,0,0,,I need all 3 of you to sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Is daddy coming in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:58.03,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, he said he wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Some days he comes in,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:00.77,英文,,0,0,0,,and some days he don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:02.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, this is a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:03.84,英文,,0,0,0,,What's in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.24,英文,,0,0,0,,It's standard language.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.41,英文,,0,0,0,,It basically says
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.05,英文,,0,0,0,,that y'all hire us to be your attorneys,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.92,英文,,0,0,0,,and we take care of the case for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.55,英文,,0,0,0,,We handle any expenses that we might have,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:18.40,英文,,0,0,0,,and then we get 1/3 of any recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.17,英文,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:23.39,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, why does it take 2 pages to say all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:25.03,英文,,0,0,0,,Don't light that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.73,英文,,0,0,0,,No wonder I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.87,英文,,0,0,0,,And all 3 of us have to sign it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am, all 3. Just where your name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.07,英文,,0,0,0,,He said he wasn't coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Take the pen and go out there
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.38,英文,,0,0,0,,and make him sign the damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.28,英文,,0,0,0,,I guess I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:50.75,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, Buddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.37,英文,,0,0,0,,you gotta sign this paper
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:55.07,英文,,0,0,0,,so Donny Ray can get that operation he needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.48,英文,,0,0,0,,and I don't want no trouble out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:59.41,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll take that damn bottle
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.41,英文,,0,0,0,,and throw it across union street.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:04.52,英文,,0,0,0,,Now sign the damn thing. Come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:09.32,英文,,0,0,0,,I know you must think they're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.89,英文,,0,0,0,,They're nice folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:23.89,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, your nose is bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.14,英文,,0,0,0,,Hold your head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.29,英文,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:33.03,英文,,0,0,0,,It's OK. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.33,英文,,0,0,0,,He's bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.30,英文,,0,0,0,,Put your head back. Put your head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:37.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Come on, put it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:40.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, sweetie, OK, it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.27,英文,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:44.61,英文,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.48,英文,,0,0,0,,OK, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.08,英文,,0,0,0,,OK, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.48,英文,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:52.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Where's the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.52,英文,,0,0,0,,Donny Ray, why don't you just rest a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:55.58,英文,,0,0,0,,You can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:56.55,英文,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:58.22,英文,,0,0,0,,No, no. I want to do this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.49,英文,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:03.26,英文,,0,0,0,,All right, all right, you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:04.59,英文,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.66,英文,,0,0,0,,You're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:20.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, Miss Birdie, it's Rudy Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.08,英文,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:24.58,英文,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:27.88,英文,,0,0,0,,It's Rudy Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:28.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.51,英文,,0,0,0,,We met at the law workshop at Memphis state.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.39,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Oh, come in, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:36.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.13,英文,,0,0,0,,How are you doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:42.17,英文,,0,0,0,,Miss Birdie, I wanted to talk to you about your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.32,英文,,0,0,0,,Cut my children out of my will. Cut, cut, cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.72,英文,,0,0,0,,Cut, cut, cut. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.02,英文,,0,0,0,,I had trouble sleeping last night
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.02,英文,,0,0,0,,'cause I was worried about your estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:51.92,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, if you're not careful, Miss Birdie,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:54.59,英文,,0,0,0,,the government is just gonna get a big chunk of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:57.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, a lot of these taxes can be avoided
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.97,英文,,0,0,0,,with a little bit of careful estate planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:02.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, that legal gobbledygook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.17,英文,,0,0,0,,I suppose you want your name
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.74,英文,,0,0,0,,in the will somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:07.01,英文,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:10.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Lawyers are always wanting their names in my wills.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.98,英文,,0,0,0,,No, ma'am. Well, there are all kinds of lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.68,英文,,0,0,0,,What I do need from you is, for purposes of estate planning,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.82,英文,,0,0,0,,I do need to know where the money is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:21.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Is it in bonds or stocks or cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:25.09,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, Rudy, not so fast, not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:31.13,英文,,0,0,0,,OK, ma'am. So we have this money somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.30,英文,,0,0,0,,Who are we gonna leave it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.23,英文,,0,0,0,,I want it all to go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.74,英文,,0,0,0,,to the reverend Kenneth Chandler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:38.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.97,英文,,0,0,0,,He's on television all the time now out of Dallas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:44.58,英文,,0,0,0,,Got this curly gray hair premature,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:45.71,英文,,0,0,0,,and he wouldn't dream
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.08,英文,,0,0,0,,of touching it up, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:50.02,英文,,0,0,0,,I want him to have the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:53.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Miss Birdie. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:54.75,英文,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:57.49,英文,,0,0,0,,I just have a real problem
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:00.76,英文,,0,0,0,,drafting a will or any instrument
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:04.03,英文,,0,0,0,,that's gonna cut out family
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.00,英文,,0,0,0,,and that's gonna replace it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.93,英文,,0,0,0,,and convey the bulk of this estate
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.94,英文,,0,0,0,,to a TV personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, he's a man of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:17.64,英文,,0,0,0,,I realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:18.88,英文,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:22.75,英文,,0,0,0,,Is there any way we could attack this in more of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:24.52,英文,,0,0,0,,do you have to give him everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:28.12,英文,,0,0,0,,Could it be more, say, 25%
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.46,英文,,0,0,0,,he's got a lot of overhead,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.49,英文,,0,0,0,,and his jet is getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:33.99,英文,,0,0,0,,His jet is getting old?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, Rudy, I want you to just please
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.06,英文,,0,0,0,,draw it up the way I ask
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:40.00,英文,,0,0,0,,and bring it back to me so I can review it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:44.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Here's the hustlers when they were still young and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Cut, cut, cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.88,英文,,0,0,0,,You come back now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:54.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, I will, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.65,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:58.18,英文,,0,0,0,,No. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Is that a little apartment back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:03.79,英文,,0,0,0,,Used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.64,英文,,0,0,0,,What do you think about my garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:07.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a fine-looking garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:09.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you do all the work on this yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:13.03,英文,,0,0,0,,I pay a young boy to cut the grass for me once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:15.10,英文,,0,0,0,,$30. Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:17.47,英文,,0,0,0,,Used to be 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't suppose you'd be interested
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:20.77,英文,,0,0,0,,in renting this place out now, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.61,英文,,0,0,0,,I couldn't afford much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:25.54,英文,,0,0,0,,I could let you have it quite reasonably
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:28.40,英文,,0,0,0,,if you'd assist me with a few chores around the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:32.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Perhaps a little weed pulling now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure. Weed pulling's my specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:39.34,英文,,0,0,0,,Go to hospitals all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:42.01,英文,,0,0,0,,Bruiser has contacts down at the main precinct,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.18,英文,,0,0,0,,guys he grew up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.41,英文,,0,0,0,,They feed him accident reports every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:46.88,英文,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:47.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:51.39,英文,,0,0,0,,What does Bruiser expect me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:53.19,英文,,0,0,0,,Get the case. You find the victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:56.09,英文,,0,0,0,,You sign 'em up to the law firm of J. Lyman Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Put the case together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.49,英文,,0,0,0,,So I should solicit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.53,英文,,0,0,0,,What did they teach you in law school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, they didn't teach me how to chase ambulances.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:06.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, you better learn quick, or you're gonna starve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:13.28,英文,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is ask for a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:15.71,英文,,0,0,0,,and we can admit you right here. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:16.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Nice flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:19.45,英文,,0,0,0,,William.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.45,英文,,0,0,0,,How you doing, Deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.62,英文,,0,0,0,,All right. 346.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:25.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Dr. Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:26.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.09,英文,,0,0,0,,How are you? Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Don't act like a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Hmm. "Do not enter."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.57,英文,,0,0,0,,How you doing, Mr. McKenzie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.73,英文,,0,0,0,,How are my tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:54.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Gall bladder. Wrong fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:56.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Van Landel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:17:00.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Mr. Van Landel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:04.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Mr. Van Landel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:05.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.21,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm Deck Schifflet, para-lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:11.73,英文,,0,0,0,,You haven't talked to any insurance companies, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:12.75,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:14.19,英文,,0,0,0,,Good. don't talk to 'em
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:15.30,英文,,0,0,0,,because they're just out to screw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:16.34,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you have a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:17.59,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:20.06,英文,,0,0,0,,My firm handles more car wrecks
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:21.43,英文,,0,0,0,,than anybody in Memphis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:24.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Insurance companies are terrified of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.23,英文,,0,0,0,,and we don't charge a dime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Can you wait till my wife gets back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.23,英文,,0,0,0,,Your wife, Mr. van...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.27,英文,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.41,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry, Mr. Van Landel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:37.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:40.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Where is your wife, Mr. Van Landel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.61,英文,,0,0,0,,She'll be back in a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.88,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm gonna have to talk to her down in my office
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:47.22,英文,,0,0,0,,because there's a ton of information that I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.49,英文,,0,0,0,,Just sign right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:50.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Remember, don't talk to anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.42,英文,,0,0,0,,except your doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.95,英文,,0,0,0,,There are gonna be people coming at you from every direction
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.56,英文,,0,0,0,,offering you settlements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:58.06,英文,,0,0,0,,I do not want you under any circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.23,英文,,0,0,0,,to sign anything without me reviewing it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Understand? My number is on this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:04.00,英文,,0,0,0,,You can call me 24 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:06.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rudy Baylor's number is on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.44,英文,,0,0,0,,You can call that number for him any time, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you have any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:11.58,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:14.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Good. We're gonna get you a bunch of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:16.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.92,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm real sorry about your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:22.55,英文,,0,0,0,,I'd like to be alone please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.83,英文,,0,0,0,,And that is how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.23,英文,,0,0,0,,What if the guy had a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.33,英文,,0,0,0,,We came with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:34.80,英文,,0,0,0,,If he'd have thrown us out of his room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:37.10,英文,,0,0,0,,for whatever reason, what have we lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.60,英文,,0,0,0,,A little dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:41.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe a little self-respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:43.74,英文,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.46,英文,,0,0,0,,In law school, Rudy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.64,英文,,0,0,0,,they don't teach you what you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.88,英文,,0,0,0,,It's all theories and lofty notions
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:51.15,英文,,0,0,0,,and big fat ethics books.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:52.55,英文,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with ethics?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Nothing, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.73,英文,,0,0,0,,I mean, I believe a lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.77,0:18:59.09,英文,,0,0,0,,should fight for his client,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:00.23,英文,,0,0,0,,refrain from stealing money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:01.39,英文,,0,0,0,,And try not to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:03.00,英文,,0,0,0,,You know, the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:04.93,英文,,0,0,0,,That was blatant ambulance chasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Right, but who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.40,英文,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of lawyers out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.24,英文,,0,0,0,,It's a marketplace. It's a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:13.71,英文,,0,0,0,,What they don't teach you in law school can get you hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:17.51,英文,,0,0,0,,How do you know when a lawyer is lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:19.78,英文,,0,0,0,,His lips are moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:24.65,英文,,0,0,0,,What's the difference between a hooker and a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:28.45,英文,,0,0,0,,A hooker will stop screwing you after you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:32.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Everybody loves lawyer jokes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.24,英文,,0,0,0,,especially lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.37,英文,,0,0,0,,They're even sort of proud of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:38.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Why do you suppose that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:41.00,英文,,0,0,0,,A third party is no defend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.57,英文,,0,0,0,,He may also be used by the plaintiff
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:44.74,英文,,0,0,0,,to bring in a third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.71,英文,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:50.63,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.06,英文,,0,0,0,,I thought we was gonna study on our own time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.82,英文,,0,0,0,,I know, Bruiser, but look, man,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.77,英文,,0,0,0,,the bar exam is next week, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:19:59.33,英文,,0,0,0,,It is next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:00.57,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm scared, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:03.28,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rudy, look, you want to study,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.20,英文,,0,0,0,,why don't you run over to the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:06.26,英文,,0,0,0,,and study with Deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.55,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna study with...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.98,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna study with Deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:13.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got a police report here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:17.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Do we represent her, this victim here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:18.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:21.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Why don't you run down to the hospital and check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:23.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe you could sign her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:03.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Would you get me a soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.63,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:15.79,英文,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.67,英文,,0,0,0,,Where did this all come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:23.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna tell them where
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:25.84,英文,,0,0,0,,all this stuff came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:26.94,英文,,0,0,0,,I know what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:28.87,英文,,0,0,0,,the second I lay eyes on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:30.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Like I'm 10 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:32.29,英文,,0,0,0,,my father crying in the bedroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.36,0:21:33.69,英文,,0,0,0,,my mother sitting at the kitchen table
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:35.03,英文,,0,0,0,,with blood all over her face
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.80,英文,,0,0,0,,telling me that daddy's sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.82,英文,,0,0,0,,and he's never gonna do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:40.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:42.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Just tell me yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:45.86,英文,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:47.78,英文,,0,0,0,,It's always the same with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.31,英文,,0,0,0,,You make me so crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:57.64,英文,,0,0,0,,Kelly Riker was admitted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:59.97,英文,,0,0,0,,to St. Peter's hospital 3 days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:01.81,英文,,0,0,0,,at midnight, I might add,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:04.38,英文,,0,0,0,,with assorted injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:07.88,英文,,0,0,0,,The cops found her lying on the sofa in the den,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.95,0:22:10.65,英文,,0,0,0,,beat to hell, wrapped in a blanket, naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Cliff Riker,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:15.77,英文,,0,0,0,,her spouse, was obviously intoxicated,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:16.94,英文,,0,0,0,,highly agitated,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:21.77,英文,,0,0,0,,and initially wanted to dish out to the cops what he was giving his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:23.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Which was, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:26.41,英文,,0,0,0,,a severe beating with an aluminum baseball bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:28.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Evidently his weapon of choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:33.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about Miss Birdie's millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.69,0:22:36.96,英文,,0,0,0,,No, I want to talk about Cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:39.76,英文,,0,0,0,,I want to talk about what happened to Cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:41.25,英文,,0,0,0,,He spent the night in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:42.25,英文,,0,0,0,,His family bailed him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.06,0:22:45.55,英文,,0,0,0,,He's due in court in a week. Nothing will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:47.52,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:50.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Colleen Janice Birdsong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.62,0:22:52.72,英文,,0,0,0,,She did indeed inherit a couple of million bucks
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.79,0:22:54.09,英文,,0,0,0,,from her late second husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:58.43,英文,,0,0,0,,But lawyers, bad trust department investments,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:02.28,英文,,0,0,0,,and the IRS totally devoured the estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.35,0:23:04.45,英文,,0,0,0,,All except for about $40,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:08.32,英文,,0,0,0,,which Miss Birdie probably tucked in her mattress
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:09.92,英文,,0,0,0,,for all we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:11.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:21.22,英文,,0,0,0,,you are my sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:22.52,英文,,0,0,0,,My only sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:25.09,英文,,0,0,0,,You make me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:27.03,英文,,0,0,0,,When skies are gray
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:34.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Do not take my sunshine away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:36.30,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:37.52,英文,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a lovely day?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.59,0:23:40.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, it's... it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:43.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, here's my mulch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:44.99,英文,,0,0,0,,That's right. There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:46.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Right there. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:48.63,英文,,0,0,0,,Stop it, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:50.47,英文,,0,0,0,,All right. Just put it right there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:52.17,英文,,0,0,0,,My yard boy will get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:54.47,英文,,0,0,0,,Just right down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:57.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a fine bunch of mulch?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.93,0:24:26.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.44,0:24:29.51,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm not one to meddle, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.37,0:24:33.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.18,0:24:35.54,英文,,0,0,0,,Are you in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.61,0:24:37.73,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.80,0:24:40.10,英文,,0,0,0,,But thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.17,0:24:42.00,英文,,0,0,0,,OK, well, I'm right up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.07,0:24:43.83,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm just studying for the bar exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.90,0:24:46.47,英文,,0,0,0,,so if you need anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.54,0:24:48.01,英文,,0,0,0,,just holler at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.07,0:24:49.06,英文,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.06,0:24:50.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Anything. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.98,0:24:53.34,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.38,0:24:57.82,英文,,0,0,0,,My name is Rudy Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.88,0:24:59.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Kelly Riker. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.64,0:25:02.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Kelly, it's nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.42,0:25:04.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Why don't you sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.49,0:25:07.29,英文,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. Take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.73,0:25:15.11,英文,,0,0,0,,What school do you go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.40,0:25:18.97,英文,,0,0,0,,I went to Austin Peay
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.04,0:25:21.41,英文,,0,0,0,,and then law school at Memphis state.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.20,0:25:26.88,英文,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to go to college,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.97,0:25:30.62,英文,,0,0,0,,but it didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.22,0:25:32.28,英文,,0,0,0,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.35,0:25:34.45,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I always thought I'd go,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.52,0:25:36.25,英文,,0,0,0,,but it didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.93,0:25:38.66,英文,,0,0,0,,What kind of lawyer do you want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.38,0:25:42.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I enjoy trial work, so, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.38,0:25:47.11,英文,,0,0,0,,I'd like to spend my days in the courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.91,0:25:51.49,英文,,0,0,0,,Defending criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.48,0:25:54.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.56,0:25:57.02,英文,,0,0,0,,They're entitled to a good defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.59,0:25:59.86,英文,,0,0,0,,They have a right to their day in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.71,0:26:01.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Murderers?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.35,0:26:07.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Most murderers can't afford a private lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.88,0:26:12.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Rapists and...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.55,0:26:15.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Child molesters?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.70,0:26:19.33,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.40,0:26:22.07,英文,,0,0,0,,Men who beat their wives?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.16,0:26:37.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Criminal work is a real rare specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.40,0:26:40.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Um, I'll probably be doing more, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.67,0:26:43.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Civil litigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.95,0:26:45.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Like lawsuits and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.64,0:26:46.93,英文,,0,0,0,,- Right. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.68,0:26:52.26,英文,,0,0,0,,It's, uh... Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.11,0:27:02.21,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.27,0:27:04.28,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey. Hey there. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.34,0:27:05.54,英文,,0,0,0,,What you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.61,0:27:07.51,英文,,0,0,0,,How's the fishing going?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.17,0:27:10.17,英文,,0,0,0,,Um, it's, uh, it's going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.35,0:27:12.13,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm actually talking to the prospect right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.20,0:27:14.50,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, you better sign her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.57,0:27:17.54,英文,,0,0,0,,What... Rudy? Rudy? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.61,0:27:18.84,英文,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.91,0:27:20.14,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.21,0:27:22.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks for the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.71,0:27:24.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, tomorrow night?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.51,0:27:26.75,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.08,0:27:43.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Time's up. Pencils down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.88,0:27:45.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Please pass your test booklets to your right
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.92,0:27:48.17,英文,,0,0,0,,so that your proctors may gather them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.26,0:27:49.69,英文,,0,0,0,,In my first year at law school,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.95,0:27:51.86,英文,,0,0,0,,everybody loved everybody else
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.92,0:27:53.92,英文,,0,0,0,,because we were all studying the law,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.99,0:27:56.46,英文,,0,0,0,,and the law was a noble thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.53,0:27:58.33,英文,,0,0,0,,By my third year,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.40,0:28:00.84,英文,,0,0,0,,you were lucky if you weren't murdered in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.20,0:28:02.33,英文,,0,0,0,,People stole exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.40,0:28:04.67,英文,,0,0,0,,hid research materials from the library,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.74,0:28:06.67,英文,,0,0,0,,and lied to the professors.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.17,0:28:12.23,英文,,0,0,0,,Such is the nature of the profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.82,0:28:18.52,英文,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.58,0:28:21.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Half an hour ago, her husband came in...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.09,0:28:22.99,英文,,0,0,0,,And threw a bowl of soup at her
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.06,0:28:24.99,英文,,0,0,0,,because she just won't get it through her head
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.06,0:28:26.97,英文,,0,0,0,,- how much he loves her. - This is my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.03,0:28:32.03,英文,,0,0,0,,Pregnant at 18, married, then a miscarriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.10,0:28:34.03,英文,,0,0,0,,probably because he beat her up...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.10,0:28:36.13,英文,,0,0,0,,and still, she can't leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.20,0:28:38.47,英文,,0,0,0,,You are gonna have to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.80,0:28:39.86,英文,,0,0,0,,Everything I've ever seen
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.87,0:28:42.21,英文,,0,0,0,,tells me that this girl is a loser,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.27,0:28:44.66,英文,,0,0,0,,scarred and broken and maybe even dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.18,0:28:47.98,英文,,0,0,0,,but I've never really seen anyone like her before,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.05,0:28:49.21,英文,,0,0,0,,and instead of running away,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.46,0:28:51.55,英文,,0,0,0,,all I want to do is protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.52,0:29:18.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Visiting hours are over, hon. You kids need to wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.83,0:29:40.48,英文,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.75,0:29:42.31,英文,,0,0,0,,He should be shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.28,0:29:46.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Any man who'd beat his wife with an aluminum bat
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.62,0:29:47.89,英文,,0,0,0,,needs to be shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.56,0:29:51.49,英文,,0,0,0,,How did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.73,0:29:53.81,英文,,0,0,0,,There are police reports, there are ambulance reports,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.88,0:29:56.31,英文,,0,0,0,,there are hospital records.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.53,0:29:57.87,英文,,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna wait, Kelly,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.93,0:30:00.66,英文,,0,0,0,,until he decides to hit you in the head with that bat of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.70,0:30:03.84,英文,,0,0,0,,'Cause that could kill you, you know. That'd be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.91,0:30:06.13,英文,,0,0,0,,A couple of good shots to the skull, and that would be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.14,0:30:09.28,英文,,0,0,0,,Stop it, don't tell me how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.57,0:30:17.34,英文,,0,0,0,,Look at me, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.40,0:30:19.30,英文,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.37,0:30:26.21,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you have a father or a brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.88,0:30:29.21,英文,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.02,0:30:32.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Because if my daughter got beat the way your husband beat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.88,0:30:35.85,英文,,0,0,0,,I swear to God I'd break his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.09,0:30:39.66,英文,,0,0,0,,No big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.04,0:30:43.66,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.73,0:30:48.97,英文,,0,0,0,,No one to take care of me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.80,0:30:58.41,英文,,0,0,0,,Kelly, I'll try to help you any way I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.48,0:31:01.24,英文,,0,0,0,,but you have to file for divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.42,0:31:05.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Do it now while you're in the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.11,0:31:06.60,英文,,0,0,0,,being treated for the last beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.28,0:31:08.35,英文,,0,0,0,,It'll sail through.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.40,0:31:10.08,英文,,0,0,0,,What better proof is there than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.06,0:31:15.29,英文,,0,0,0,,I...I can't file for a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.26,0:31:17.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.84,0:31:20.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Because he'll kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.55,0:31:25.06,英文,,0,0,0,,He tells me so all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.66,0:31:29.82,英文,,0,0,0,,That's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.15,0:31:32.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Could you pass me a pillow, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.93,0:31:35.00,英文,,0,0,0,,and put it under my foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.28,0:31:36.86,英文,,0,0,0,,There's one over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.24,0:31:47.47,英文,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.25,0:31:51.86,英文,,0,0,0,,That OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.95,0:31:53.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.20,0:31:54.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.80,0:31:56.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Could you pass me my gown, too, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.57,0:31:57.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.82,0:32:00.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.15,0:32:02.86,英文,,0,0,0,,You need some help putting it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.15,0:32:05.33,英文,,0,0,0,,No. Just turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.60,0:32:07.01,英文,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.80,0:32:27.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.82,0:32:29.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.77,0:32:31.24,英文,,0,0,0,,I live here. Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.33,0:32:33.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh. I'm Delbert's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.82,0:32:34.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Delbert? Who the hell is Delbert?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.11,0:32:36.08,英文,,0,0,0,,How did you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.22,0:32:37.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Birdie gave me the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.08,0:32:39.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.28,0:32:40.48,英文,,0,0,0,,I am the person who lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.53,0:32:42.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you understand that? You have no right to be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.71,0:32:43.82,英文,,0,0,0,,- This is a private residence. - Oh, yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.95,0:32:45.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Some place. Get a grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.42,0:32:47.28,英文,,0,0,0,,Birdie wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.69,0:32:52.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Agreements are permanent,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.11,0:32:55.82,英文,,0,0,0,,and restrictions mentioned above herein...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.08,0:32:57.40,英文,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.60,0:32:59.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, you must be the lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.60,0:33:00.75,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm Rudy Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.93,0:33:02.80,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm Delbert Birdsong, Birdie's youngest.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.11,0:33:04.53,英文,,0,0,0,,He yelled at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.71,0:33:06.66,英文,,0,0,0,,He told me to get out of his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.93,0:33:08.00,英文,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.08,0:33:09.37,英文,,0,0,0,,You're damn right that's so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.42,0:33:10.40,英文,,0,0,0,,That goes for the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.48,0:33:11.55,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't want neither one of you up there
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.60,0:33:13.51,英文,,0,0,0,,going through my stuff. That's private property.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.64,0:33:15.02,英文,,0,0,0,,I come home to check on mama,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.06,0:33:17.82,英文,,0,0,0,,and, damn, she's got a stinking lawyer living with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.31,0:33:20.48,英文,,0,0,0,,You been messing with my mama's will?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.69,0:33:22.89,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, she's your mama. Why don't you ask her?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.99,0:33:26.62,英文,,0,0,0,,She won't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.69,0:33:27.83,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.31,0:33:29.60,英文,,0,0,0,,then neither can I.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.55,0:33:32.71,英文,,0,0,0,,That's a lawyer-client privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.59,0:33:40.25,英文,,0,0,0,,But I tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.33,0:33:45.23,英文,,0,0,0,,I made a couple of phone calls...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.35,0:33:48.05,英文,,0,0,0,,Verifying some accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.62,0:33:50.58,英文,,0,0,0,,Your mama's second husband
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.11,0:33:53.02,英文,,0,0,0,,left her an enormous fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.08,0:33:54.42,英文,,0,0,0,,How big?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.77,0:33:56.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Big.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.76,0:33:58.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Big.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.48,0:34:00.17,英文,,0,0,0,,I hope you're not meddling, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.08,0:34:05.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Mama, wouldn't you just love to come and visit with us
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.71,0:34:07.25,英文,,0,0,0,,down in Florida for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.42,0:34:09.10,英文,,0,0,0,,You'd love it down there, mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.17,0:34:11.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Mama, come on back in and get some cake, mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.60,0:34:12.62,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll get her some milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.71,0:34:15.46,英文,,0,0,0,,We're close to the fountain of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.55,0:34:18.88,英文,,0,0,0,,We ain't but 33 Miles away and 180 Miles from Disney world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.55,0:34:44.97,英文,,0,0,0,,How you feeling, Donny Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.04,0:34:46.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.17,0:34:48.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Don't I look fantastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.81,0:34:49.97,英文,,0,0,0,,You feel up to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.04,0:34:51.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's go already.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.78,0:34:53.11,英文,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.25,0:34:58.71,英文,,0,0,0,,A lawyer's not supposed to become personally involved with his client,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.38,0:35:01.20,英文,,0,0,0,,but there's all kinds of lawyers
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.99,0:35:03.82,英文,,0,0,0,,and all kinds of clients, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.72,0:35:20.39,英文,,0,0,0,,You OK, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.62,0:35:34.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Riker! Riker! Riker!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.97,0:35:36.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Riker! Riker!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.80,0:35:38.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Can I get you guys anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.08,0:35:42.61,英文,,0,0,0,,Um, want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.68,0:35:45.11,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll have a shot of Jack Daniels, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.65,0:35:49.98,英文,,0,0,0,,What's it gonna do, kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.37,0:35:55.49,英文,,0,0,0,,Miss Birdie, this is my friend Donny Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.56,0:35:56.59,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, Donny Ray,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.66,0:35:59.59,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad to have you come over and visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.66,0:36:01.16,英文,,0,0,0,,Hello, Miss Birdie.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.23,0:36:02.93,英文,,0,0,0,,Where... oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.00,0:36:04.16,英文,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.23,0:36:06.33,英文,,0,0,0,,You just come right over here and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.40,0:36:08.07,英文,,0,0,0,,Just have a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.64,0:36:11.10,英文,,0,0,0,,You have me all...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.17,0:36:12.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Blocked off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.87,0:36:14.07,英文,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.04,0:36:28.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Miss Birdie. I got to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.13,0:36:29.11,英文,,0,0,0,,My back's killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.27,0:36:31.96,英文,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot. This came for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.17,0:36:38.43,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.50,0:36:40.50,英文,,0,0,0,,Ohh! Isn't it exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.57,0:36:44.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Ohh. I'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.07,0:36:45.37,英文,,0,0,0,,- I passed the bar. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.16,0:36:48.59,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on. Here's to Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.66,0:36:51.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on passing the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.66,0:36:53.36,英文,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.43,0:36:54.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Iced tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.23,0:36:58.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.40,0:37:00.04,英文,,0,0,0,,That's some good work, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.11,0:37:02.14,英文,,0,0,0,,I got a check today from the Van Landel settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.21,0:37:03.91,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm giving you boys a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.98,0:37:06.44,英文,,0,0,0,,5,500 each.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.51,0:37:07.54,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.61,0:37:09.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Sign up some more cases, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.85,0:37:11.92,英文,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.45,0:37:17.29,英文,,0,0,0,,So are we gonna be ready for tomorrow morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.36,0:37:18.82,英文,,0,0,0,,9:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.42,0:37:22.53,英文,,0,0,0,,We're gonna argue
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.53,0:37:25.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Great Benefit's motion to dismiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.73,0:37:28.93,英文,,0,0,0,,Mmm, yeah, I think we're ready. We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.00,0:37:32.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Deck and I have been going over it. I think we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.11,0:37:35.87,英文,,0,0,0,,I hope so, because I might, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.94,0:37:39.44,英文,,0,0,0,,I might have you handle some of that argument, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.22,0:37:46.66,英文,,0,0,0,,It would be awfully embarrassing if we lose this case on a dismissal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.12,0:37:48.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.35,0:37:51.16,英文,,0,0,0,,OK, I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.52,0:37:54.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Food's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.09,0:37:56.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.73,0:37:58.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Bruiser. Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.86,0:38:08.75,英文,,0,0,0,,Something's about to go down. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.64,0:38:12.66,英文,,0,0,0,,He never split money like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.73,0:38:15.91,英文,,0,0,0,,What do you think's behind his generosity?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.41,0:38:18.45,英文,,0,0,0,,Come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.48,0:38:20.72,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.55,0:38:23.72,英文,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.22,0:38:28.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, one of Bruiser's ex-partners testified before a grand jury.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.09,0:38:30.86,英文,,0,0,0,,I think he's cut a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.93,0:38:32.33,英文,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.40,0:38:34.26,英文,,0,0,0,,- before he's singing on Bruiser. - So what? So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.31,0:38:38.00,英文,,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.75,0:38:40.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Make a move? Deck, I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.73,0:38:44.18,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Well, things might get a little hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.81,0:38:47.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Jury-tampering, tax evasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.81,0:38:49.58,英文,,0,0,0,,money-skimming, you name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.65,0:38:51.28,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm nervous, real nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.35,0:38:54.29,英文,,0,0,0,,What are you nervous about? They can't arrest us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.35,0:38:56.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.62,0:38:59.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Supposing they come in with subpoenas and hacksaws. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.62,0:39:00.89,英文,,0,0,0,,They can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.96,0:39:03.86,英文,,0,0,0,,They've been known to do that in racketeering cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.35,0:39:05.91,英文,,0,0,0,,They come in, they confiscate the files,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.00,0:39:08.13,英文,,0,0,0,,they haul the computers out. What's that leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.26,0:39:09.87,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried about being arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.04,0:39:11.55,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.60,0:39:14.21,英文,,0,0,0,,All right, so what are you saying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.27,0:39:15.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's bolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.95,0:39:19.38,英文,,0,0,0,,How much money you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.75,0:39:22.35,英文,,0,0,0,,I got... Got $5,500.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.41,0:39:23.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.78,0:39:25.82,英文,,0,0,0,,We can rent a small office,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.88,0:39:27.85,英文,,0,0,0,,$500 a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.62,0:39:31.64,英文,,0,0,0,,We operate on a shoestring for the first 6 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.04,0:39:33.57,英文,,0,0,0,,It'll be beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.86,0:39:35.71,英文,,0,0,0,,We split everything, everything
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.78,0:39:37.71,英文,,0,0,0,,right down the middle, 50-50.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.17,0:39:42.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Costs, expenses, profits... everything right down the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.51,0:39:46.44,英文,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.08,0:39:49.68,英文,,0,0,0,,You don't want to be my partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.84,0:39:52.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Um, no, it's not... they...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.66,0:39:54.71,英文,,0,0,0,,it's not that. It's just that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.80,0:39:56.57,英文,,0,0,0,,You're hitting me with this right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.71,0:39:58.58,英文,,0,0,0,,and I mean, you got to give me a minute, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.65,0:40:00.82,英文,,0,0,0,,I mean, you can't just spring it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.89,0:40:02.89,英文,,0,0,0,,We have to act fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.36,0:40:08.96,英文,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.91,0:40:13.20,英文,,0,0,0,,We'll do it for a while, see how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.77,0:40:15.63,英文,,0,0,0,,How many files do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.70,0:40:19.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Um, I... I got 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.46,0:40:21.28,英文,,0,0,0,,Get them out of there. Take them home,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.42,0:40:23.47,英文,,0,0,0,,but don't get caught, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.54,0:40:27.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Is somebody watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.18,0:40:28.68,英文,,0,0,0,,The feds.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.28,0:40:32.85,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm eatin' too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.03,0:41:03.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.42,0:41:07.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey. Listen, I went by the office this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.67,0:41:09.94,英文,,0,0,0,,The FBI was chaining up the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.00,0:41:11.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Is Bruiser comin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.55,0:41:12.53,英文,,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.97,0:41:14.27,英文,,0,0,0,,Arrest warrants have been issued
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.34,0:41:15.86,英文,,0,0,0,,for both Bruiser and Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.91,0:41:16.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.84,0:41:18.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Just relax. You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.75,0:41:20.81,英文,,0,0,0,,It's just a motion. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.88,0:41:22.18,英文,,0,0,0,,- Me? - Yeah. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.25,0:41:23.28,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.35,0:41:25.37,英文,,0,0,0,,You know this case. You're gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.42,0:41:26.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Listen, I don't even have my license.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.71,0:41:28.42,英文,,0,0,0,,We don't need a license. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.13,0:41:38.53,英文,,0,0,0,,I've memorized the Black files cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.15,0:41:41.02,英文,,0,0,0,,I've read all the books on jurisprudence,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.24,0:41:43.09,英文,,0,0,0,,the rules of evidence and discovery,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.64,0:41:45.56,英文,,0,0,0,,but I take one look around the courtroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.99,0:41:48.41,英文,,0,0,0,,and I realize I haven't even been born yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.57,0:41:54.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Uh, sir? Your honor, um, ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.84,0:41:58.59,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm here for the Black vs. Great Benefit hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.20,0:42:00.45,英文,,0,0,0,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.66,0:42:01.77,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, Rudy Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.84,0:42:05.18,英文,,0,0,0,,I work for J. Lyman Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.24,0:42:07.61,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, you work for J. Lyman.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.84,0:42:14.30,英文,,0,0,0,,Staunch supporter of the tobacco lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.57,0:42:18.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Where's Mr. Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.57,0:42:24.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Honestly, your honor, I... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.66,0:42:26.17,英文,,0,0,0,,He was supposed to meet me here,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.35,0:42:27.51,英文,,0,0,0,,and I don't know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.58,0:42:30.28,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, why doesn't that surprise me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.15,0:42:33.29,英文,,0,0,0,,So what do you want? You want a continuance.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.35,0:42:34.45,英文,,0,0,0,,No, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.66,0:42:37.61,英文,,0,0,0,,I... I am prepared to argue this motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.68,0:42:39.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Are you a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.41,0:42:42.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I just passed the bar,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.75,0:42:44.84,英文,,0,0,0,,and, uh, these are my clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.88,0:42:46.88,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Stone filed this on my behalf
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.95,0:42:48.48,英文,,0,0,0,,until I passed the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.15,0:42:50.93,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, you got a hell of a lot of nerve
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.15,0:42:52.84,英文,,0,0,0,,walking into my courtroom without a license.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.88,0:42:54.75,英文,,0,0,0,,Now get the hell out of here, get your license,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.76,0:42:55.95,英文,,0,0,0,,and then you come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.08,0:42:57.39,英文,,0,0,0,,Get a license!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.51,0:42:59.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Come back when you got a damn license!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.55,0:43:01.67,英文,,0,0,0,,May it please the court...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.73,0:43:05.97,英文,,0,0,0,,For the record, my name is Leo F. Drummond
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.04,0:43:07.81,英文,,0,0,0,,of Tinley-Brit,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.87,0:43:09.27,英文,,0,0,0,,counsel for Great Benefit,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.34,0:43:10.77,英文,,0,0,0,,and I say
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.84,0:43:14.04,英文,,0,0,0,,if this young man has passed the bar exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.41,0:43:16.35,英文,,0,0,0,,your honor, let him argue the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.18,0:43:21.22,英文,,0,0,0,,We welcome him to, uh, big-time litigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.29,0:43:23.89,英文,,0,0,0,,You have no objection, Mr. Drummond?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.96,0:43:25.92,英文,,0,0,0,,If it please the court,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.13,0:43:29.02,英文,,0,0,0,,I would be honored to introduce Mr. Baylor
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.28,0:43:31.55,英文,,0,0,0,,to the practice of law in the great state of Tennessee.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.86,0:43:35.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Judge, you can give him the oath right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.15,0:43:37.02,英文,,0,0,0,,and I'll be pleased to stand for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.00,0:43:40.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Are you certain you're prepared to proceed, Mr. Baylor?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.82,0:43:43.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Abso...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.59,0:43:45.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Your honor, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.39,0:43:49.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Very well, then. Raise your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.73,0:43:51.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you solemnly swear, Rudy Baylor,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.67,0:43:54.93,英文,,0,0,0,,that you will support the constitution and the laws
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.06,0:43:57.24,英文,,0,0,0,,of the United States and the state of Tennessee faithfully and honorably,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.27,0:43:59.33,英文,,0,0,0,,conduct yourself in the practice of your profession
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.34,0:44:02.81,英文,,0,0,0,,to the best of your skills and abilities, so help you God?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.15,0:44:05.61,英文,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.68,0:44:09.12,英文,,0,0,0,,- OK, fine, fine. That's it. - Let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.18,0:44:10.84,英文,,0,0,0,,- Congratulations. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.97,0:44:11.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.89,0:44:15.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Sworn in by a fool and vouched for by a scoundrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.62,0:44:16.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Harvey.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.62,0:44:17.95,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm a lawyer at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.08,0:44:19.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.22,0:44:26.04,英文,,0,0,0,,May I, Harv?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.08,0:44:27.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.17,0:44:29.64,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.61,0:44:39.02,英文,,0,0,0,,This lawsuit bothers me, Mr. Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.46,0:44:41.73,英文,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't use the word "Frivolous,"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.62,0:44:45.95,英文,,0,0,0,,but I'm not impressed with the merits of it, to be Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.91,0:44:49.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Ahem. I'm gonna try to sneak some gym time in.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.64,0:44:51.77,英文,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm really tired of these type of lawsuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.12,0:44:53.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Don't make no excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.22,0:44:57.42,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm inclined to grant the motion to dismiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.88,0:45:02.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, you can, uh, refile it in federal court, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.80,0:45:04.13,英文,,0,0,0,,take it somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.37,0:45:08.31,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't want it clogging up my docket.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.09,0:45:11.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, excuse me while I go to the can.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.46,0:45:12.84,英文,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.82,0:45:17.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.37,0:45:21.28,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm a very expensive lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.26,0:45:24.40,英文,,0,0,0,,from a very expensive firm, and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.71,0:45:26.22,英文,,0,0,0,,I've had a lot of cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.91,0:45:29.52,英文,,0,0,0,,I can hit pretty close to the center of the dart board,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.04,0:45:31.55,英文,,0,0,0,,and I told my clients, Great Benefit,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.00,0:45:35.37,英文,,0,0,0,,that cost alone here gonna be a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.46,0:45:38.88,英文,,0,0,0,,And for you, too. Your side, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.55,0:45:41.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, they've authorized me...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.57,0:45:45.51,英文,,0,0,0,,To offer you and your clients...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.68,0:45:50.48,英文,,0,0,0,,$50,000 to settle this thing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.17,0:45:54.80,英文,,0,0,0,,And I... I may even be able to raise that figure up
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.88,0:45:58.48,英文,,0,0,0,,as high as, uh, maybe 75,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.98,0:46:02.26,英文,,0,0,0,,No admission of liability, you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.60,0:46:05.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Course, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.22,0:46:07.87,英文,,0,0,0,,If you say no,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.48,0:46:10.22,英文,,0,0,0,,then it's going to be world war III.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.96,0:46:14.86,英文,,0,0,0,,My turn now. May I, Harv?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.93,0:46:16.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.35,0:46:26.44,英文,,0,0,0,,There's not much of a lawsuit here, I'm afraid, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.26,0:46:30.22,英文,,0,0,0,,But maybe I could lean on Leo
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.31,0:46:31.73,英文,,0,0,0,,to make you an offer of a settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.17,0:46:33.82,英文,,0,0,0,,They'll probably want to throw some money at you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.86,0:46:36.93,英文,,0,0,0,,to keep from paying Leo a thousand bucks a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.82,0:46:42.40,英文,,0,0,0,,But he already offered me the cost of the defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.46,0:46:45.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.16,0:46:48.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, 75,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.48,0:46:52.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Jeez. Well, looky here, son,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.46,0:46:56.04,英文,,0,0,0,,you'd be crazy not to take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.51,0:46:58.53,英文,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.15,0:47:00.44,英文,,0,0,0,,75,000? Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.75,0:47:03.82,英文,,0,0,0,,That's a... That's a bunch of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.08,0:47:05.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Doesn't sound like Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.51,0:47:07.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, he's a... he's a great guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.29,0:47:17.25,英文,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.32,0:47:18.72,英文,,0,0,0,,That was not a meeting in chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.79,0:47:20.26,英文,,0,0,0,,That was an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.32,0:47:20.84,英文,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.97,0:47:22.17,英文,,0,0,0,,They tag-teamed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.31,0:47:23.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.42,0:47:24.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Think they would have done that to Bruiser?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.80,0:47:26.93,英文,,0,0,0,,Nah. Bruiser's too savvy for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.33,0:47:28.53,英文,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.75,0:47:30.35,英文,,0,0,0,,They offered me 75,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.40,0:47:31.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Good. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.08,0:47:34.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Our third is 25,000. We need the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.93,0:47:36.88,英文,,0,0,0,,Judge Hale is serious about dismissing this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.02,0:47:38.80,英文,,0,0,0,,He's an just an old angry man
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.81,0:47:40.04,英文,,0,0,0,,who's been sitting on that bench too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.31,0:47:42.53,英文,,0,0,0,,The best thing we can do is grab what we can
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.57,0:47:44.71,英文,,0,0,0,,to make things easy on his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.06,0:47:47.64,英文,,0,0,0,,The insurance company made an offer to settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.14,0:47:49.91,英文,,0,0,0,,What kind of offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.88,0:47:52.48,英文,,0,0,0,,$75,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.26,0:47:56.31,英文,,0,0,0,,They figure that's what it's gonna cost
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.40,0:47:58.35,英文,,0,0,0,,to pay their lawyers to defend the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.33,0:48:02.17,英文,,0,0,0,,Son of a bitches think they can just buy us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.58,0:48:05.72,英文,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what they think.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.46,0:48:11.64,英文,,0,0,0,,You better talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.73,0:48:18.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna settle, Rudy?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.05,0:48:23.86,英文,,0,0,0,,I mean, some of the money is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.91,0:48:29.55,英文,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.91,0:48:34.22,英文,,0,0,0,,I wanna expose these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.48,0:48:38.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Mama, could you get me a glass of water, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.10,0:48:41.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.45,0:48:50.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Whatever you get out of this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.84,0:48:52.84,英文,,0,0,0,,take care of my family with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.42,0:48:57.51,英文,,0,0,0,,I really love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.95,0:48:59.24,英文,,0,0,0,,I can't help thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.37,0:49:02.17,英文,,0,0,0,,that while we're all out there scrambling around for an edge
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.40,0:49:04.09,英文,,0,0,0,,like we're never gonna die,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.31,0:49:06.06,英文,,0,0,0,,this boy's looking right at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.13,0:49:08.60,英文,,0,0,0,,and he's doing it almost alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.67,0:49:10.40,英文,,0,0,0,,I can't even begin
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.47,0:49:12.75,英文,,0,0,0,,to imagine the courage it must take.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.68,0:49:20.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.15,0:49:23.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Guess who died last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.18,0:49:24.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.18,0:49:25.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you ever sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.04,0:49:27.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Harvey Hale.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.73,0:49:28.57,英文,,0,0,0,,62.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.80,0:49:30.09,英文,,0,0,0,,Quite a pedigree.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.66,0:49:31.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Judge Hale?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.64,0:49:33.59,英文,,0,0,0,,Yep. Croaked with a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.66,0:49:35.63,英文,,0,0,0,,Dropped dead in his swimming pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.04,0:49:37.02,英文,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.19,0:49:38.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.20,0:49:39.60,英文,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.35,0:49:41.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Guess what newly made judge
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.08,0:49:44.08,英文,,0,0,0,,was assigned Great Benefit case in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.35,0:49:46.48,英文,,0,0,0,,How in the hell am I supposed to know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.57,0:49:47.77,英文,,0,0,0,,Tyrone Kipler.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.91,0:49:50.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Black Harvard civil-rights lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.62,0:49:52.62,英文,,0,0,0,,He can't stand Tinley-Brit,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.88,0:49:54.48,英文,,0,0,0,,and he's tough on insurance companies...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.57,0:49:56.13,英文,,0,0,0,,sues them all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.22,0:49:57.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Great luck for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.18,0:49:58.00,英文,,0,0,0,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.13,0:49:59.60,英文,,0,0,0,,You know what a rainmaker is, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.73,0:50:01.65,英文,,0,0,0,,The bucks are gonna be falling from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.72,0:50:03.20,英文,,0,0,0,,It's 5:00 right now. What time you coming down?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.37,0:50:04.62,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll be down in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.69,0:50:06.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Get down here. We gotta talk about fast-tracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.53,0:50:07.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Coffee's on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.69,0:50:08.86,英文,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.54,0:50:12.34,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Drummond...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.18,0:50:15.64,英文,,0,0,0,,You've objected to the fast-tracking of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.24,0:50:18.44,英文,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.20,0:50:20.12,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, your honor, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.19,0:50:23.91,英文,,0,0,0,,This issue's already been ruled upon by Judge Hale.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.22,0:50:28.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, the preparations required for fast-tracking the case
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.70,0:50:31.46,英文,,0,0,0,,place an undue burden on both parties, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.91,0:50:33.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.35,0:50:36.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you something, Mr. Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.97,0:50:38.44,英文,,0,0,0,,As a defense lawyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.48,0:50:42.66,英文,,0,0,0,,have you ever agreed to the fast-tracking of a lawsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.75,0:50:44.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Why, your honor, I believe I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.00,0:50:47.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.18,0:50:49.88,英文,,0,0,0,,Give me the name of the case and the court it was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.13,0:50:53.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.46,0:50:54.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, your honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.84,0:50:56.93,英文,,0,0,0,,I have to get back to you on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.33,0:50:59.39,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, call me this afternoon by 3:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.49,0:51:03.56,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't believe I'm gonna be in before 3:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.63,0:51:06.17,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, call me when you get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.23,0:51:10.08,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm very anxious to hear about this case you agreed to fast-track.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.48,0:51:11.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.40,0:51:14.48,英文,,0,0,0,,This boy is about to die, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.74,0:51:17.71,英文,,0,0,0,,You do agree that we need to record his testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.78,0:51:19.18,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.25,0:51:20.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Of course, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.97,0:51:22.72,英文,,0,0,0,,It's just my trial calendar is pushing me around pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.25,0:51:27.42,英文,,0,0,0,,How about next Thursday afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.49,0:51:29.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Great for me, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.16,0:51:32.59,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.66,0:51:34.19,英文,,0,0,0,,That's a week from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.26,0:51:36.20,英文,,0,0,0,,I believe I'm out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.84,0:51:38.75,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am out of town Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.30,0:51:43.87,英文,,0,0,0,,Deposition is set for...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.94,0:51:46.41,英文,,0,0,0,,Next Thursday afternoon at 2 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.84,0:51:49.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Sorry if it inconveniences the defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.94,0:51:54.08,英文,,0,0,0,,but God knows there's enough of you guys to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.98,0:51:56.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, what's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.02,0:51:58.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, your honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.75,0:52:01.06,英文,,0,0,0,,the motion to dismiss is still pending.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.15,0:52:04.12,英文,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.19,0:52:07.09,英文,,0,0,0,,That motion is denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.60,0:52:08.61,英文,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.68,0:52:10.50,英文,,0,0,0,,I guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.28,0:52:13.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.00,0:52:15.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your appointment, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.97,0:52:17.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.04,0:52:21.37,英文,,0,0,0,,And, Mr. Drummond...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.62,0:52:25.91,英文,,0,0,0,,don't forget to call me
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.00,0:52:28.26,英文,,0,0,0,,with the name of that case you agreed to fast-track.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.33,0:52:30.87,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.91,0:52:42.08,英文,,0,0,0,,You in over your head, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.60,0:52:46.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.25,0:52:53.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Now Deck wants to do an ad on the local rap station.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.00,0:52:55.66,英文,,0,0,0,,And as much as I'd love to hear it, we can't afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.93,0:52:59.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Furnishings, bar dues, 750 for a fax machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.73,0:53:01.73,英文,,0,0,0,,400 for a lease on a computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.91,0:53:03.95,英文,,0,0,0,,a down payment on a new secondhand car,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.13,0:53:05.51,英文,,0,0,0,,and we're broke again.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.09,0:53:09.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Deck says he's thrilled with the way things are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.94,0:53:41.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.27,0:53:42.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.47,0:53:44.87,英文,,0,0,0,,Come in. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.94,0:53:46.38,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm doing good. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.44,0:53:47.61,英文,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.68,0:53:50.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'm going up to Cleveland Wednesday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.48,0:53:51.75,英文,,0,0,0,,It's the headquarters of Great Benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.82,0:53:54.22,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take depositions from all the executives.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.29,0:53:56.55,英文,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.62,0:53:58.22,英文,,0,0,0,,And don't worry about expenses, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.35,0:53:59.73,英文,,0,0,0,,We're gonna take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.86,0:54:02.22,英文,,0,0,0,,- Thank you, Rudy. - It's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.51,0:54:07.64,英文,,0,0,0,,It's awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.67,0:54:12.26,英文,,0,0,0,,My associate, Deck Schifflet.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.31,0:54:13.86,英文,,0,0,0,,- How do you do? - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.02,0:54:27.92,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rudy...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.22,0:54:29.75,英文,,0,0,0,,Tyrone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.82,0:54:31.29,英文,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.35,0:54:32.42,英文,,0,0,0,,The judge is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.37,0:54:35.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Here, wait, Dot. Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.36,0:54:37.83,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.82,0:54:40.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.02,0:54:41.96,英文,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.13,0:54:43.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Come right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.26,0:54:45.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.11,0:54:46.04,英文,,0,0,0,,This is Mrs. Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.31,0:54:47.64,英文,,0,0,0,,His honor Tyrone Kipler.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.82,0:54:49.33,英文,,0,0,0,,It's a privilege to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.37,0:54:50.74,英文,,0,0,0,,The privilege is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.33,0:54:53.78,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.44,0:54:56.15,英文,,0,0,0,,There's not a lot of room here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.40,0:54:57.64,英文,,0,0,0,,Tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.73,0:54:58.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.60,0:55:01.28,英文,,0,0,0,,Is that all right with you, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.52,0:55:04.45,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.71,0:55:06.26,英文,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.52,0:55:07.64,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.11,0:55:22.56,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm looking at a team of lawyers
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.62,0:55:24.84,英文,,0,0,0,,who are pulling down a $1,000 an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.02,0:55:26.08,英文,,0,0,0,,and I hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.80,0:55:28.35,英文,,0,0,0,,From their lofty perch,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.48,0:55:31.60,英文,,0,0,0,,pissing down on the whole justice system with disdain.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.40,0:55:35.57,英文,,0,0,0,,I used to hate them because I wasn't good enough for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.40,0:55:38.34,英文,,0,0,0,,Now I hate them for who they represent
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.41,0:55:40.42,英文,,0,0,0,,and what they represent.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.84,0:55:42.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.43,0:55:43.43,英文,,0,0,0,,Fine, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.49,0:55:45.43,英文,,0,0,0,,Hope the dogs didn't startle you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.50,0:55:46.84,英文,,0,0,0,,We're doing this thing outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.93,0:55:48.13,英文,,0,0,0,,It's a little cramped inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.26,0:55:49.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Just have a seat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.68,0:55:50.66,英文,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.75,0:55:52.71,英文,,0,0,0,,- How you doing? - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.20,0:56:12.01,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.42,0:56:20.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, Donny Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.82,0:56:23.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.68,0:56:26.17,英文,,0,0,0,,You've already met Judge Kipler.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.84,0:56:27.64,英文,,0,0,0,,Howdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.70,0:56:30.71,英文,,0,0,0,,This is Leo F. Drummond
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.77,0:56:32.53,英文,,0,0,0,,and associates.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.36,0:56:36.80,英文,,0,0,0,,This here is Tammy. She's the court reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.86,0:56:38.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.87,0:56:40.30,英文,,0,0,0,,Swear him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.75,0:56:42.93,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you swear the testimony you are about to give
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.06,0:56:44.67,英文,,0,0,0,,will be the truth, the whole truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.74,0:56:46.08,英文,,0,0,0,,and nothing but the truth, so help you God?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.22,0:56:47.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.66,0:56:54.53,英文,,0,0,0,,I told him...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.71,0:56:56.13,英文,,0,0,0,,I know. Come here, come here, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.26,0:56:58.65,英文,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. It's just a deposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.72,0:57:00.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Donny Ray, I'm Leo Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.66,0:57:02.71,英文,,0,0,0,,I represent Great Benefit,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.84,0:57:04.35,英文,,0,0,0,,and I'm very sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.61,0:57:06.18,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.24,0:57:07.74,英文,,0,0,0,,under these circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.26,0:57:09.25,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, we wouldn't be here
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.31,0:57:11.16,英文,,0,0,0,,if your clients had done what they should've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.86,0:57:13.42,英文,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon? I didn't hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.51,0:57:15.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid, you want a stick of gum?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.28,0:57:16.69,英文,,0,0,0,,- Sure. - Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.28,0:57:18.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Did you break your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.57,0:57:19.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.62,0:57:21.06,英文,,0,0,0,,You had an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.12,0:57:22.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.09,0:57:24.19,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm a lawyer, and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.26,0:57:26.70,英文,,0,0,0,,Give this to your mom... you his mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.76,0:57:29.70,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can get you some money for the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.31,0:57:45.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Why don't you help with the display?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.00,0:57:48.22,英文,,0,0,0,,OK. I'll go help this man first.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.29,0:57:50.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I got it. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.46,0:57:57.23,英文,,0,0,0,,Can I help you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.29,0:57:58.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm just looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.83,0:58:23.24,英文,,0,0,0,,There's a cinema down the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.30,0:58:25.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Buy a ticket. Center section, back row.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.31,0:58:26.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Be there in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.31,0:58:29.64,英文,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.51,0:59:09.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Cliff wants me to have a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.69,0:59:15.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, you have a decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.52,0:59:19.49,英文,,0,0,0,,He's become obsessed with sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.56,0:59:21.83,英文,,0,0,0,,He thinks it's going to keep us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.89,0:59:24.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Listen, I really don't want to talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.17,0:59:28.00,英文,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.03,1:00:17.15,英文,,0,0,0,,I think I can smell her perfume all the way to Cleveland.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.07,1:00:21.06,英文,,0,0,0,,It's hard keeping my mind on Leo Drummond and his people.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.30,1:00:23.60,英文,,0,0,0,,They'll be flying in, first class,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.67,1:00:25.31,英文,,0,0,0,,and after a leisurely dinner,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.37,1:00:26.40,英文,,0,0,0,,they'll meet in some board room
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.57,1:00:28.35,英文,,0,0,0,,and discuss my total destruction.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.21,1:00:31.18,英文,,0,0,0,,Around the time I'm checking into motel 6,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.25,1:00:33.28,英文,,0,0,0,,they'll be sleeping soundly in their suites.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.82,1:00:36.32,英文,,0,0,0,,And they'll wake up fresh and rested
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.38,1:00:37.73,英文,,0,0,0,,and ready for war.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.35,1:00:40.32,英文,,0,0,0,,It's my deposition,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.39,1:00:42.52,英文,,0,0,0,,but it's their turf.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.73,1:00:45.16,英文,,0,0,0,,Ah, young Rudy Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.23,1:00:46.63,英文,,0,0,0,,Just on time, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.70,1:00:47.63,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.70,1:00:49.70,英文,,0,0,0,,Get this boy some coffee, Tyler.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.76,1:00:50.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Jack Underhall.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.80,1:00:51.77,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.83,1:00:53.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Young lawyer is always a hungry lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.60,1:00:55.33,英文,,0,0,0,,All these boys claims, underwriting...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.37,1:00:58.53,英文,,0,0,0,,There must be a 100 years of legal experience gathered around the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.82,1:01:02.53,英文,,0,0,0,,My staff has flunked the bar exam 6 times.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.61,1:01:04.01,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, Rudy, don't be intimidated
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.08,1:01:06.05,英文,,0,0,0,,by all these boys on this side of the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.35,1:01:08.35,英文,,0,0,0,,I guarantee, you get them on the golf course,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.66,1:01:10.25,英文,,0,0,0,,they fold like a cheap suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.59,1:01:14.59,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's see what we got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.33,1:01:17.54,英文,,0,0,0,,I think maybe it's, uh, appropriate
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.61,1:01:20.58,英文,,0,0,0,,to start with the corporate designee,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.06,1:01:22.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Jack Underhall here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.06,1:01:24.45,英文,,0,0,0,,I... I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.32,1:01:26.58,英文,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.65,1:01:27.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, you heard me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.75,1:01:30.84,英文,,0,0,0,,I want to start with, uh, Jackie Lemancyzk, the claims handler.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.33,1:01:39.41,英文,,0,0,0,,I think it's best we start with Mr. Underhall.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.11,1:01:42.80,英文,,0,0,0,,With all due respect, Mr. Drummond,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.88,1:01:43.58,英文,,0,0,0,,this is my deposition.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.65,1:01:46.25,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna call these witnesses in the order in which I see fit,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.57,1:01:49.02,英文,,0,0,0,,so I'd like to start with Jackie Lemancyzk.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.51,1:01:54.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should just go call the judge.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.48,1:01:59.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't believe we have to get pugilistic
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.42,1:02:00.89,英文,,0,0,0,,this time of the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.24,1:02:03.32,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm not admitting to being pugilistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.29,1:02:06.57,英文,,0,0,0,,We're simply having a little problem
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.62,1:02:08.62,英文,,0,0,0,,with, uh, Jackie Lemancyzk.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.80,1:02:10.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, this Polish woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.66,1:02:12.80,英文,,0,0,0,,What sort of problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.50,1:02:16.17,英文,,0,0,0,,She doesn't work here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.47,1:02:18.70,英文,,0,0,0,,Was she fired?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.33,1:02:22.93,英文,,0,0,0,,She resigned. She resigned.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.77,1:02:25.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Um, well, where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.20,1:02:30.26,英文,,0,0,0,,She is no longer working for our client, and, uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.42,1:02:33.33,英文,,0,0,0,,we can't produce her as a witness,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.40,1:02:37.07,英文,,0,0,0,,so let's move along.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.06,1:02:40.99,英文,,0,0,0,,All right. Russell Crockett.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.06,1:02:43.39,英文,,0,0,0,,Anybody in the room named Russell Crockett?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.90,1:02:47.42,英文,,0,0,0,,He's gone, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.97,1:02:49.37,英文,,0,0,0,,He was downsized.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.60,1:02:51.14,英文,,0,0,0,,Downsized?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.51,1:02:53.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, what a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.44,1:02:55.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Our client's going through a periodic downsizing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.91,1:02:57.88,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that will happen, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.92,1:03:07.68,英文,,0,0,0,,How about Everett, uh, Lufkin...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.40,1:03:09.89,英文,,0,0,0,,Vice President of Claims.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.96,1:03:11.72,英文,,0,0,0,,Has he been downsized, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.79,1:03:14.26,英文,,0,0,0,,No, he's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.43,1:03:19.86,英文,,0,0,0,,You're Everett Lufkin?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.31,1:03:23.73,英文,,0,0,0,,My congratulations...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.62,1:03:26.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lufkin...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.88,1:03:28.57,英文,,0,0,0,,On your miraculous survival
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.71,1:03:30.52,英文,,0,0,0,,of the carnage of late here at Great Benefit.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.13,1:03:42.13,英文,,0,0,0,,I may not be 100% today, but I'm here in spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.48,1:03:49.77,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.62,1:03:51.86,英文,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.60,1:03:54.99,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm just wondering.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.17,1:03:58.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you even remember when you first sold out?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.34,1:04:08.35,英文,,0,0,0,,You're an arrogant little piss ant, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.55,1:04:13.46,英文,,0,0,0,,I advise you to mind your manners.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.15,1:04:15.65,英文,,0,0,0,,You're in the big water now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.72,1:04:17.39,英文,,0,0,0,,Mind my manners?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.59,1:04:21.68,英文,,0,0,0,,I come up here from Memphis
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.80,1:04:24.31,英文,,0,0,0,,to depose 4 people,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.80,1:04:26.17,英文,,0,0,0,,2 of whom are not here,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.15,1:04:29.15,英文,,0,0,0,,and you tell me to mind my manners?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.53,1:04:31.70,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, it's your dime.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.77,1:04:33.74,英文,,0,0,0,,What's your call, son?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.94,1:04:37.34,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna depose him...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.68,1:04:39.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lufkin over there...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.91,1:04:41.33,英文,,0,0,0,,then I'm gonna pack up,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.55,1:04:43.15,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go back to Memphis.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.79,1:04:49.15,英文,,0,0,0,,So this is how the uninsured die.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.75,1:04:52.19,英文,,0,0,0,,In a society filled with brilliant doctors
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.26,1:04:54.19,英文,,0,0,0,,and state-of-the-art technology,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.26,1:04:57.90,英文,,0,0,0,,it's obscene to let this boy just wither away and die.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.96,1:04:59.86,英文,,0,0,0,,He was covered by an insurance policy
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.93,1:05:02.23,英文,,0,0,0,,that his mother paid good money for.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.30,1:05:05.24,英文,,0,0,0,,It wasn't big money, but it was good money.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.30,1:05:07.21,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm alone in this trial.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.95,1:05:10.68,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm seriously outgunned, and I'm scared,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.74,1:05:12.38,英文,,0,0,0,,but I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.02,1:05:15.75,英文,,0,0,0,,I sit here with this poor suffering kid,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.17,1:05:18.05,英文,,0,0,0,,and I swear revenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.83,1:05:30.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.80,1:05:32.23,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.30,1:05:33.76,英文,,0,0,0,,What's... what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.80,1:05:36.27,英文,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.33,1:05:38.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.30,1:05:39.74,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm at the store.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.80,1:05:42.26,英文,,0,0,0,,OK, um, don't move, OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.35,1:05:43.27,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.34,1:05:44.54,英文,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.96,1:06:01.09,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.86,1:06:06.66,英文,,0,0,0,,She's in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.37,1:06:14.50,英文,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.37,1:06:26.57,英文,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.71,1:06:28.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's show him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.64,1:06:46.84,英文,,0,0,0,,I got you. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.94,1:06:50.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rudy, I'm so glad you called.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.38,1:06:51.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Come. Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.88,1:06:53.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, you poor child.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.88,1:06:55.77,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take care of you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.91,1:06:57.98,英文,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.05,1:07:00.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry. We'll manage just fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.08,1:07:02.48,英文,,0,0,0,,All right. You know where I'll be if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.62,1:07:04.08,英文,,0,0,0,,I do. I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.11,1:07:07.33,英文,,0,0,0,,I tell myself I'll do whatever I have to do
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.51,1:07:08.88,英文,,0,0,0,,to get her out of this
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.06,1:07:11.64,英文,,0,0,0,,because this guy's never gonna stop until he's killed her.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.08,1:07:13.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.40,1:07:36.07,英文,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.07,1:07:39.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Now it's a wrongful death suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.91,1:07:41.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Gazillions.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.28,1:07:42.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Deck...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.45,1:07:51.42,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Dot.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.10,1:08:43.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.51,1:08:45.07,英文,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.22,1:09:16.69,英文,,0,0,0,,It'll be OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.46,1:09:24.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.52,1:09:32.80,英文,,0,0,0,,For bugs?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.58,1:09:56.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.91,1:09:58.18,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.25,1:09:59.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your meal.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.05,1:10:02.57,英文,,0,0,0,,This bugging device has got...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.55,1:10:05.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Medium-grade circuitry.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.59,1:10:09.72,英文,,0,0,0,,It's a weak transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.89,1:10:14.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Probably manufactured in Czechoslovakia.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.08,1:10:18.48,英文,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think the cops or the feds would place this.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.90,1:10:23.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Somebody else is listening.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.07,1:10:25.54,英文,,0,0,0,,Who else would be listening to us?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.57,1:10:28.74,英文,,0,0,0,,I got a pretty good idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.75,1:10:33.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.13,1:10:34.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.15,1:10:36.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Just checking in.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.08,1:10:38.13,英文,,0,0,0,,- You need anything from downtown? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.12,1:10:41.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, guess what. Guess who wants to settle.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.12,1:10:42.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.29,1:10:43.72,英文,,0,0,0,,Dot Black.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.79,1:10:45.43,英文,,0,0,0,,Dot Black?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.49,1:10:47.06,英文,,0,0,0,,I went by there today,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.13,1:10:48.66,英文,,0,0,0,,and, uh, check up on her.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.71,1:10:50.53,英文,,0,0,0,,I brought her a fruitcake.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.60,1:10:53.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and she said she just doesn't have the willpower
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.60,1:10:56.07,英文,,0,0,0,,to stand a long trial
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.14,1:10:57.04,英文,,0,0,0,,and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.11,1:10:58.04,英文,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.11,1:10:59.97,英文,,0,0,0,,She said she'd take 17.5.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.04,1:11:01.74,英文,,0,0,0,,I think we should take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.81,1:11:04.44,英文,,0,0,0,,We'll sleep on it. I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.66,1:11:05.77,英文,,0,0,0,,All right, but I say you take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.98,1:11:07.72,英文,,0,0,0,,I know. I heard you. I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.78,1:11:08.66,英文,,0,0,0,,All right. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.95,1:11:11.09,英文,,0,0,0,,Hah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.15,1:11:13.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Son...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.49,1:11:16.72,英文,,0,0,0,,This family's been through a hell of a lot,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.79,1:11:19.69,英文,,0,0,0,,and I feel this woman wants to settle.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.53,1:11:22.63,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.08,1:11:26.28,英文,,0,0,0,,You go ahead and call her.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.35,1:11:28.55,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll wait here one while.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.62,1:11:30.75,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll get back to you, Mr. Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.82,1:11:32.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.32,1:11:45.75,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about the boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.32,1:11:49.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Listen, my client, uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.42,1:11:50.71,英文,,0,0,0,,wants to settle, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.36,1:11:52.76,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's say, Rudy,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.83,1:11:55.26,英文,,0,0,0,,just for the sake of putting the numbers on the board,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.33,1:11:56.80,英文,,0,0,0,,that if the claim was covered
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.86,1:11:59.77,英文,,0,0,0,,that my client should have paid out somewhere
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.83,1:12:02.50,英文,,0,0,0,,around 150-175,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.37,1:12:05.01,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.42,1:12:06.87,英文,,0,0,0,,They bugged our phones.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.94,1:12:09.81,英文,,0,0,0,,I do say so. And, uh, we will offer...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.88,1:12:12.93,英文,,0,0,0,,Guess we should tell Judge Kipler.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.68,1:12:15.32,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.77,1:12:16.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.75,1:12:21.29,英文,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.52,1:12:25.51,英文,,0,0,0,,A kind of a crazy idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.60,1:12:27.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Jury tampering.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.40,1:12:28.70,英文,,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.70,1:12:31.30,英文,,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.00,1:12:33.64,英文,,0,0,0,,Who's our biggest nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.60,1:12:36.30,英文,,0,0,0,,The judge gave us the names
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.37,1:12:38.31,英文,,0,0,0,,of 92 potential jurors.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.88,1:12:40.37,英文,,0,0,0,,We investigated their backgrounds,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.44,1:12:42.64,英文,,0,0,0,,and we rated them with plus or minus numbers.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.71,1:12:44.35,英文,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.41,1:12:45.81,英文,,0,0,0,,- All right. Here we go. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.00,1:12:48.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Any direct contact would of course be a serious offense.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.68,1:12:50.62,英文,,0,0,0,,What are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.84,1:12:52.17,英文,,0,0,0,,We're gonna do this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.22,1:12:54.15,英文,,0,0,0,,- Just do what I say. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.76,1:12:59.83,英文,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.95,1:13:02.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh, Rudy Baylor, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.51,1:13:04.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, this is Rudy Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.31,1:13:07.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, this is Billy Porter.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.42,1:13:09.17,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, you stopped by the shop today.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.24,1:13:10.47,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes. Mr. Porter.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.81,1:13:12.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for calling back.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.20,1:13:14.84,英文,,0,0,0,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.28,1:13:17.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes, well, it's about the trial.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.68,1:13:19.42,英文,,0,0,0,,You know, the one you got a jury summons for.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.60,1:13:20.75,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm one of the lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.93,1:13:23.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Is... is this legal?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.08,1:13:25.87,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, of course it's legal, Mr. Porter.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.94,1:13:28.07,英文,,0,0,0,,Just don't go telling anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.53,1:13:31.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Look, I represent this lady whose son died of leukemia
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.22,1:13:34.04,英文,,0,0,0,,because the Great Benefit insurance company
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.22,1:13:36.44,英文,,0,0,0,,wouldn't give them the money they needed for an operation.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.28,1:13:39.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, why, that sounds awful.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.95,1:13:42.20,英文,,0,0,0,,You know, I had an aunt that had that same disease.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.27,1:13:45.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Kept wasting away and my Uncle cried and...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.44,1:13:50.04,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.11,1:13:50.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.97,1:13:53.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, thank you, Mr. Porter. You have a fine afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.61,1:13:55.32,英文,,0,0,0,,Bye. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.38,1:13:57.42,英文,,0,0,0,,What... what... what about the aunt?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.60,1:13:58.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Where'd the aunt come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.97,1:13:59.89,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.96,1:14:01.39,英文,,0,0,0,,You told me to be sympathetic.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.46,1:14:03.42,英文,,0,0,0,,I know but you don't have to don't elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.00,1:14:05.39,英文,,0,0,0,,Get your coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.46,1:14:06.96,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's go back up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.16,1:14:09.93,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.00,1:14:10.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.97,1:14:12.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.50,1:14:16.14,英文,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.53,1:14:18.17,英文,,0,0,0,,what I'm about to ask
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.77,1:14:21.64,英文,,0,0,0,,is the most important question of the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.48,1:14:23.94,英文,,0,0,0,,It's a simple question.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.01,1:14:25.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Can be answered yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.66,1:14:28.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.85,1:14:32.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Have any of y'all been contacted about this case?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.46,1:14:36.97,英文,,0,0,0,,This is serious business.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.04,1:14:38.94,英文,,0,0,0,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.01,1:14:41.06,英文,,0,0,0,,We need to know now.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.68,1:14:44.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Let me ask it another way.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.45,1:14:49.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Did any of you have a conversation recently
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.64,1:14:51.89,英文,,0,0,0,,with either Mr. Rudy Baylor
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.96,1:14:54.22,英文,,0,0,0,,or directly behind him, Mr. Deck Schifflet.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.31,1:14:55.63,英文,,0,0,0,,Objection, your honor!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.69,1:14:56.93,英文,,0,0,0,,This is an outrage!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.00,1:14:58.60,英文,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Mr. Drummond?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.15,1:15:00.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.35,1:15:01.70,英文,,0,0,0,,we have reason to believe
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.82,1:15:03.28,英文,,0,0,0,,that this panel has been tampered with.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.42,1:15:05.07,英文,,0,0,0,,And he's accusing me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.68,1:15:07.86,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you're doing, Mr. Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.08,1:15:09.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, neither do I, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.51,1:15:10.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.51,1:15:12.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Approach the bench, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.33,1:15:18.43,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor, this panel's been tampered with.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.50,1:15:19.60,英文,,0,0,0,,I want proof, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.82,1:15:22.47,英文,,0,0,0,,I can't say without divulging
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.54,1:15:24.20,英文,,0,0,0,,confidential information, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.27,1:15:25.31,英文,,0,0,0,,You are just out of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.37,1:15:26.94,英文,,0,0,0,,You are acting rather bizarrely.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.01,1:15:28.28,英文,,0,0,0,,- I'm gonna prove it. - How?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.05,1:15:31.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Accuse us of something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.01,1:15:33.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Tamper. I...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.38,1:15:34.92,英文,,0,0,0,,it's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.98,1:15:36.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Just allow me to finish questioning the panel.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.02,1:15:38.62,英文,,0,0,0,,I think the truth will come forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.69,1:15:40.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Any objection, Mr. Baylor?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.29,1:15:42.66,英文,,0,0,0,,No, no objection.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.80,1:15:44.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Very well. Proceed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.33,1:15:46.49,英文,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.83,1:15:51.02,英文,,0,0,0,,What in the Sam hill is going on up there?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.68,1:15:53.64,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just lawyer stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.04,1:15:56.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Porter.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.46,1:16:00.40,英文,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you a direct question.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.64,1:16:03.24,英文,,0,0,0,,And I'd appreciate
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.73,1:16:05.11,英文,,0,0,0,,an honest response.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.35,1:16:08.17,英文,,0,0,0,,You ask an honest question,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.62,1:16:09.83,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll give you an honest answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.13,1:16:11.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.14,1:16:14.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Did you, Mr. Porter, or did you not
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.27,1:16:16.44,英文,,0,0,0,,have a phone conversation a few days ago
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.51,1:16:17.87,英文,,0,0,0,,with Mr. Rudy Baylor?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.94,1:16:19.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Hell, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.31,1:16:22.17,英文,,0,0,0,,I thought you were gonna give me an honest answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.68,1:16:24.26,英文,,0,0,0,,I gave you an honest answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.35,1:16:26.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Mr. Porter?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.15,1:16:28.80,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm damn sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.06,1:16:30.07,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Porter,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.14,1:16:31.15,英文,,0,0,0,,in a courthouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.57,1:16:33.27,英文,,0,0,0,,In a courthouse in the United States,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.34,1:16:35.61,英文,,0,0,0,,in a courthouse of justice, state of Tennessee,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.68,1:16:37.55,英文,,0,0,0,,I say you did not provide an honest answer!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.64,1:16:39.23,英文,,0,0,0,,Don't call me a liar.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.30,1:16:40.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.48,1:16:42.00,英文,,0,0,0,,You son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.55,1:16:46.09,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, get off him!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.15,1:16:47.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Order in the court!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.42,1:16:50.89,英文,,0,0,0,,Bailiff,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.96,1:16:52.83,英文,,0,0,0,,remove Mr. Porter from this courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.89,1:16:56.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Billy Porter, you are excused from the jury.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.85,1:17:00.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.51,1:17:03.82,英文,,0,0,0,,I move to dismiss the entire panel, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.99,1:17:07.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Denied.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.24,1:17:08.71,英文,,0,0,0,,It's been tainted.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.18,1:17:17.48,英文,,0,0,0,,You, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.55,1:17:21.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Your shoe, you left it...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.29,1:17:25.86,英文,,0,0,0,,Are we ready to proceed now
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.93,1:17:28.53,英文,,0,0,0,,with the jury selection, Mr. Drummond?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.68,1:17:32.23,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to proceed, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.30,1:17:34.67,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.64,1:17:59.61,英文,,0,0,0,,We'll file it today.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.68,1:18:00.78,英文,,0,0,0,,He'll go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.85,1:18:01.85,英文,,0,0,0,,He already is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.75,1:18:04.85,英文,,0,0,0,,He'll come after you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.28,1:18:06.48,英文,,0,0,0,,I hope he does.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.15,1:18:08.97,英文,,0,0,0,,This is that good processed Turkey.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.37,1:18:13.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I gotta get back to court.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.28,1:18:15.14,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm late. I gotta get back to court.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.68,1:18:17.02,英文,,0,0,0,,What about your sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.20,1:18:19.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was gonna take that with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.73,1:18:21.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.02,1:18:23.35,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.42,1:18:25.18,英文,,0,0,0,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.90,1:18:35.46,英文,,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.35,1:18:38.75,英文,,0,0,0,,I served the papers on Cliff when he was on his way to lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.20,1:18:41.28,英文,,0,0,0,,He didn't take it too well,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.64,1:18:42.75,英文,,0,0,0,,but I said I was ready to rumble.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.88,1:18:43.64,英文,,0,0,0,,He backed down.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.95,1:18:46.87,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, man, you better watch your back.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.28,1:18:50.35,英文,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.66,1:18:52.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Butch. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.75,1:18:54.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you solemnly swear
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.06,1:18:57.32,英文,,0,0,0,,that the testimony you're about to give in this cause
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.39,1:18:58.42,英文,,0,0,0,,will be the truth, the whole truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.49,1:19:00.39,英文,,0,0,0,,and nothing but the truth, so help you, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.46,1:19:01.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.76,1:19:03.64,英文,,0,0,0,,You may take the stand.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.65,1:19:12.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Please state your name for the record.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.68,1:19:16.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Margarine Black.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.45,1:19:19.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, Mrs. Black,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.12,1:19:21.36,英文,,0,0,0,,you are the mother of Donny Ray Black,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.43,1:19:23.69,英文,,0,0,0,,who recently died of acute myelocytic leukemia
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.76,1:19:24.93,英文,,0,0,0,,because the defendant, Great Benefit...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.00,1:19:26.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Objection.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.40,1:19:27.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Leading.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.60,1:19:31.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Sustained.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.12,1:19:35.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Your son,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.55,1:19:38.08,英文,,0,0,0,,- Donny Ray, needed an operation. - Objection.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.43,1:19:39.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Leading.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.17,1:19:41.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Sustained.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.73,1:19:46.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Black, did you purchase this medical policy
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.40,1:19:48.72,英文,,0,0,0,,because you were concerned about medical care for your son?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.79,1:19:49.72,英文,,0,0,0,,Objection.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.79,1:19:50.93,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.22,1:19:52.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Leading.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.62,1:19:54.79,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Baylor,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.20,1:19:56.59,英文,,0,0,0,,why don't you show the policy
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.66,1:19:57.95,英文,,0,0,0,,and ask her why she bought it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.17,1:19:58.84,英文,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.66,1:20:04.17,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.62,1:20:06.97,英文,,0,0,0,,You must ask to approach the witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.73,1:20:09.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Sorry, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.66,1:20:12.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Permission to approach the witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.68,1:20:13.94,英文,,0,0,0,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.31,1:20:19.50,英文,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.57,1:20:22.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.27,1:20:25.47,英文,,0,0,0,,Great Benefit. July 7, 1996.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.54,1:20:34.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Policy 7849909886.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.15,1:20:36.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Dear Mrs. Black,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.48,1:20:38.65,英文,,0,0,0,,on 7 prior occasions
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.72,1:20:42.52,英文,,0,0,0,,this company has denied your claim in writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.59,1:20:48.16,英文,,0,0,0,,We now deny it for the eighth and final time.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.23,1:20:53.27,英文,,0,0,0,,You must be stupid, stupid, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.77,1:20:57.14,英文,,0,0,0,,Sincerely Everett Lufkin,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.20,1:20:59.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Vice President, Claims Department."
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.59,1:21:03.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Read it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.76,1:21:04.89,英文,,0,0,0,,Objection.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.96,1:21:06.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Repetitious, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.40,1:21:07.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Sustained.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.51,1:21:10.71,英文,,0,0,0,,I tender the witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.86,1:21:13.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.10,1:21:14.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.17,1:21:17.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Please remove that exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.15,1:21:20.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, Mrs. Black.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.02,1:21:25.25,英文,,0,0,0,,Turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.97,1:21:31.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Black, why did you sue Great Benefit
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.91,1:21:33.28,英文,,0,0,0,,for $10 million?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.78,1:21:35.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.55,1:21:38.80,英文,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.68,1:21:41.20,英文,,0,0,0,,I thought it was more than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.62,1:21:42.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.71,1:21:45.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes. Your client has about a billion dollars,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.06,1:21:47.46,英文,,0,0,0,,and your client killed my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.69,1:21:50.04,英文,,0,0,0,,I wanted to sue for a whole lot more.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.35,1:21:54.88,英文,,0,0,0,,What would you do with the money?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.11,1:21:57.05,英文,,0,0,0,,If this jury awards you $10 million,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.11,1:21:58.55,英文,,0,0,0,,what you gonna do with the money?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.62,1:22:01.55,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna give it to the American leukemia society.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.55,1:22:03.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Every cent.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.68,1:22:08.31,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't want a dime of your stinking money.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.46,1:22:12.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Realize you are under oath, Mrs. Black.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.86,1:22:15.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Approach the witness, your honor?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.35,1:22:16.04,英文,,0,0,0,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.35,1:22:19.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Black, I want you to read from the policy.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.74,1:22:23.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Page 16, section "K," paragraph 14, item "E,"
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.08,1:22:25.38,英文,,0,0,0,,in which the insurance company
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.44,1:22:27.01,英文,,0,0,0,,has in plain English wording said
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.08,1:22:30.00,英文,,0,0,0,,that it will not pay for experimental procedures.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.37,1:22:33.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, your lawsuit says
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.42,1:22:35.52,英文,,0,0,0,,that your son would have been saved if he had had
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.59,1:22:36.92,英文,,0,0,0,,a bone marrow transplant.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.99,1:22:38.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a fact, Mrs. Black,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.06,1:22:40.46,英文,,0,0,0,,that there are only 7,000
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.52,1:22:42.61,英文,,0,0,0,,bone marrow transplants performed a year in the United States?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.08,1:22:45.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Less than 200 in the state of Tennessee?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.75,1:22:46.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Objection, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.98,1:22:48.18,英文,,0,0,0,,He's leading the witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.25,1:22:50.68,英文,,0,0,0,,This is cross-examination. Leading is allowed.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.28,1:22:52.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Overruled,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.62,1:22:54.52,英文,,0,0,0,,as to leading.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.59,1:22:59.03,英文,,0,0,0,,So it was not covered by the policy.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.09,1:23:00.09,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, Mrs. Black,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.16,1:23:02.90,英文,,0,0,0,,who was it, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.96,1:23:06.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Who was it first diagnosed your son's condition?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.52,1:23:09.45,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, at the very beginning,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.22,1:23:12.31,英文,,0,0,0,,our doctor, Dr. page.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.06,1:23:15.43,英文,,0,0,0,,That would be your family physician?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.73,1:23:17.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, it would.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.19,1:23:18.59,英文,,0,0,0,,Is he a good doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.66,1:23:20.36,英文,,0,0,0,,He's a very good doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.37,1:23:22.93,英文,,0,0,0,,And is it not true, Mrs. Black,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.00,1:23:24.43,英文,,0,0,0,,that this capable, truthful man
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.50,1:23:28.39,英文,,0,0,0,,told you repeatedly that a bone marrow transplant
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.46,1:23:29.49,英文,,0,0,0,,would do your son no good
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.56,1:23:32.66,英文,,0,0,0,,because of the type of leukemia he had?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.93,1:23:35.70,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.76,1:23:37.08,英文,,0,0,0,,No, he did not.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.15,1:23:38.11,英文,,0,0,0,,He didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.18,1:23:40.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Not like that, to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.25,1:23:43.42,英文,,0,0,0,,Approach the witness, your honor?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.49,1:23:44.26,英文,,0,0,0,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.32,1:23:50.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Black, is this not Dr. page's letterhead?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.73,1:23:53.73,英文,,0,0,0,,And at the bottom there, is that not his signature?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.80,1:23:55.57,英文,,0,0,0,,He can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.63,1:23:57.03,英文,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.10,1:23:58.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Because he can't introduce evidence
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.17,1:24:00.08,英文,,0,0,0,,that way. Plus it's hearsay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.47,1:24:02.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Objection, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.37,1:24:06.28,英文,,0,0,0,,A... a letter from... from the Blacks' family physician
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.34,1:24:08.41,英文,,0,0,0,,to Mr. Drummond is inadmissible.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.48,1:24:10.38,英文,,0,0,0,,That is quite correct, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.45,1:24:12.28,英文,,0,0,0,,And I'm not asking for this letter
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.35,1:24:13.75,英文,,0,0,0,,to be admitted into evidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.82,1:24:16.22,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm simply asking that this witness
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.52,1:24:17.59,英文,,0,0,0,,be allowed to read the letter
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.65,1:24:19.39,英文,,0,0,0,,under rule 612 of the Tennessee
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.46,1:24:20.72,英文,,0,0,0,,rules of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.79,1:24:22.59,英文,,0,0,0,,So her recollection can be refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.66,1:24:25.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Baylor, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.16,1:24:26.73,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't know, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.80,1:24:27.93,英文,,0,0,0,,I just object to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.00,1:24:31.77,英文,,0,0,0,,And also we were not furnished this letter
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.84,1:24:33.24,英文,,0,0,0,,in pre-trial discovery.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.30,1:24:35.77,英文,,0,0,0,,What do you say to that, Mr. Drummond?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.84,1:24:37.57,英文,,0,0,0,,I had no idea this letter would be needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.64,1:24:39.33,英文,,0,0,0,,I expected this lady to tell the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.39,1:24:41.03,英文,,0,0,0,,about what her doctor told her.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.05,1:24:45.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Anything else, Mr. Baylor?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.28,1:24:48.82,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.89,1:24:52.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Drummond,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.12,1:24:54.79,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna give you a little latitude,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.86,1:24:56.86,英文,,0,0,0,,but don't stray too far.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.93,1:24:58.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Very well, your honor. Now, Mrs. Black,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.18,1:25:01.75,英文,,0,0,0,,does that letter refresh your recollection
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.82,1:25:04.05,英文,,0,0,0,,as to whether or not Donny Ray's leukemia
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.12,1:25:05.42,英文,,0,0,0,,was the kind that could be helped
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.49,1:25:06.65,英文,,0,0,0,,with a bone marrow transplant?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.72,1:25:08.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, see, now, he is not a specialist.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.93,1:25:10.04,英文,,0,0,0,,But he is a licensed,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.09,1:25:13.49,英文,,0,0,0,,experienced, capable physician
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.56,1:25:16.18,英文,,0,0,0,,who lovingly told you time and time again
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.25,1:25:19.45,英文,,0,0,0,,what you quite understandably did not want to accept:
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.52,1:25:22.35,英文,,0,0,0,,That your son was going to die of leukemia
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.42,1:25:25.22,英文,,0,0,0,,despite the best efforts of medical science.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.29,1:25:26.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Is that not true?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.72,1:25:29.29,英文,,0,0,0,,But he wasn't a specialist.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.36,1:25:30.76,英文,,0,0,0,,I didn't believe him.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.83,1:25:33.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Not only did you not believe him, ma'am,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.96,1:25:35.58,英文,,0,0,0,,but you were less than truthful with me
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.65,1:25:37.72,英文,,0,0,0,,and with this jury moments ago
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.79,1:25:39.24,英文,,0,0,0,,when you told us under oath
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.30,1:25:42.31,英文,,0,0,0,,that Dr. page never said that your son
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.37,1:25:44.56,英文,,0,0,0,,had the type of leukemia that could not be treated
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.63,1:25:46.03,英文,,0,0,0,,by a bone marrow transplant.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.09,1:25:48.16,英文,,0,0,0,,I believe your exact words were,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.23,1:25:50.40,英文,,0,0,0,,he never said that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.46,1:25:51.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Not like that
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.67,1:25:53.43,英文,,0,0,0,,to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.50,1:25:55.82,英文,,0,0,0,,He wasn't a specialist.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.47,1:25:58.77,英文,,0,0,0,,I just wanted Donny Ray
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.84,1:26:02.45,英文,,0,0,0,,to have the best medical treatment available.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.02,1:26:06.11,英文,,0,0,0,,You'd do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.70,1:26:08.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Of course, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.48,1:26:11.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.94,1:26:13.25,英文,,0,0,0,,That'll be all.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.97,1:26:17.14,英文,,0,0,0,,You may step down, Mrs. Black.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.00,1:26:27.78,英文,,0,0,0,,I didn't do very good, did I?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.85,1:26:29.94,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, you did fine. You did fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.62,1:26:31.82,英文,,0,0,0,,It's all right. The jury can see
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.88,1:26:34.22,英文,,0,0,0,,exactly what he's up to.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.28,1:26:35.82,英文,,0,0,0,,The jury can see what he's up to.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.93,1:26:36.89,英文,,0,0,0,,I need a smoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.96,1:26:37.86,英文,,0,0,0,,I know you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.93,1:26:38.76,英文,,0,0,0,,We're gonna get to that later.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.45,1:26:44.80,英文,,0,0,0,,I hope he hasn't changed the locks.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.00,1:26:47.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.60,1:26:49.12,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.22,1:26:52.99,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.75,1:27:21.55,英文,,0,0,0,,What a pig.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.42,1:27:23.62,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.69,1:27:26.43,英文,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Kelly. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.85,1:27:31.56,英文,,0,0,0,,There's more of my stuff in the closet.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.01,1:27:42.51,英文,,0,0,0,,You can't take everything, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.89,1:28:00.03,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.89,1:28:03.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, hello!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.46,1:28:05.06,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.90,1:28:07.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.87,1:28:10.44,英文,,0,0,0,,What do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.50,1:28:12.34,英文,,0,0,0,,What you two been doing in here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.41,1:28:14.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, take it easy, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.29,1:28:14.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.37,1:28:16.45,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm your husband. Remember that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.45,1:28:17.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, Buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.11,1:28:18.01,英文,,0,0,0,,You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.48,1:28:19.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen, Buddy, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.86,1:28:20.80,英文,,0,0,0,,I ain't listening to nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.86,1:28:22.67,英文,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.08,1:28:24.34,英文,,0,0,0,,You hurt me, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.51,1:28:25.87,英文,,0,0,0,,You hurt me so bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.00,1:28:28.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this to me?!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.44,1:28:30.57,英文,,0,0,0,,No, Cliff!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.15,1:28:36.70,英文,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.43,1:29:11.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy, Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.16,1:29:12.16,英文,,0,0,0,,Cliff!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.23,1:29:13.30,英文,,0,0,0,,You idiot, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.37,1:29:14.47,英文,,0,0,0,,You see what you did?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.53,1:29:15.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Kelly!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.02,1:29:17.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Is this what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.02,1:29:19.16,英文,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.22,1:29:21.26,英文,,0,0,0,,I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.94,1:29:35.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.18,1:29:42.75,英文,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.81,1:29:44.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.32,1:29:48.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Give me the bat and leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.60,1:29:50.30,英文,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.82,1:29:54.16,英文,,0,0,0,,Give me the bat and leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.22,1:29:56.83,英文,,0,0,0,,You were not here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.89,1:29:58.83,英文,,0,0,0,,Give me the bat.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.18,1:30:14.14,英文,,0,0,0,,Go, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.21,1:30:16.38,英文,,0,0,0,,You were not here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.28,1:30:55.18,英文,,0,0,0,,He's finally killed her.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.25,1:30:57.19,英文,,0,0,0,,No, it's him. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.25,1:30:58.29,英文,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.36,1:30:59.32,英文,,0,0,0,,Just saw her.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.39,1:31:00.56,英文,,0,0,0,,How'd it happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.62,1:31:01.62,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.69,1:31:03.39,英文,,0,0,0,,They say when you commit a murder,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.46,1:31:04.76,英文,,0,0,0,,you make at least 25 mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.83,1:31:07.96,英文,,0,0,0,,and later you're lucky if you remember 5 of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.03,1:31:09.10,英文,,0,0,0,,It was self-defense,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.17,1:31:11.20,英文,,0,0,0,,but I can't get past the fact that he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.27,1:31:13.70,英文,,0,0,0,,And the mistakes are piling up in my mind so fast
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.77,1:31:15.51,英文,,0,0,0,,I can't think.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.24,1:31:18.44,英文,,0,0,0,,But Kelly knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.51,1:31:20.08,英文,,0,0,0,,She knew what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.14,1:31:21.68,英文,,0,0,0,,She knew it was time.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.37,1:31:24.55,英文,,0,0,0,,With everything that was happening
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.62,1:31:26.38,英文,,0,0,0,,and all that was at stake,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.45,1:31:28.85,英文,,0,0,0,,her first thought was for my safety.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.24,1:31:33.16,英文,,0,0,0,,And I left her in there all alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.59,1:31:36.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.44,1:31:37.64,英文,,0,0,0,,God damn you, Kelly!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.71,1:31:39.38,英文,,0,0,0,,What the hell's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.45,1:31:41.45,英文,,0,0,0,,What the hell did you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.86,1:31:50.49,英文,,0,0,0,,You killed my son!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.56,1:31:51.72,英文,,0,0,0,,God damn you!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.63,1:32:29.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'm her lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.18,1:32:32.15,英文,,0,0,0,,I insist on being here while she's being questioned.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.22,1:32:33.62,英文,,0,0,0,,This is your attorney?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.68,1:32:35.32,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.15,1:32:40.09,英文,,0,0,0,,I want her released to my custody.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.16,1:32:41.32,英文,,0,0,0,,I can't do that
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.39,1:32:43.29,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't know what kind of lawyer you are,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.36,1:32:44.86,英文,,0,0,0,,but we got a dead body here,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.93,1:32:47.80,英文,,0,0,0,,and bond needs to be set by a judge.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.86,1:32:49.40,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm going to jail?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.47,1:32:52.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, can we arrange for a private cell?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.07,1:32:54.30,英文,,0,0,0,,Look, asshole, I don't run the jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.37,1:32:56.34,英文,,0,0,0,,You got a better way of doing things,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.41,1:32:58.54,英文,,0,0,0,,then you need to talk to the jailer.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.61,1:33:00.84,英文,,0,0,0,,They love lawyers down there, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.05,1:33:03.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.45,1:33:05.33,英文,,0,0,0,,If your lawyer here is worth his salt,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.40,1:33:06.83,英文,,0,0,0,,you'll be out of here
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.90,1:33:09.15,英文,,0,0,0,,sometime tomorrow if you can post bond, OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.65,1:33:12.96,英文,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.21,1:33:18.97,英文,,0,0,0,,- You got 5. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.22,1:33:27.97,英文,,0,0,0,,They're watching us through that window there,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.91,1:33:31.37,英文,,0,0,0,,and this room is probably bugged,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.48,1:33:33.65,英文,,0,0,0,,so just be careful what you say.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.91,1:33:35.74,英文,,0,0,0,,What does "manslaughter" mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.81,1:33:38.68,英文,,0,0,0,,It's just murder without the element of intent.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.75,1:33:40.62,英文,,0,0,0,,How much time could I get?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.68,1:33:42.22,英文,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, you have to be convicted first.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.29,1:33:44.05,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.60,1:33:47.72,英文,,0,0,0,,That's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.97,1:33:53.65,英文,,0,0,0,,Cross your wrists behind you please, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.64,1:34:01.67,英文,,0,0,0,,This way, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.55,1:34:10.45,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lufkin,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.51,1:34:13.25,英文,,0,0,0,,you are the Vice President of Claims at Great Benefit, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.48,1:34:14.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.59,1:34:15.77,英文,,0,0,0,,Approach the witness, your honor?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.82,1:34:17.09,英文,,0,0,0,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.01,1:34:20.51,英文,,0,0,0,,You recognize this?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.49,1:34:22.63,英文,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.42,1:34:27.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Read that to the jury.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.60,1:34:30.70,英文,,0,0,0,,Dear Mrs. Black,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.77,1:34:32.10,英文,,0,0,0,,on 7 prior occasions
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.17,1:34:34.04,英文,,0,0,0,,this company has denied your claim in writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.10,1:34:35.74,英文,,0,0,0,,We now deny it for the eighth and final time.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.81,1:34:37.87,英文,,0,0,0,,You must be stupid, stupid, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.94,1:34:39.61,英文,,0,0,0,,"Sincerely Everett Lufkin,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.68,1:34:41.49,英文,,0,0,0,,Vice President, Claims."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.56,1:34:42.80,英文,,0,0,0,,That's you?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.63,1:34:44.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.48,1:34:49.37,英文,,0,0,0,,How do you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.36,1:34:56.99,英文,,0,0,0,,It was a difficult time for me personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.06,1:34:59.60,英文,,0,0,0,,I was under a lot of stress.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.66,1:35:03.15,英文,,0,0,0,,We had denied this claim 7 times before.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.42,1:35:05.42,英文,,0,0,0,,I was trying to be emphatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.89,1:35:07.49,英文,,0,0,0,,I snapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.55,1:35:09.09,英文,,0,0,0,,I regret having written the letter,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.16,1:35:11.20,英文,,0,0,0,,and I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.00,1:35:14.34,英文,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a little late for an apology?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.98,1:35:17.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.78,1:35:18.75,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.82,1:35:20.85,英文,,0,0,0,,The boy is dead, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.22,1:35:25.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.89,1:35:28.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, Mr. Lufkin,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.88,1:35:31.18,英文,,0,0,0,,who is Jackie Lemancyzk?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.24,1:35:37.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Jackie Lemancyzk is a former claims handler.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.22,1:35:39.05,英文,,0,0,0,,And did she work in your department?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.25,1:35:40.05,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.91,1:35:43.08,英文,,0,0,0,,And when did she stop working for Great Benefit?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.94,1:35:46.09,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't remember the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.16,1:35:48.09,英文,,0,0,0,,How about October 30?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.16,1:35:49.63,英文,,0,0,0,,Sounds close.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.70,1:35:51.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that just 2 days before she was scheduled
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.02,1:35:53.88,英文,,0,0,0,,to give a deposition in this case?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.95,1:35:55.52,英文,,0,0,0,,I really don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.71,1:35:58.29,英文,,0,0,0,,I'd like to refresh the witness' recollection
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.35,1:36:01.09,英文,,0,0,0,,under rule 612.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.69,1:36:05.06,英文,,0,0,0,,October 30th.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.13,1:36:06.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Apparently.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.33,1:36:07.50,英文,,0,0,0,,And that was just 2 days before she was scheduled
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.56,1:36:09.42,英文,,0,0,0,,to give a deposition in this matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.54,1:36:09.88,英文,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.00,1:36:11.75,英文,,0,0,0,,And she was the person responsible
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.82,1:36:13.32,英文,,0,0,0,,for handling Donny Ray Black's claim,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.39,1:36:14.29,英文,,0,0,0,,was she not?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.40,1:36:16.16,英文,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.22,1:36:17.59,英文,,0,0,0,,And you fired her?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.56,1:36:21.25,英文,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.51,1:36:24.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, how'd you get rid of her?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.16,1:36:25.26,英文,,0,0,0,,She resigned.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.33,1:36:27.80,英文,,0,0,0,,It's right here in the letter you just gave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.87,1:36:29.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh. Why'd she resign?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.99,1:36:33.66,英文,,0,0,0,,"I hereby resign for personal reasons"
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.72,1:36:35.16,英文,,0,0,0,,so it was her idea
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.22,1:36:36.86,英文,,0,0,0,,to leave her job?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.08,1:36:38.39,英文,,0,0,0,,That's what it says.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.46,1:36:40.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Nothing further.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.62,1:36:42.28,英文,,0,0,0,,You may step down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.49,1:36:50.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.57,1:36:55.41,英文,,0,0,0,,Hi. I'm Jackie Lemancyzk's brother James.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.48,1:36:56.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Is it possible to see her?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.98,1:36:58.11,英文,,0,0,0,,- James Lemancyzk? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.48,1:37:01.25,英文,,0,0,0,,One minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.82,1:37:21.85,英文,,0,0,0,,All rise.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.51,1:37:26.45,英文,,0,0,0,,Let me explain, Miss Lemancyzk.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.99,1:37:28.93,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm really not your brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.05,1:37:35.65,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy. Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.72,1:37:38.39,英文,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to meet Jackie Lemancyzk.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.05,1:37:48.88,英文,,0,0,0,,This is Jackie Lemancyzk.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.95,1:37:52.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Where she goes, Carl goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.99,1:37:55.62,英文,,0,0,0,,This is my partner,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.69,1:37:57.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy S. Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.52,1:37:59.76,英文,,0,0,0,,Just tell him what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.83,1:38:01.25,英文,,0,0,0,,Miss Lemancyzk.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.93,1:38:03.70,英文,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.51,1:38:05.83,英文,,0,0,0,,Is it all right if I sit down?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.90,1:38:07.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.88,1:38:09.67,英文,,0,0,0,,All right, Miss Lemancyzk,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.97,1:38:12.45,英文,,0,0,0,,let's talk about the Black file.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.57,1:38:13.48,英文,,0,0,0,,It was assigned to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.94,1:38:15.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.88,1:38:19.02,英文,,0,0,0,,The initial claim from Mrs. Black was assigned to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.37,1:38:21.14,英文,,0,0,0,,Pursuant to company policy at the time,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.30,1:38:23.31,英文,,0,0,0,,I sent her a letter of denial.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.77,1:38:25.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.65,1:38:27.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.87,1:38:31.21,英文,,0,0,0,,Because all claims were initially denied.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.81,1:38:36.31,英文,,0,0,0,,All claims?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.38,1:38:38.95,英文,,0,0,0,,All claims.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.35,1:38:46.85,英文,,0,0,0,,OK, this is how it works.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.02,1:38:48.62,英文,,0,0,0,,The policy...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.73,1:38:52.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Is sold door to door in the poorer neighborhoods.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.00,1:38:55.88,英文,,0,0,0,,Paid in cash each week.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.25,1:39:02.15,英文,,0,0,0,,The claim comes in and is assigned to a handler.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.22,1:39:05.54,英文,,0,0,0,,That's basically a low level paper pusher.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.77,1:39:09.88,英文,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the handler reviews it
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.30,1:39:14.07,英文,,0,0,0,,and immediately sends a letter to the insured
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.13,1:39:15.23,英文,,0,0,0,,denying the claim.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.30,1:39:17.04,英文,,0,0,0,,The claims handler then sends the file over to underwriting.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.11,1:39:22.54,英文,,0,0,0,,Underwriting sends a memo back to claims
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.61,1:39:25.61,英文,,0,0,0,,saying, "don't pay this until you hear from us."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.81,1:39:28.21,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, what you should keep in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.28,1:39:31.02,英文,,0,0,0,,is that even though all these people work for this big company,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.18,1:39:32.42,英文,,0,0,0,,and they all work in the same building,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.49,1:39:33.60,英文,,0,0,0,,they don't know each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.82,1:39:36.59,英文,,0,0,0,,Nor do they know what the other department is up to.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.66,1:39:37.76,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, this is very intentional.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.82,1:39:40.03,英文,,0,0,0,,The departments are kept at war with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.09,1:39:42.19,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, meanwhile,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.26,1:39:45.20,英文,,0,0,0,,there's the client.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.50,1:39:49.47,英文,,0,0,0,,And they're getting all these letters.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.54,1:39:53.54,英文,,0,0,0,,Some from claims, some from underwriting,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.34,1:39:56.61,英文,,0,0,0,,and most people give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.21,1:40:01.91,英文,,0,0,0,,And this, of course, is...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.98,1:40:03.78,英文,,0,0,0,,Intended.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.18,1:40:17.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Your next witness, Mr. Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.98,1:40:21.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Plaintiff calls Jackie Lemancyzk.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.71,1:40:23.94,英文,,0,0,0,,What'd he say?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.67,1:40:29.78,英文,,0,0,0,,Objection, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.94,1:40:30.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Approach the bench?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.88,1:40:32.49,英文,,0,0,0,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.56,1:40:34.45,英文,,0,0,0,,This is a complete surprise, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.51,1:40:36.25,英文,,0,0,0,,Why? She's listed as a potential witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.32,1:40:37.60,英文,,0,0,0,,We have a right to be forewarned.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.77,1:40:38.91,英文,,0,0,0,,When did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.91,1:40:39.94,英文,,0,0,0,,I didn't know she was lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.17,1:40:41.44,英文,,0,0,0,,It's a fair question, Mr. Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.01,1:40:44.01,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, it's my first trial.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.07,1:40:45.31,英文,,0,0,0,,That's not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.77,1:40:47.63,英文,,0,0,0,,It is a matter of fairness, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.69,1:40:49.93,英文,,0,0,0,,We have a right to be notified about your witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.00,1:40:51.30,英文,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.36,1:40:52.77,英文,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me she can't testify?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.08,1:40:55.53,英文,,0,0,0,,She's listed in the pretrial order, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.60,1:40:58.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Pursuant to rule 26.06,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.40,1:41:00.51,英文,,0,0,0,,we have the right to call her as a witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.14,1:41:04.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Objection overruled.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.17,1:41:11.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Go memorize.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.26,1:41:25.94,英文,,0,0,0,,State your name for the record.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.37,1:41:28.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Jackie Lemancyzk.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.00,1:41:29.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Miss Lemancyzk,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.04,1:41:31.94,英文,,0,0,0,,how long did you work for Great Benefit?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.01,1:41:33.74,英文,,0,0,0,,6 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.81,1:41:35.54,英文,,0,0,0,,And when did your employment end?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.61,1:41:37.64,英文,,0,0,0,,October 30th.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.71,1:41:38.91,英文,,0,0,0,,How did it end?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.98,1:41:40.48,英文,,0,0,0,,I was fired.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.37,1:41:43.12,英文,,0,0,0,,You mean you did not resign?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.18,1:41:44.98,英文,,0,0,0,,No, I was fired.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.74,1:41:47.77,英文,,0,0,0,,Approach the witness, your honor?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.15,1:41:49.09,英文,,0,0,0,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.16,1:41:50.52,英文,,0,0,0,,I am baffled, Miss Lemancyzk,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.59,1:41:51.59,英文,,0,0,0,,because I have this letter here,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.66,1:41:54.56,英文,,0,0,0,,and it says you quit for personal reasons.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.63,1:41:55.93,英文,,0,0,0,,The letter is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.40,1:42:00.17,英文,,0,0,0,,I was fired so the company could claim
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.22,1:42:01.77,英文,,0,0,0,,that I no longer worked there.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.94,1:42:03.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Can you please point out the man in the courtroom
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.87,1:42:05.80,英文,,0,0,0,,who made you write this letter?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.60,1:42:14.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Jack Underhall.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.60,1:42:20.60,英文,,0,0,0,,He told me I was leaving immediately,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.67,1:42:22.67,英文,,0,0,0,,and I had 2 choices...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.74,1:42:25.24,英文,,0,0,0,,I could call it a firing and leave with nothing,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.31,1:42:27.28,英文,,0,0,0,,or I could write that letter,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.34,1:42:28.84,英文,,0,0,0,,call it a resignation,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.91,1:42:32.18,英文,,0,0,0,,and the company would give me $10,000 in cash
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.25,1:42:34.05,英文,,0,0,0,,to keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.15,1:42:38.48,英文,,0,0,0,,And I had to make that decision right there in his presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.69,1:42:44.86,英文,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.20,1:42:47.77,英文,,0,0,0,,I took the cash...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.63,1:42:52.48,英文,,0,0,0,,And I also signed a letter saying I would never discuss
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.53,1:42:54.27,英文,,0,0,0,,any of my claims files with anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.02,1:42:56.34,英文,,0,0,0,,Including the Black file?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.75,1:42:58.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Specifically the Black file.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.49,1:43:02.19,英文,,0,0,0,,So you knew that claim should have been paid?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.78,1:43:05.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Everybody knew...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.68,1:43:08.80,英文,,0,0,0,,But the company was playing the odds.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.65,1:43:11.45,英文,,0,0,0,,What odds?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.54,1:43:15.77,英文,,0,0,0,,The odds that the insured would not consult a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.33,1:43:26.47,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, during that time...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.67,1:43:31.15,英文,,0,0,0,,You were a senior claims examiner?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.11,1:43:33.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.38,1:43:35.71,英文,,0,0,0,,During that time, was there ever an occasion
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.78,1:43:36.91,英文,,0,0,0,,when you were given instructions
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.98,1:43:38.80,英文,,0,0,0,,regarding how you should handle claims?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.50,1:43:41.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Deny all claims for a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.44,1:43:43.99,英文,,0,0,0,,Add up the money saved,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.05,1:43:46.09,英文,,0,0,0,,deduct the amount spent on quick court settlements,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.44,1:43:47.77,英文,,0,0,0,,and there's a pot of gold left.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.62,1:43:49.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Approach the clerk, your honor?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.04,1:43:50.44,英文,,0,0,0,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.51,1:43:51.41,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.48,1:43:53.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Number 6, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.35,1:43:56.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Here's what has heretofore been marked
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.22,1:43:58.02,英文,,0,0,0,,defense exhibit number 6.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.99,1:44:00.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize this?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.69,1:44:03.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's a Great Benefits company claims manual.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.24,1:44:06.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Would you do me a favor
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.97,1:44:08.97,英文,,0,0,0,,and just flip over to section "U," please?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.83,1:44:16.00,英文,,0,0,0,,There is no section "U."
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.70,1:44:18.34,英文,,0,0,0,,But do you remember a section "U"
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.40,1:44:20.34,英文,,0,0,0,,when you were a senior claims examiner?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.37,1:44:22.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.24,1:44:26.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Section "U" was an executive memorandum
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.15,1:44:28.68,英文,,0,0,0,,in the senior examiners manual.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.75,1:44:29.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.38,1:44:31.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.32,1:44:35.75,英文,,0,0,0,,this is Jackie Lemancyzk's actual senior claims manual,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.82,1:44:37.56,英文,,0,0,0,,and within it, there is an executive memorandum
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.62,1:44:38.92,英文,,0,0,0,,entitled section "U."
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.99,1:44:39.99,英文,,0,0,0,,I ask that I might approach...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.06,1:44:41.95,英文,,0,0,0,,objection, your honor. Approach the bench?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.40,1:44:47.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor, we were not given a complete manual.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.17,1:44:48.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor, this document contains
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.47,1:44:50.60,英文,,0,0,0,,executive memoranda that are stolen work papers
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.67,1:44:52.00,英文,,0,0,0,,and may not be admitted.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.07,1:44:52.75,英文,,0,0,0,,May not be admitted?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.82,1:44:54.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Can you prove this, Leo?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.09,1:44:56.43,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor, I ask that you instruct my colleague here not to read from
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.56,1:44:59.78,英文,,0,0,0,,nor to make reference to any suspect...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.85,1:45:03.38,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't understand why this is not admissible.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.45,1:45:05.08,英文,,0,0,0,,It was not proffered at the correct time,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.15,1:45:06.29,英文,,0,0,0,,nor do we know how it was obtained...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.35,1:45:08.19,英文,,0,0,0,,I just found out about this last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.25,1:45:10.17,英文,,0,0,0,,Assuming that I can't get this in now,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.24,1:45:12.04,英文,,0,0,0,,do you have any more questions for the witness?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.88,1:45:13.84,英文,,0,0,0,,No, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.48,1:45:16.44,英文,,0,0,0,,You may cross-examine, Mr. Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.71,1:45:17.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.25,1:45:34.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Is it true, Miss Lemancyzk...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.80,1:45:38.22,英文,,0,0,0,,That you have recently been committed
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.50,1:45:40.44,英文,,0,0,0,,to an institution for various problems?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.06,1:45:42.64,英文,,0,0,0,,I was not committed.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.28,1:45:46.22,英文,,0,0,0,,I am suffering from alcoholism and depression,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.44,1:45:49.38,英文,,0,0,0,,and I voluntarily checked into a facility.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.04,1:45:53.55,英文,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to be covered by my group policy at Great Benefit,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.62,1:45:56.03,英文,,0,0,0,,and they, of course, are denying my claim.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.10,1:45:57.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Is that why you're here, Miss Lemancyzk?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.31,1:46:00.17,英文,,0,0,0,,Because you're angry with Great Benefit?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.47,1:46:01.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Miss Lemancyzk?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.64,1:46:03.51,英文,,0,0,0,,I hate Great Benefit
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.18,1:46:06.95,英文,,0,0,0,,and most of the worms that work there.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.60,1:46:09.32,英文,,0,0,0,,Did you feel Mr. Lufkin was a worm
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.32,1:46:10.95,英文,,0,0,0,,when you were sleeping with him?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.92,1:46:13.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Objection.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.09,1:46:15.29,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.36,1:46:17.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Drummond might find this fun to talk about,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.69,1:46:19.89,英文,,0,0,0,,but this is not relevant at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.96,1:46:21.83,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's no fun for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.48,1:46:23.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Overruled.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.55,1:46:24.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's see where this takes us.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.77,1:46:28.22,英文,,0,0,0,,You admit to having an affair with Mr. Lufkin?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.55,1:46:36.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Miss Lemancyzk?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.11,1:46:47.42,英文,,0,0,0,,As long as I had sex with certain executives at Great Benefit,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.02,1:46:53.64,英文,,0,0,0,,my pay was increased, and I was promoted.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.11,1:46:57.60,英文,,0,0,0,,When I stopped, I was demoted.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.64,1:46:58.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Miss Lemancyzk,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.98,1:47:00.82,英文,,0,0,0,,as an employee of Great Benefit,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.88,1:47:02.72,英文,,0,0,0,,you promised not to disclose
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.79,1:47:05.12,英文,,0,0,0,,confidential private claims information.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.19,1:47:06.62,英文,,0,0,0,,- Yes? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.06,1:47:10.35,英文,,0,0,0,,In fact, you testified that you sealed that promise
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.94,1:47:13.95,英文,,0,0,0,,by demand of payment for $10,000, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.01,1:47:16.26,英文,,0,0,0,,That payment was not my idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.31,1:47:17.52,英文,,0,0,0,,But you accepted it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.58,1:47:19.42,英文,,0,0,0,,You put it right in your pocketbook.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.95,1:47:21.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Even though in your mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.11,1:47:23.28,英文,,0,0,0,,you never intended to keep that promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.28,1:47:25.82,英文,,0,0,0,,In fact, you were very angry
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.04,1:47:28.13,英文,,0,0,0,,at Great Benefit and Mr. Lufkin, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.26,1:47:30.35,英文,,0,0,0,,You know, they preyed on me,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.48,1:47:34.17,英文,,0,0,0,,because I was broke, and I was single, and I had 2 kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.22,1:47:35.91,英文,,0,0,0,,So you told him you're gonna go to his wife,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.91,1:47:36.88,英文,,0,0,0,,go to the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.93,1:47:40.31,英文,,0,0,0,,And that $10,000, that was just a piece of blackmail, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.32,1:47:43.31,英文,,0,0,0,,A way to extort money from the company you hated!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.38,1:47:44.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.58,1:47:45.33,英文,,0,0,0,,No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.46,1:47:48.05,英文,,0,0,0,,In fact, your testimony here today is just a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.11,1:47:49.71,英文,,0,0,0,,You stole company work papers,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.91,1:47:53.05,英文,,0,0,0,,confidential reports as blackmail for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.64,1:47:57.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Hell hath no fury as what, Miss Lemancyzk?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.59,1:48:00.73,英文,,0,0,0,,A woman scorned!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.13,1:48:03.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor, I move that all documents
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.83,1:48:07.00,英文,,0,0,0,,provided the plaintiff by Miss Jackie Lemancyzk
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.33,1:48:08.93,英文,,0,0,0,,be deemed stolen work papers
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.00,1:48:10.84,英文,,0,0,0,,and struck from these proceedings.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.42,1:48:22.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Based on the evidence presently before the court,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.68,1:48:25.46,英文,,0,0,0,,these documents are inadmissible.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.19,1:48:31.72,英文,,0,0,0,,No further questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.79,1:48:33.39,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.46,1:48:35.19,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.53,1:48:39.70,英文,,0,0,0,,You may step down, Miss Lemancyzk.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.22,1:48:48.99,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.16,1:49:07.42,英文,,0,0,0,,- Hello. - Hi. This is Deck Schifflet.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.60,1:49:09.24,英文,,0,0,0,,I need to speak to big rhino. Can you connect me?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.37,1:49:11.16,英文,,0,0,0,,Big rhino? Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.23,1:49:12.40,英文,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.30,1:49:18.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.44,1:49:19.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, boss, it's Deck.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.05,1:49:21.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, Deck, how you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.71,1:49:22.61,英文,,0,0,0,,Good. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.67,1:49:23.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.81,1:49:24.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.61,1:49:27.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm here and there.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.15,1:49:29.25,英文,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah, here and there.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.31,1:49:33.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Listen, I got a stolen-evidence situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.55,1:49:36.69,英文,,0,0,0,,OK. Stolen evidence, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.76,1:49:38.49,英文,,0,0,0,,Let me see, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.56,1:49:40.99,英文,,0,0,0,,OK. The De Soto case.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.06,1:49:42.03,英文,,0,0,0,,De Soto?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.09,1:49:45.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Carmine De Soto. You remember him?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.60,1:49:46.50,英文,,0,0,0,,Club Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.57,1:49:47.93,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.00,1:49:49.93,英文,,0,0,0,,Where... where do I find that?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.00,1:49:53.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, around '92, you'll find it, uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.51,1:49:55.91,英文,,0,0,0,,let's see, 650 something, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.97,1:49:57.34,英文,,0,0,0,,Southwest second.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.41,1:49:58.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Boss, you're a lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.88,1:49:59.81,英文,,0,0,0,,'92?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.88,1:50:01.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Club Ruby case.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.58,1:50:03.41,英文,,0,0,0,,'92...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.48,1:50:04.52,英文,,0,0,0,,Carmine De Soto.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.58,1:50:05.65,英文,,0,0,0,,Carmine De Soto.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.72,1:50:06.65,英文,,0,0,0,,Club Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.72,1:50:07.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Club Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.69,1:50:08.95,英文,,0,0,0,,It's from the appellate court.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.02,1:50:10.99,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It kind of rings a bell.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.34,1:50:16.31,英文,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.38,1:50:18.45,英文,,0,0,0,,And from Bruiser, of all people.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.51,1:50:20.45,英文,,0,0,0,,Bruiser? I thought you didn't know where Bruiser was.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.52,1:50:23.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't, but I got an emergency-contact number.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.55,1:50:25.72,英文,,0,0,0,,I call them, they get me in touch with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.79,1:50:26.99,英文,,0,0,0,,Look, Rudy,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.06,1:50:29.29,英文,,0,0,0,,nobody knows more than Bruiser about stolen evidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.36,1:50:31.29,英文,,0,0,0,,You might say it's his stock and trade.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.88,1:50:34.44,英文,,0,0,0,,- Hello? - Mr. Rudy Baylor?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.62,1:50:36.40,英文,,0,0,0,,- Yes. - This is the Shelby county D.A.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.63,1:50:38.07,英文,,0,0,0,,Can you come to the courthouse tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.13,1:50:39.82,英文,,0,0,0,,I'd like to discuss the Kelly Riker case.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.95,1:50:41.68,英文,,0,0,0,,- Sure. - Come to room 6.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.54,1:50:47.21,英文,,0,0,0,,There's an advantage to dealing with pimps and thieves.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.28,1:50:50.24,英文,,0,0,0,,In the case of Carmine De Soto vs. The Club Ruby,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.31,1:50:52.25,英文,,0,0,0,,there are reams of stolen evidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.31,1:50:54.32,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, Bruiser worked on this stuff himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.38,1:50:56.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Not now. I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.92,1:50:58.15,英文,,0,0,0,,You got to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.22,1:51:00.66,英文,,0,0,0,,You got the CEO of Great Benefit coming in tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.72,1:51:04.03,英文,,0,0,0,,We... we got to nail this guy, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.64,1:51:17.14,英文,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.21,1:51:18.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.21,1:51:25.11,英文,,0,0,0,,I met with the D.A.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.18,1:51:27.08,英文,,0,0,0,,She's not gonna prosecute.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.15,1:51:29.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Said she'd never get a conviction.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.32,1:51:32.49,英文,,0,0,0,,It was self-defense, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.11,1:51:48.62,英文,,0,0,0,,The plaintiff would like to call Wilfred Keeley to the stand.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.19,1:51:50.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Raise your right hand, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.91,1:51:52.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Do you solemnly swear that the testimony
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.88,1:51:54.04,英文,,0,0,0,,you're about to give in this cause
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.11,1:51:55.48,英文,,0,0,0,,will be the truth, the whole truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.54,1:51:57.45,英文,,0,0,0,,and nothing but the truth, so help you God?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.51,1:51:58.13,英文,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.22,1:51:59.33,英文,,0,0,0,,You may take the stand.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.46,1:52:04.84,英文,,0,0,0,,State your name for the record.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.99,1:52:06.19,英文,,0,0,0,,Wilfred Keeley.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.26,1:52:08.12,英文,,0,0,0,,May I approach the witness, your honor?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.19,1:52:09.62,英文,,0,0,0,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.69,1:52:13.03,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Keeley, uh, in this Great Benefit brochure,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.10,1:52:14.90,英文,,0,0,0,,is that you? Is that your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.96,1:52:15.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.97,1:52:18.27,英文,,0,0,0,,And what do those initials stand for?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.33,1:52:19.73,英文,,0,0,0,,CEO?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.80,1:52:22.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What do they stand for? What does "CEO" mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.80,1:52:24.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Chief executive officer.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.31,1:52:27.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Chief executive officer. Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.33,1:52:29.38,英文,,0,0,0,,So you're the... you're the guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.51,1:52:32.25,英文,,0,0,0,,You're the main guy, you're the cheese.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.31,1:52:33.98,英文,,0,0,0,,The buck stops with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.31,1:52:35.82,英文,,0,0,0,,You could say that, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.95,1:52:37.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah. OK. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.37,1:52:40.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, your honor, I'd like to turn the questioning
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.44,1:52:43.91,英文,,0,0,0,,of Mr. Keeley over to my partner Rudy Baylor.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.56,1:52:46.14,英文,,0,0,0,,Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.21,1:52:47.31,英文,,0,0,0,,You don't have a license.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.38,1:52:49.31,英文,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a choice. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.38,1:52:50.78,英文,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.11,1:52:52.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Good morning, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.22,1:52:54.19,英文,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.20,1:52:56.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Approach the witness, your honor?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.67,1:52:58.36,英文,,0,0,0,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.93,1:53:02.31,英文,,0,0,0,,This is the claims manual that was given to me by Jackie Lemancyzk.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.40,1:53:03.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Objection, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.51,1:53:04.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Stolen work papers. Inadmissible.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.02,1:53:05.82,英文,,0,0,0,,You ruled on this.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.91,1:53:06.86,英文,,0,0,0,,Sustained.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.93,1:53:08.33,英文,,0,0,0,,May we approach?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.64,1:53:14.71,英文,,0,0,0,,I thought this matter was already settled, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.93,1:53:18.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor, I just this morning found a case that is controlled
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.38,1:53:19.71,英文,,0,0,0,,in this factual situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.78,1:53:21.15,英文,,0,0,0,,What do you have?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.21,1:53:23.72,英文,,0,0,0,,If you'll just take a look at this ruling.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.78,1:53:26.35,英文,,0,0,0,,It's Club Ruby vs. Carmine De Soto.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.42,1:53:28.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Copy for your honor and one for Mr. Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.89,1:53:31.86,英文,,0,0,0,,Number 585, southwest second, page 431,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.92,1:53:34.69,英文,,0,0,0,,argued by Bruiser... by J. Lyman Stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.76,1:53:36.13,英文,,0,0,0,,And it shows very clearly
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.26,1:53:38.35,英文,,0,0,0,,that stolen documents are, in fact, admissible
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.44,1:53:40.87,英文,,0,0,0,,if the lawyers played no part in the theft.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.68,1:53:43.77,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, according to these head notes,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.00,1:53:45.73,英文,,0,0,0,,this case will overrule your objection.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.80,1:53:47.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.72,1:53:50.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sure you are, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.76,1:53:52.49,英文,,0,0,0,,But note my strong objection.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.56,1:53:53.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Objection noted.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.71,1:53:55.68,英文,,0,0,0,,May I approach?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.75,1:53:57.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Do so.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.92,1:54:00.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh... Your honor...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.50,1:54:03.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.57,1:54:07.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Excuse the interruption, Mr. Keeley.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.33,1:54:08.48,英文,,0,0,0,,We were about to talk about
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.62,1:54:10.36,英文,,0,0,0,,the Great Benefit claims manual.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.66,1:54:14.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Is that a complete Great Benefit claims manual, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.47,1:54:17.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.67,1:54:19.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Does it have a section "U"?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.21,1:54:27.85,英文,,0,0,0,,It has a section "U" in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.91,1:54:29.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, let's talk about this mysterious section "U."
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.02,1:54:31.98,英文,,0,0,0,,Why don't we explain it to the jury?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.05,1:54:33.92,英文,,0,0,0,,Take a look at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.02,1:54:36.99,英文,,0,0,0,,Just read paragraph 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.08,1:54:44.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Claim handlers are directed to deny all claims
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.43,1:54:48.44,英文,,0,0,0,,within 3 days of receipt of claim. No exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.62,1:54:51.27,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, how do you explain this section "U"?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.51,1:54:54.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, sometimes we get some frivolous
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.51,1:54:57.77,英文,,0,0,0,,and fraudulent claims in our business,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.31,1:55:00.48,英文,,0,0,0,,and sometimes we have to use this kind of language
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.55,1:55:02.81,英文,,0,0,0,,to focus in on the legitimate
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.88,1:55:05.15,英文,,0,0,0,,and more needy claims.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.55,1:55:09.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Keeley, do you honestly expect this court
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.29,1:55:11.39,英文,,0,0,0,,to believe that explanation?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.39,1:55:12.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, this chapter merely denotes
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.88,1:55:15.81,英文,,0,0,0,,in-house processing guidelines.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.88,1:55:17.34,英文,,0,0,0,,In-house processing guidelines.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.41,1:55:19.65,英文,,0,0,0,,No, Mr. Keeley. No, it does not.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.72,1:55:21.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Section "U" does a lot more than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.55,1:55:23.32,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't think it does that, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.39,1:55:25.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Keeley, doesn't it explain precisely
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.95,1:55:28.53,英文,,0,0,0,,how claims should be routed and shuffled and rerouted,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.54,1:55:30.26,英文,,0,0,0,,anything to avoid payment?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.57,1:55:31.64,英文,,0,0,0,,I admit nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.77,1:55:32.83,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor, approach the witness?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.90,1:55:34.25,英文,,0,0,0,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.42,1:55:40.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, Mr. Keeley,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.88,1:55:47.60,英文,,0,0,0,,how many policies did Great Benefit have in effect in the year 1995?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.63,1:55:53.51,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.97,1:55:55.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.68,1:56:01.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Does the figure 98,000 sound correct, give or take a few?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.99,1:56:04.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.59,1:56:06.39,英文,,0,0,0,,That could be right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.46,1:56:07.63,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.70,1:56:11.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, of these policies, how many claims were filed?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.14,1:56:15.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't... I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.31,1:56:18.88,英文,,0,0,0,,Does the figure of 11,400 sound correct to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.37,1:56:21.01,英文,,0,0,0,,give or take a few?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.42,1:56:22.88,英文,,0,0,0,,That's about right,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.73,1:56:26.75,英文,,0,0,0,,but I'd have to verify it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.82,1:56:28.57,英文,,0,0,0,,I see. So the information that I want
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.66,1:56:29.86,英文,,0,0,0,,is right there in that book?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.48,1:56:31.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.37,1:56:32.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Can you tell the jury
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.22,1:56:34.62,英文,,0,0,0,,of the 11 some odd thousand claims filed,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.80,1:56:36.54,英文,,0,0,0,,how many were denied?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.63,1:56:41.56,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't think I could. That would take more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.22,1:56:43.77,英文,,0,0,0,,You've had 2 months, Mr. Keeley.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.77,1:56:45.67,英文,,0,0,0,,Now answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.22,1:56:52.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.97,1:56:54.81,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.95,1:57:02.65,英文,,0,0,0,,9,141.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.09,1:57:07.29,英文,,0,0,0,,11,462 filed.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.01,1:57:12.71,英文,,0,0,0,,9,141 denied.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.76,1:57:16.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Your honor...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.37,1:57:19.30,英文,,0,0,0,,I have yet another document.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.37,1:57:20.64,英文,,0,0,0,,This is a report
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.70,1:57:23.28,英文,,0,0,0,,from Great Benefit's medical committee.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.00,1:57:28.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Request permission under previous precedent
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.66,1:57:29.91,英文,,0,0,0,,to present it to Mr. Keeley.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.08,1:57:31.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Same objection, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.51,1:57:35.27,英文,,0,0,0,,Overruled. Objection noted.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.33,1:57:36.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.73,1:57:46.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, Mr. Keeley, that is a report
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.08,1:57:47.86,英文,,0,0,0,,from Great Benefit's own medical committee,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.63,1:57:49.68,英文,,0,0,0,,which you chaired.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.91,1:57:54.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Would you please read from line 18?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.11,1:58:00.83,英文,,0,0,0,,Since bone-marrow transplants
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.89,1:58:03.43,英文,,0,0,0,,have become standard procedure,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.50,1:58:06.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Great Benefit would be financially justified
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.80,1:58:09.33,英文,,0,0,0,,in investing in bone-marrow clinics.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.04,1:58:12.30,英文,,0,0,0,,Approach the witness, your honor?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.06,1:58:14.57,英文,,0,0,0,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.64,1:58:15.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.91,1:58:19.29,英文,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:19.77,1:58:20.97,英文,,0,0,0,,A little louder.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.02,1:58:23.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Objection, your honor. Repetitious.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:23.22,1:58:24.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Overruled.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.60,1:58:27.51,英文,,0,0,0,,I want the jury to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.48,1:58:31.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Since bone-marrow transplants
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.91,1:58:34.38,英文,,0,0,0,,have become standard procedure,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.44,1:58:37.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Great Benefit would be financially justified
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.18,1:58:40.06,英文,,0,0,0,,in investing in bone-marrow clinics.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.48,1:58:41.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Financially justified.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.87,1:58:45.37,英文,,0,0,0,,That's what it's all about at Great Benefit, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.54,1:58:47.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Tender the witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.93,1:58:50.17,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.68,1:58:53.64,英文,,0,0,0,,No questions. We rest on our objections.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.71,1:58:56.00,英文,,0,0,0,,You're excused, Mr. Keeley.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.35,1:58:58.23,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.24,1:59:18.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.62,1:59:20.77,英文,,0,0,0,,Come on. Get up. Come on. It's time.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.84,1:59:22.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.64,1:59:28.48,英文,,0,0,0,,What will giving a judgment of $10 million accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.87,1:59:34.27,英文,,0,0,0,,All insurance company premiums will spin out of reach,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.34,1:59:36.24,英文,,0,0,0,,and it will pave the way
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.30,1:59:40.01,英文,,0,0,0,,for government-controlled health coverage.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.31,1:59:43.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Yours is a grave responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.60,1:59:47.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Be wise,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.65,1:59:49.52,英文,,0,0,0,,be careful,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.59,1:59:51.06,英文,,0,0,0,,and be just.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.93,1:59:56.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Be just.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.14,1:59:59.86,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.96,2:00:04.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Baylor, your rebuttal.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.87,2:00:06.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.32,2:00:09.89,英文,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen of the jury...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:12.72,2:00:15.43,英文,,0,0,0,,When I think of Donny Ray Black...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.40,2:00:20.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Gasping for his last breath of air and slowly dying...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.47,2:00:24.93,英文,,0,0,0,,I am disgusted with myself...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.26,2:00:27.64,英文,,0,0,0,,And with the entire legal profession
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.82,2:00:29.20,英文,,0,0,0,,that could not save him.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.46,2:00:33.81,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't even feel good enough about myself as a lawyer
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.82,2:00:35.20,英文,,0,0,0,,to make my own summation.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.58,2:00:42.84,英文,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd... I'd let Donny Ray do that.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.22,2:00:45.29,英文,,0,0,0,,It's exhibit 16.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.56,2:00:52.88,英文,,0,0,0,,I weigh 110 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:53.60,2:00:57.77,英文,,0,0,0,,11 months ago, I weighed 160.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.32,2:01:03.56,英文,,0,0,0,,The leukemia was detected in plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.77,2:01:07.86,英文,,0,0,0,,I was in the hospital being treated
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.93,2:01:09.20,英文,,0,0,0,,when the doctors realized
Dialogue: 0,2:01:09.26,2:01:11.11,英文,,0,0,0,,that the only thing that could save my life
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.28,2:01:13.67,英文,,0,0,0,,would be a bone-marrow transplant.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.35,2:01:20.17,英文,,0,0,0,,So, I got released from the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.24,2:01:23.14,英文,,0,0,0,,'cause my family couldn't afford to pay
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.26,2:01:26.13,英文,,0,0,0,,- the bill for what they had recommended. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.53,2:01:33.94,英文,,0,0,0,,- Great Benefit insurance denied our claim. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.17,2:01:35.47,英文,,0,0,0,,It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.39,2:01:40.98,英文,,0,0,0,,If I had had a bone-marrow transplant,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.05,2:01:44.21,英文,,0,0,0,,I would have had a 90% chance of living.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.65,2:01:52.31,英文,,0,0,0,,I hope that you are astonished as I am,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:52.88,2:01:55.13,英文,,0,0,0,,At the lengths to which a wealthy insurance company,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.19,2:01:56.26,英文,,0,0,0,,like the defendant,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.33,2:01:58.80,英文,,0,0,0,,will go to take money from a low-income family
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.86,2:02:01.82,英文,,0,0,0,,and then keep it by denying a legitimate claim.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.67,2:02:06.66,英文,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder they spend so much money on their lawyers
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.04,2:02:09.77,英文,,0,0,0,,and their lobbyists and their public relations machine
Dialogue: 0,2:02:09.84,2:02:12.78,英文,,0,0,0,,to convince us we need tort reform,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:12.84,2:02:15.42,英文,,0,0,0,,that we need to put an end to punitive damages.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.04,2:02:27.31,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you, the jury...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.23,2:02:29.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.00,2:02:35.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Do what you think is right in your hearts.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.23,2:02:39.47,英文,,0,0,0,,If you don't punish Great Benefit...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.77,2:02:43.47,英文,,0,0,0,,You could be their next victim.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:47.51,2:02:49.05,英文,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.10,2:03:10.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Don't be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.79,2:03:33.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Has the jury reached a verdict?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.86,2:03:35.24,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have, your honor.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:35.68,2:03:37.86,英文,,0,0,0,,Is it written on paper, according to my instructions?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.48,2:03:39.65,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:39.71,2:03:41.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Please read the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.95,2:03:47.22,英文,,0,0,0,,We, the jury, find for the plaintiff
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.29,2:03:49.79,英文,,0,0,0,,and award actual damages
Dialogue: 0,2:03:49.86,2:03:53.96,英文,,0,0,0,,in the amount of $150,000.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.30,2:04:02.62,英文,,0,0,0,,And we, the jury, find for the plaintiff
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.69,2:04:05.16,英文,,0,0,0,,and award punitive damages
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.22,2:04:09.51,英文,,0,0,0,,in the amount of $50 million.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:24.94,2:04:26.81,英文,,0,0,0,,All rise.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:28.05,2:04:29.55,英文,,0,0,0,,These people were trying to hide things
Dialogue: 0,2:04:29.61,2:04:32.28,英文,,0,0,0,,and trying to get away with something they were, uh...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:32.35,2:04:33.55,英文,,0,0,0,,And they got caught at it.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:33.62,2:04:35.25,英文,,0,0,0,,Another remarkable part of the story...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:35.32,2:04:37.54,英文,,0,0,0,,the lead attorney on the case Rudy Baylor
Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.61,2:04:39.24,英文,,0,0,0,,was trying his first case.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:39.31,2:04:40.61,英文,,0,0,0,,That's a staggering verdict,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:40.68,2:04:42.61,英文,,0,0,0,,I think, by anybody's estimation.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:42.68,2:04:44.08,英文,,0,0,0,,It's certainly one of the largest...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:44.15,2:04:46.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, not bad for a yard boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:46.58,2:04:48.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, it wasn't that difficult, really.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.45,2:04:50.55,英文,,0,0,0,,We just had a great jury is what we had,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:50.62,2:04:52.69,英文,,0,0,0,,and the facts just fell into place.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.75,2:04:54.29,英文,,0,0,0,,$50 million in punitive damages.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:54.36,2:04:55.62,英文,,0,0,0,,$50 million?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.69,2:04:56.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:56.73,2:04:58.29,英文,,0,0,0,,How much do you get?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:58.36,2:05:00.39,英文,,0,0,0,,You get right to the point, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:00.46,2:05:01.96,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.03,2:05:02.66,英文,,0,0,0,,I know you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.88,2:05:06.35,英文,,0,0,0,,We get 1/3, but the money's not in the bank yet.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.07,2:05:09.50,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:09.57,2:05:11.51,英文,,0,0,0,,You gonna leave this girl all alone?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.57,2:05:13.14,英文,,0,0,0,,Not for long.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.61,2:05:17.34,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy. Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:17.41,2:05:20.71,英文,,0,0,0,,I've decided I'm gonna put your name in my will.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.78,2:05:22.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh. You know what?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:22.44,2:05:24.66,英文,,0,0,0,,You are just too kind to me, Miss Birdie.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:29.17,2:05:30.94,英文,,0,0,0,,Hot off the newswire.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.01,2:05:35.58,英文,,0,0,0,,Mr. Wilfred Keeley, CEO of Great Benefit,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.65,2:05:38.12,英文,,0,0,0,,was detained yesterday afternoon at JFK
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.18,2:05:41.18,英文,,0,0,0,,just after boarding a flight bound for Heathrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.25,2:05:43.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Traveling with his wife,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:43.20,2:05:45.56,英文,,0,0,0,,they claimed to be sneaking away for a quick holiday.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.62,2:05:47.76,英文,,0,0,0,,However, they could not produce the name of a hotel anywhere in Europe
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.99,2:05:50.26,英文,,0,0,0,,At which they were expected.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.33,2:05:53.03,英文,,0,0,0,,At 5 P.M. today, insurance company Great Benefit
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.10,2:05:55.03,英文,,0,0,0,,filed for protection under the bankruptcy code
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.10,2:05:56.60,英文,,0,0,0,,in federal court in Cleveland.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.67,2:05:59.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Many states are now investigating Great Benefit,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.47,2:06:01.89,英文,,0,0,0,,and a number of class-action lawsuits have been filed.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.20,2:06:06.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:06.51,2:06:08.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Rudy, Leo Drummond here.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.98,2:06:12.22,英文,,0,0,0,,It appears the company's been looted.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:13.59,2:06:15.55,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm sorry, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:16.13,2:06:18.26,英文,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to get every penny of that money.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:18.96,2:06:21.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Everybody loses on this one.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:21.94,2:06:24.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Wanted you to know.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:25.25,2:06:27.08,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:28.32,2:06:30.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Great Benefit's like a bad slot machine...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.60,2:06:32.13,英文,,0,0,0,,never pays off.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.20,2:06:35.17,英文,,0,0,0,,We should have taken 175,000.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.91,2:06:37.77,英文,,0,0,0,,What the hell were we thinking?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.38,2:06:44.38,英文,,0,0,0,,It just got all twisted, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.45,2:06:46.40,英文,,0,0,0,,This legal profession.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:47.39,2:06:48.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Every lawyer in America is talking about me right now,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:50.91,2:06:52.17,英文,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't exactly make me feel
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.24,2:06:54.22,英文,,0,0,0,,like a member of the legal community.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:55.44,2:06:57.34,英文,,0,0,0,,I might be able to go on practicing law
Dialogue: 0,2:06:57.41,2:06:59.60,英文,,0,0,0,,if I was working with my whole heart,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:00.04,2:07:01.85,英文,,0,0,0,,but I can't do that and cover Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:03.06,2:07:05.20,英文,,0,0,0,,And she's gonna need a lot of cover for a while.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:08.48,2:07:11.11,英文,,0,0,0,,I still love the law. I'll always love it,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:11.33,2:07:12.71,英文,,0,0,0,,but maybe I should be teaching it
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.80,2:07:14.80,英文,,0,0,0,,instead of practicing it out here in the world.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:16.51,2:07:18.08,英文,,0,0,0,,I need time to work it out.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:18.72,2:07:21.32,英文,,0,0,0,,Great Benefit has gone belly up.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.82,2:07:25.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Barring a miracle way off in the distance,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:25.95,2:07:27.12,英文,,0,0,0,,we won't get a dime.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.62,2:07:29.68,英文,,0,0,0,,God.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:30.08,2:07:31.68,英文,,0,0,0,,You've put them out of business, Dot.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.75,2:07:34.72,英文,,0,0,0,,One little woman from Memphis, Tennessee,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.78,2:07:37.95,英文,,0,0,0,,bankrupted them sons of bitches?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.60,2:07:43.64,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go to Donny Ray's grave tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.73,2:07:45.20,英文,,0,0,0,,and tell him all about it.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:52.00,2:07:54.15,英文,,0,0,0,,So, I guess Kelly and I
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.22,2:07:56.57,英文,,0,0,0,,will be taking off first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.39,2:08:00.49,英文,,0,0,0,,We made history, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:01.89,2:08:03.33,英文,,0,0,0,,You know that?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:05.93,2:08:07.96,英文,,0,0,0,,We can always brag.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.97,2:08:11.47,英文,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:12.54,2:08:14.27,英文,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it... I'm hot.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.84,2:08:16.41,英文,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm so hot after this case,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:16.47,2:08:18.84,英文,,0,0,0,,there's no place for me to go but down.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:19.34,2:08:20.38,英文,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.45,2:08:22.78,英文,,0,0,0,,Every client I ever have will expect this...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:22.85,2:08:25.98,英文,,0,0,0,,the same magic, nothing less.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:26.05,2:08:28.13,英文,,0,0,0,,And I could probably give it to them,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.55,2:08:30.62,英文,,0,0,0,,if it didn't matter how I did it.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:31.24,2:08:32.51,英文,,0,0,0,,And then one morning,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:32.57,2:08:35.11,英文,,0,0,0,,I'd wake up and find that I'd become Leo Drummond.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.28,2:08:39.86,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, you give me a call when you pass the bar exam.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:41.11,2:08:42.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:45.59,2:08:48.45,英文,,0,0,0,,Every lawyer, at least once in every case,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.52,2:08:51.73,英文,,0,0,0,,feels himself crossing a line he doesn't really mean to cross.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.79,2:08:52.86,英文,,0,0,0,,It just happens.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:52.93,2:08:54.93,英文,,0,0,0,,And if you cross it enough times,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.00,2:08:57.03,英文,,0,0,0,,it disappears forever.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:58.20,2:09:00.90,英文,,0,0,0,,And then you're nothing but another lawyer joke,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:00.97,2:09:04.07,英文,,0,0,0,,just another shark in the dirty water.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.88,0:53:20.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,凯丽 雷科
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.59,1:09:29.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是布奇 他来找窃听器
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.25,1:09:47.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,办公室内有小型窃听器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我父亲一生都恨律师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:42.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我个人认为 他不算是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:45.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他酗酒 并且虐待我的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:47.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他也殴打我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:49.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要是你认为我要成为一个律师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:50.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只是为了气他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:52.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那你也许就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:55.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我之所以想成为一个律师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:56.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是自从我读了有关民权律师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在五十和六十年代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:00.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为法律发掘出令人惊异的运用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:03.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们做了许多人认为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:04.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,本来是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:07.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们给了律师一个好名声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:10.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因此我进了法学院
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:11.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这确实激怒了我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:13.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不过他其实总是在发火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:15.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在我读大学的第一年 有一天他喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:16.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,从梯子上摔下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:19.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这发生在他干活的工厂里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:21.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而他却不知道要先告谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:24.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,大约两个月后他就因此去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:27.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我喝干啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:28.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的一些同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.53,0:01:30.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,知道他们将从学校出去后直接
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:31.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,进入顶级的律师事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:34.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,主要依靠他们的家庭关系网
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:36.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而我所仅有的一个关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:38.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是三年来在一个酒巴跑堂而建立起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:40.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为我得赚钱付我的学费
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:42.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当我踌躇满志
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:45.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要让正义之光 照亮每一个黑暗角落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:48.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我其实迫切需要的是一份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:50.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为孟菲斯的律师 太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:57.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这座城市到处是他们的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:06.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不知道有什么能比这更令人苦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就是告诉别人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.95,0:02:11.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是为伯鲁瑟斯通工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:16.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是说 他是个律师 大家叫他伯鲁瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:19.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我如此失望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:20.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:22.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把门关上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:25.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 不是那个 也不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:28.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:29.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:32.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就在我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:38.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我真的同情这个可怜的FBI探员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:40.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他非要想从交谈中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:41.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,搞些资料出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:44.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,律师的办公室里养着活生生的鲨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是个玩笑 明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如此说来 普林斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:49.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这就是你向我提起过的法学院学生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.96,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是 先生我刚在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.79,中文简体,,0,0,0,,孟菲斯州立大学读完三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你能让他在这里工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:56.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你看 我可以为他担保
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这孩子需要找份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:01.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他在我们俱乐部的酒巴打工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:04.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪 这儿会是你工作的好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:06.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这儿会是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:08.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你工作的好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:10.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你可以看到真正的律师是怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:13.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但这里不提供带薪职位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不算吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我希望我的人 能自己挣出工资来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:21.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,自己创收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,向我汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:26.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那怎么运作呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 鲁迪 你每月支取一千美金
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:32.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,另外你可以从你赚到的钱里抽取三分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要是你赚的比支取的多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:37.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那到每个月底差额就算你欠我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你听明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我觉得挺公平 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:43.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是个不易接受的交易 的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但这么做你能挣很多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:47.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让我来告诉你 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是我唯一的经营方式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我会让你接手很多好案子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我手里有案子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:55.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我现在手上有两个案子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,一个是办遗嘱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我替一个老妇人起草遗嘱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她很富有 值好几百万
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而另一个案子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是个保险案子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,巨大福利公司 听说过么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你有委托人的签字吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:14.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我现在正要去找他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:15.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们也很愿意听我的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:17.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我在法律工作室帮过他们的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很好 我会让你去和我的一个同事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,狄克谢佛来尔谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:24.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他常与那些大保险公司打交道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他负责所有高级别的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嘿 狄克！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,狄克！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.79,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你建立了那些案子的档案了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:34.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在我的车上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嘿 帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是狄克谢佛来尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:46.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这家伙会带你上路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想让你做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:51.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,立案起诉这个巨大福利保险公司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:54.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,并署上我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们今天就建立档案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:59.50,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪 你会学到很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:02.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪 我很高兴你到这儿来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你做了个很好的选择 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不错 那么 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,出去的时候把门带上 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:10.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,律师事务所 要帮忙么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是个办公室 有人在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要是有人在办公室里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你就别用它 太挤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.78,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这里是厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:16.79,中文简体,,0,0,0,,等一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:17.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么 你是他的的同事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,算是吧 不是正式的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,确凿说来我还不算个律师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:25.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,伯鲁瑟一般要求我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,审查那些牵涉保险的案子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:29.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我曾经在保险公司工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,干厌了就进了法学院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:33.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么 你什么时候从法学院毕业的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,瞧 我在律师执照考试上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有那么点儿小麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我考了六次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:40.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,听到这些真让我感到遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:41.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是啊 你什么时候参加执照考试？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:42.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我差不多三周后就要考了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:43.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:44.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这真那么难吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我要说 相当地难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我一年前考过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想 我再也不去考了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:51.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,随它去吧 这里是伯鲁瑟的法律图书室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要是你从冰箱里拿任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:54.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,或者你要用这个冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你可以在你的东西上写上你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不过他们照样会吃了它 把这个放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 这只是米饭罢了 这是什么玩意儿 黛茜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:01.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们把这儿搞的很糟 清理一下啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然 狄克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:04.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,随它去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,等等 你上法庭的时候怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,老实说 我是很少单独出庭的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所以至今还没被抓住过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这里有这么多律师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:14.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们不太可能会引起注意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:18.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,伯鲁瑟拥有这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:20.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:22.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你真不能称其为律师事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,每个人都只是为了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:25.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你会学到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,什么 你是在搬家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:31.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,被赶出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是保险单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.50,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:39.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你觉的怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:42.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 这真是最烂的保单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们拒付的理由是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:46.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 全部拒付
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:48.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,先在不符合理赔规定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:52.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,然后他们说白血病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是在投保之前就有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:54.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,接着又说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:56.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,白血病根本就不在本保单范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我这里有七封信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,保费都交全了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,根据勃拉克女士的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:01.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,每一项保费她都付过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这些个杂种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:07.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是典型的保险诈骗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,黑人们称这为街头险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你签字接办 所有的都签
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:18.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,然后交给简李曼斯通事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这就对了 我会帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:24.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的 那么 谢谢 十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没什么比搞定保险公司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,更令人激动的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨 勃拉克女士 我是鲁迪拜勒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:52.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,还记得吗？我在处理你控告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:53.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,巨大福利保险公司的案子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我在孟菲斯州立大学法律工作室和你见过面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对 快请进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:01.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请进 很抱歉 那些疯狗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:02.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 那没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我还以为你是 耶和华听证会的教士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:06.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,伯迪在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:07.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他在外面车里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他要去哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:12.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他哪儿都不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他的脑袋不太对劲儿 是战争创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:17.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在朝鲜留下的 知道机场的金属探测器吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他就是脱光了过安检
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,警铃都会响个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他的脑袋里还留着块弹片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:28.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:32.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,丹尼雷还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 时好时坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:34.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,脑袋里留着块弹片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.79,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你要见他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也许等会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:39.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:47.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,巨大福利保险公司 第一次拒赔是在去年八月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:50.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当丹尼雷被确诊之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:52.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为什么直到现在 你们才向律师咨询？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:55.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我猜是愚蠢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我只是不断地给他们写信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而他们也不断地给我回信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:01.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哪 这是最后收到的一封
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:04.96,中文简体,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 勃拉克女士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,前面七次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,本公司已经书面拒绝了你的索赔要求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:11.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,现在我们第八次也是最后一次 拒绝赔偿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:14.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你一定是很愚蠢 很愚蠢 相当的愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:23.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,真诚地 艾沃特鲁富肯 理赔部副总经理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,真令人难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你就是那位律师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我妈夸过你好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:39.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她说你会控告巨大福利保险公司的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:42.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让他们赔钱 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对 是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:46.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:51.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 在我们建立索赔档案之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我需要你们三个人的签字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,爸爸进来么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:58.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,唉 他说会进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他有时候进来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:00.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有时候又不进来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:02.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 这是合同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:03.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,上面写了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只是些格式条款
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,总的来说就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你们将请我们做为代理人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们将接手处理你们的案子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,并负担所有可能的开销
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:18.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,然后我们从赔偿款中抽取三分之一作为佣金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:23.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 可就这么几句话 干嘛要写两页纸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:25.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,怪不得我要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们三个人都必须签吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 夫人 都得签 签在你们名字旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他说他不进来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,拿枝笔去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让他去签下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想我只能这么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:50.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,喂 伯迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你得在文件上签个字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:55.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这样丹尼雷就可以做手术了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:59.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把这可恶的酒瓶子给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我要把它扔到大街上去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:04.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,现在 在这签字 快点 快点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:09.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我知道你一定以为他们都疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们都是很好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨 哥们儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:23.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨 你留鼻血了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,勃拉克女士！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把头仰起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,勃拉克女士！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:33.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没什么我来弄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他在流鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把头仰起来 仰起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:37.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,快点儿 仰起头来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:40.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,啊 亲爱的 没什么 一切都会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我自己来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:44.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让我自己来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,都会好的 都会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好啦 我捂住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你一定会好起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:52.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,文件在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,丹尼雷 你不能稍稍歇一歇吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:55.58,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你可以等一会儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:56.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你不用着急
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:58.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 不 我想现在就做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:03.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对 对 你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:04.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:20.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,啊 柏蒂女士 这是鲁迪拜勒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:24.58,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:27.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是鲁迪拜勒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:28.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们在孟菲斯法律工作室见过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 对了 噢 请进 快请进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:36.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,多谢 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,您今天还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不错 很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:42.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,柏蒂女士 我想跟您谈谈遗嘱的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把我的孩子们从我的遗嘱里剔出去 剔除 剔除 剔除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,剔除 剔除 剔除 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我昨晚上没睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,原因是我一直在担心您的财产
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:51.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,现在 如果您大意了 柏蒂女士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:54.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,政府就会从中抽取相当大的份额
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:57.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,其实 很多税款是可以避免支付的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只要仔细制订一下财产分配计划
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:02.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 全都是废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是不是想把你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,写进我的遗嘱里去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:07.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然不是 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:10.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,律师们总是想把他们的名字写进我的遗嘱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 夫人 律师和律师是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为了安排您的财产 我需要您告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,钱是存在哪里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:21.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是债券 股票还是现金？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:25.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哎 鲁迪 别那么急 不要那么急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:31.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 夫人 那先不管在哪儿 反正有这笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们将把它留给谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我希望把所有的钱留给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,肯尼思钱德勒 教士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:38.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你知道这个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他最近老是出现在达拉斯的电视里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:44.58,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他一头的灰白卷发 老得早了点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:45.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他根本不会想到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,会得到这笔钱的 你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:50.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我希望他拿到这笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:53.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起 柏蒂女士 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:54.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:57.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我只是有一个很实际的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:00.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,起草这么一个遗嘱或契约
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:04.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要把家庭成员都剔除出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反而
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把大部分财产
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,给一个电视台的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,啊 他是上帝的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:17.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:18.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:22.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有没有别的方法把这件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:24.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有必要把所有的一切都给他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:28.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,能不能 比如说 给他25%？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他的开销很大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他的零件也已经老了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:33.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,零件已经老了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这样 鲁迪 我希望请你只是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,按照我要求的去起草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:40.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,然后拿回来让我过目 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:44.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是强盗小时候还招人喜欢时的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,剔除 剔除 剔除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你会回来的 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:54.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 我会 我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:58.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不客气 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,后院是个小公寓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:03.79,中文简体,,0,0,0,,以前是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你觉得我的花园怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:07.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,啊 这是个很漂亮的花园
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:09.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,您自己当园丁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,大部分是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:13.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我请了一个男孩子 每周替我剪一次草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:15.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我付三十美金 你信吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:17.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,以前是五美金的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 我不知道您想不想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:20.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,出租这个地方 愿意么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我可付不起太多租金？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:25.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我会给你个好价钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:28.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只要你能帮我干点杂货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然 当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:32.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也就是除除草之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然 我是除草专家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:39.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我常来医院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:42.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,伯鲁瑟和各行都有联系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他的那些发小们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,每天早上都会向他提供事故报告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:46.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我可以问你点儿事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:47.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:51.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,到底伯鲁瑟想让我做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:53.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,发掘案子 找受害人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:56.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让他们委托 简李曼斯通律师事务所 替他们打官司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把案子集中起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这么说我得去征求别人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在法学院他们是怎么教你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 他们并没有教我追着救护车跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:06.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 你最好快点儿学会 否则就要挨饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:13.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你只要预约一个门诊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:15.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们现在就可以为您登记 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:16.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:19.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,维廉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,狄克 你好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,挺好 去346病房
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:25.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,威尔斯大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:26.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你好吗？有幸见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别整的像个律师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哼 请勿入内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你好吗？麦克肯兹先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的化验怎么样啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:54.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,该死 钓错鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:56.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,万蓝德尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:17:00.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,下午好 万蓝德尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:04.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,能听见我说话吗 万蓝德尔先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:05.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是狄克谢佛来尔 救难的律师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:11.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你还没有和保险公司谈过吧？有没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:12.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:14.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很好 不要和他们交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:15.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为他们只是要勒索你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:16.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你有没有私人律师？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:17.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:20.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的律师事务所处理的车祸案子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:21.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在孟菲斯是最多的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:24.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,保险公司见了我们就怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而且我们不收一分钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你能不能等我太太来了再说？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你太太 万先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,真对不起 万蓝德尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:37.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:40.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你太太在哪儿 万蓝德尔先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她稍等一会儿就会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的 我想在我的办公室和她谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:47.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为我需要了解很多情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在这上面签个字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:50.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,记住 除了你的大夫之外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别与任何人交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,来找你的人会有很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,向你提供解决方案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:58.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不希望你在任何情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在我没有审查之前 签署任何文件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,听明白了没？我的电话号码 就写在名片上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:04.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你24小时都可以找我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:06.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪拜勒先生的电话号码印在反面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你也可以在任何时候找他 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你还有什么疑问吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:11.58,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:14.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很好 我们会帮你讨回一大笔钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:16.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对你的腿 我真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:22.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请你让我一个人清静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这就是怎么去做交易的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,小菜一碟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要是遇到个家伙有自己的律师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们没做什么承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:34.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如果出于某种原因 把我们赶出门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:37.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们也没失去什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,失去点儿做人的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:41.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也许是自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:43.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪 在法学院里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们并不教你想学的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那里只有理论 玄虚的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:51.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,再加上大本的道德规范
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:52.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,道德又有什么不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我猜 没什么不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 我相信一个律师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.77,0:18:59.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,必须为他的委托人去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:00.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,防止钱财被盗去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:01.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,并且尽量不骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:03.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你知道的 这是最基本的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:04.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这样追着救护车找客户 太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没错儿 可谁在乎呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,遍地都是律师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这就是市场 这就是竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:13.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法学院没教你的东西 可能会让你受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:17.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你怎么判断律师是否在说谎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:19.78,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他开口就是在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:24.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,律师和妓女有什么区别？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:28.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,至少妓女在你死后 就不会再缠着你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:32.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,大家都喜欢听有关律师的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,律师自己就特别喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们甚至以此为荣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:38.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谁知道为什么会这样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:41.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,第三方将辩护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所以控方也可以利用这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:44.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,去引进第三方证人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你这是在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:50.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 我在学习
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我觉得学习该占用自己的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我知道 伯鲁瑟 可是你瞧 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,下个礼拜要考律师执照了 对不？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:19:59.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就是下个礼拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:00.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我有点儿担心 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:03.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨 鲁迪 瞧 你想学习
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为什么不能跑到医院去学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:06.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,跟狄克学习？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不想从那方面学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不想跟着狄克学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:13.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不错 我这里有个警察的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:17.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们能做这个受害人的代理人吗？雷科女士？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:18.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:21.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那为什么你不能跑到医院去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:23.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也许你能得到她的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:03.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你能替我弄点饮料来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:15.79,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你要的饮料来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.67,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这些伤都是从哪儿来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:23.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你想告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:25.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这些伤是怎么来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:26.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在我注视他们那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:28.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我知道这事是怎么发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:30.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就如同我十岁大时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:32.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我父亲在卧室里哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.36,0:21:33.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我母亲满脸是血
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:35.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,坐在餐桌旁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,告诉我说爸爸很懊悔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,并保证以后再不这样做了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:40.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,老天爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:42.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你只要对我说是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:45.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为什么你要这样对我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:47.78,中文简体,,0,0,0,,和你在一起 总是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你让我发疯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:57.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,凯丽雷科 三天前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:59.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就被送到圣彼德医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:01.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想强调一下 是在半夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:04.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,带着各式各样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:07.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,警察在小房间的沙发上发现了她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.95,0:22:10.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,赤身裸体裹着条毯子 几乎被打死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,克利夫雷科
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:15.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她的丈夫 显然是喝醉了酒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:16.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,情绪激动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:21.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,一开始居然想用打老婆的东西 殴打警察
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:23.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她是被
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:26.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,一根铝合金棒球棒 狠揍了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:28.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是他惯用的凶器
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:33.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让我们来讨论一下柏蒂女士的百万家产
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.69,0:22:36.96,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 我想讨论克利夫的案子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:39.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想讨论克利夫身上发生了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:41.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他只被关了一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:42.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他家里把他保释了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.06,0:22:45.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他在一周内就要出庭 啥事都不会有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:47.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:50.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,考林 简尼思 伯德松
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.62,0:22:52.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她的确是从第二个丈夫手里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.79,0:22:54.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,继承了几百万遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:58.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可是扣除律师费 失败的信托投资
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:02.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,以及税金 他的财产已经所剩无几
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.35,0:23:04.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,大概只剩四万美金
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:08.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,恐怕柏蒂女士 把它们都塞进了床垫里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:09.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如我们所知
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:11.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:21.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是我的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:22.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我唯一的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:25.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你令我快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:27.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当天空灰濛濛的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:34.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不要夺走我的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:36.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 早上好啊 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:37.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是不是可爱的一天啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.59,0:23:40.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 是的 天气真美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:43.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 铺草坪的垫土来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:44.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,正好 那边点儿 靠那边点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:46.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就在这儿 对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:48.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,停 停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:50.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不错 就直接卸在这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:52.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的园丁会来取的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:54.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就卸在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:57.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好大一堆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.93,0:24:26.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.44,0:24:29.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我并非多管闲事 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.37,0:24:33.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你没什么吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.18,0:24:35.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是不是痛啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.61,0:24:37.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.80,0:24:40.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不过还是多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.17,0:24:42.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 好吧 我就站这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.07,0:24:43.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我只不过在那边准备律师执照考试
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.90,0:24:46.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要是你有什么事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.54,0:24:48.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就招呼我一声
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.07,0:24:49.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.06,0:24:50.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不管什么事 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.98,0:24:53.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我会为你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.38,0:24:57.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我叫鲁迪拜勒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.88,0:24:59.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,凯丽雷科 很高兴与你相识
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.64,0:25:02.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,凯丽 能认识你很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.42,0:25:04.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为什么你不坐下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.49,0:25:07.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,去搬个椅子坐下来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.73,0:25:15.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你在那个学校念书？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.40,0:25:18.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我进过奥斯汀匹艾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.04,0:25:21.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,后来就进了孟菲斯州立大学的法学院
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.20,0:25:26.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我一直想进大学
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.97,0:25:30.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但却一直也没成功
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.22,0:25:32.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.35,0:25:34.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是啊 我一直以为我会进的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.52,0:25:36.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可就是没成功
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.93,0:25:38.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你想成为一个什么样的律师？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.38,0:25:42.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 我喜欢庭审工作 所以嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.38,0:25:47.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我喜欢整天都待在法庭上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.91,0:25:51.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为罪犯辩护吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.48,0:25:54.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也许 也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.56,0:25:57.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们也需要有人辩护
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.59,0:25:59.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在法庭上他们有这个权力
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.71,0:26:01.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那杀人犯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.35,0:26:07.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,大多数杀人犯 雇不起私人律师
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.88,0:26:12.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,强奸犯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.55,0:26:15.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,和侵害儿童的罪犯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.70,0:26:19.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.40,0:26:22.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么殴打妻子的男人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.16,0:26:37.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,刑事案件有其特殊性
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.40,0:26:40.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我更愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.67,0:26:43.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,民事诉讼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.95,0:26:45.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就像诉讼和调查
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.64,0:26:46.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 对 - 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.68,0:26:52.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那是 请原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.11,0:27:02.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪拜勒
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.27,0:27:04.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你好 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.34,0:27:05.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.61,0:27:07.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鱼钓得怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.17,0:27:10.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 这个 嗯 进行的还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.35,0:27:12.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,事实上我现在正在和潜在委托人交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.20,0:27:14.50,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不错 你最好让她签约雇你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.57,0:27:17.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,怎么啦 鲁迪？鲁迪？你听见我说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.61,0:27:18.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很高兴和你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.91,0:27:20.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.21,0:27:22.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是啊 多谢你和我作伴
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.71,0:27:24.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嘿 明晚上还继续么？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.51,0:27:26.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也许行
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.08,0:27:43.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,时间到了 停笔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.88,0:27:45.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请把你的考卷往右传
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.92,0:27:48.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这样监考员可以把它们收在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.26,0:27:49.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我在法学院的第一学年
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.95,0:27:51.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,大家都是相亲相爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.92,0:27:53.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为我们都是学法律的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.99,0:27:56.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而法律是很清高的事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.53,0:27:58.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,到了第三学年
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.40,0:28:00.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你要庆幸自己没在睡梦里被人谋杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.20,0:28:02.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,人们在考场作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.40,0:28:04.67,中文简体,,0,0,0,,从图书馆里偷取研究资料
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.74,0:28:06.67,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对教授们撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.17,0:28:12.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这就是这行的本质
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.82,0:28:18.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.58,0:28:21.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,半小时之前 她丈夫来过
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.09,0:28:22.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把一大碗汤泼向她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.06,0:28:24.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为她不想听到那些
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.06,0:28:26.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 我多爱你之类的甜言蜜语 - 这就是我的病房
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.03,0:28:32.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,十八岁怀孕 结婚 然后就流产了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.10,0:28:34.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也许就因为他殴打她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.10,0:28:36.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是 她却仍然不想离开他
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.20,0:28:38.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你得帮我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.80,0:28:39.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我虽没亲眼看到这些
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.87,0:28:42.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但一切都告诉我 这姑娘是个失败者
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.27,0:28:44.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,流产啊断骨啊也许还有更危险的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.18,0:28:47.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我以前真没见过像她这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.05,0:28:49.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,与其逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.46,0:28:51.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我要尽我的一切保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.52,0:29:18.36,中文简体,,0,0,0,,探视时间已过 亲爱的 请长话短说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.83,0:29:40.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.75,0:29:42.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他该被枪毙
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.28,0:29:46.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,用铝合金棒球棒打自己妻子的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.62,0:29:47.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,都该被枪毙
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.56,0:29:51.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你怎么会知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.73,0:29:53.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有警察的报告 有救护车的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.88,0:29:56.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,还有医院的病历
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.53,0:29:57.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,凯丽 你还想再等多久呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.93,0:30:00.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,等他决定用他的棒球棒打碎你的脑袋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.70,0:30:03.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这会致你于死地 你知道吗 你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.91,0:30:06.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,几下你就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.14,0:30:09.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别说了 用不着告诉我我该怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.57,0:30:17.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,看着我 凯丽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.40,0:30:19.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我能问你点儿事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.37,0:30:26.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你有父亲或者兄弟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.88,0:30:29.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为什么问这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.02,0:30:32.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,假如你是我的女儿 像你这样被打了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.88,0:30:35.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我向上帝起誓 我会扭断他的脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.09,0:30:39.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没有哥哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.04,0:30:43.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.73,0:30:48.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没人照顾我 你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.80,0:30:58.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,凯丽 我会尽我所能帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.48,0:31:01.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但你一定得申请离婚
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.42,0:31:05.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,趁你还在医院里治疗家暴创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.11,0:31:06.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,赶快办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.28,0:31:08.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,现成的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.40,0:31:10.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,还有什么更好的证据吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.06,0:31:15.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我 我不能申请离婚
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.26,0:31:17.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为什么不能呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.84,0:31:20.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为他会杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.55,0:31:25.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他一直是对我这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.66,0:31:29.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这决不会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.15,0:31:32.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请你递个枕头给我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.93,0:31:35.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把它垫在我腿下好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.28,0:31:36.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那边有一只
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.24,0:31:47.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.25,0:31:51.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这样行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.95,0:31:53.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.20,0:31:54.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.80,0:31:56.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请再把我的睡袍递给我 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.57,0:31:57.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.82,0:32:00.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.15,0:32:02.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要我帮你穿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.15,0:32:05.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不用 你只要背过身去就行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.60,0:32:07.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.80,0:32:27.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.82,0:32:29.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢！你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.77,0:32:31.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我住在这里 你又是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.33,0:32:33.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 我的上帝 我是笛尔伯特的太太
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.82,0:32:34.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,笛尔伯特？谁又是笛尔伯特？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.11,0:32:36.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你怎么进来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.22,0:32:37.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是柏蒂把钥匙交给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.08,0:32:39.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.28,0:32:40.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我住在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.53,0:32:42.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你明白么？你无权待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.71,0:32:43.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是私人住宅 - 是的 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.95,0:32:45.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,行了行了 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.42,0:32:47.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,柏蒂要见你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.69,0:32:52.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,协议永久有效
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.11,0:32:55.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,且包含上述限制条款
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.08,0:32:57.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.60,0:32:59.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 你想必就是那个律师了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.60,0:33:00.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是鲁迪拜勒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.93,0:33:02.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是笛尔伯特伯德松 柏蒂的小儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.11,0:33:04.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他朝我大喊大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.71,0:33:06.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他让我滚出他的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.93,0:33:08.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.08,0:33:09.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你说对了 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.42,0:33:10.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对你们两位都是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.48,0:33:11.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不希望你们任何一个上去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.60,0:33:13.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,乱翻我的东西 那是私人财产
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.64,0:33:15.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我回家来看望我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.06,0:33:17.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,发觉 她让一个混身发臭的 律师和她一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.31,0:33:20.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是不是在篡改我妈的遗嘱？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.69,0:33:22.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她是你妈 为什么不直接问她？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.99,0:33:26.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她一句话都不说
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.69,0:33:27.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.31,0:33:29.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那我也什么都不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.55,0:33:32.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是律师与委托人之间的隐私
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.59,0:33:40.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是让我来告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.33,0:33:45.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我打过好几个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.35,0:33:48.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,查过某些账目
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.62,0:33:50.58,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你妈妈的第二任丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.11,0:33:53.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,给她留下了巨额的财产
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.08,0:33:54.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,多大呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.77,0:33:56.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很大
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.76,0:33:58.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很大？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.48,0:34:00.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你不会从中作梗吧 小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.08,0:34:05.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,妈妈 你不是想到我们家去住些日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.71,0:34:07.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,去弗罗里达吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.42,0:34:09.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,妈妈 你会爱上那儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.17,0:34:11.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,妈妈 坐回来吃点儿点心吧 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.60,0:34:12.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我来给她倒杯牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.71,0:34:15.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们住的离青年喷水池很近
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.55,0:34:18.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,离那儿只有33英里 我们离迪斯尼乐园也只有180英里
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.55,0:34:44.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,丹尼雷 感觉怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.04,0:34:46.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.17,0:34:48.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我看上去不是很棒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.81,0:34:49.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你觉得能行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.04,0:34:51.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,行啊 动身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.78,0:34:53.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.25,0:34:58.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,按说律师不该和委托人建立私人感情
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.38,0:35:01.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是律师和律师还不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.99,0:35:03.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,委托人也有很多种
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.72,0:35:20.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,都还好吧 宝贝儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.62,0:35:34.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,雷科！雷科！雷科！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.97,0:35:36.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,雷科！雷科！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.80,0:35:38.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,还需要点儿什么别的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.08,0:35:42.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 要点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.68,0:35:45.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请再给我一杯杰克丹尼尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.65,0:35:49.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,干嘛？想宰了我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.37,0:35:55.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,柏蒂女士 这是我的朋友丹尼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.56,0:35:56.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 丹尼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.66,0:35:59.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,欢迎你的光临
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.66,0:36:01.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,您好 柏蒂女士
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.23,0:36:02.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在--噢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.00,0:36:04.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.23,0:36:06.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你就过来坐在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.40,0:36:08.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,放松一下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.64,0:36:11.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,您快把我吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.17,0:36:12.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把我围住了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.87,0:36:14.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.04,0:36:28.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起 柏蒂女士 我得歇会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.13,0:36:29.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,腰酸背痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.27,0:36:31.96,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我差点儿忘了 这是寄给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.17,0:36:38.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,啊 我的上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.50,0:36:40.50,中文简体,,0,0,0,,呕！太让人激动了不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.57,0:36:44.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我真为你骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.07,0:36:45.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 我通过律师执照考试了 - 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.16,0:36:48.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨 来来 这杯敬鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.66,0:36:51.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,祝贺你通过考试
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.66,0:36:53.36,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.43,0:36:54.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,冰茶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.23,0:36:58.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,祝贺你 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.40,0:37:00.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,孩子们 干得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.11,0:37:02.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我今天从万蓝德尔的案子拿到一笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.21,0:37:03.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我要给你们发奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.98,0:37:06.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,每人五千五百美金
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.51,0:37:07.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.61,0:37:09.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,再争取多签些合同 啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.85,0:37:11.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.45,0:37:17.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,明天一早 准备好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.36,0:37:18.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,九点整？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.42,0:37:22.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们要准备辩论
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.53,0:37:25.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,巨大福利保险公司的撤诉请求
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.73,0:37:28.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 对 我觉得我们准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.00,0:37:32.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,狄克和我很清楚 我想我们准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.11,0:37:35.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但愿如此 因为我可能 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.94,0:37:39.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我可能让你出马辩论 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.22,0:37:46.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们要是输了这场官司 会很丢面子的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.12,0:37:48.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,老板？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.35,0:37:51.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.52,0:37:54.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我来付账
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.09,0:37:56.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你们享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.73,0:37:58.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,多谢 伯鲁瑟 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.86,0:38:08.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,情况有些不妙 我确信
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.64,0:38:12.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他以前从不这么分钱
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.73,0:38:15.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你能想像 他慷慨的背后是什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.41,0:38:18.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,得了吧 伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.48,0:38:20.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.55,0:38:23.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,瞧这里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.22,0:38:28.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,昨天 伯鲁瑟过去的一个搭档在大法官面前作证
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.09,0:38:30.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我觉得他和大法官做了笔交易
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.93,0:38:32.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,迟早的事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.40,0:38:34.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 他会出卖伯鲁瑟 - 那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.31,0:38:38.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,到时你就得拍屁股走人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.75,0:38:40.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,走人？狄克 我才刚进来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.73,0:38:44.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是吗？嗯 事情也许会很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.81,0:38:47.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,贿赂陪审员 逃税
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.81,0:38:49.58,中文简体,,0,0,0,,敲竹杠 应有尽有
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.65,0:38:51.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我害怕 真的害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.35,0:38:54.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你怕什么呢？他们又不能抓你我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.35,0:38:56.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.62,0:38:59.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,假设他们带着传票和封条来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.62,0:39:00.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们可以这么干
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.96,0:39:03.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们在处理诈骗案时就这么干过
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.35,0:39:05.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们过来 没收所有文件
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.00,0:39:08.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,拿走所有的计算机 你手里还剩什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.26,0:39:09.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我并不担心被抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.04,0:39:11.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我担心我的饭碗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.60,0:39:14.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 那你说这些是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.27,0:39:15.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,开溜
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.95,0:39:19.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你有多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.75,0:39:22.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我我有五千五百美金
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.41,0:39:23.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.78,0:39:25.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们能租一个小办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.88,0:39:27.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,五百美金一月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.62,0:39:31.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们小本经营它六个月
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.04,0:39:33.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.86,0:39:35.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们平分一切 所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.78,0:39:37.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,全都五五开
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.17,0:39:42.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,开销 花费 利润 一切都对半开
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.51,0:39:46.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.08,0:39:49.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你不愿意和我合伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.84,0:39:52.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,啊 不是那意思 他们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.66,0:39:54.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不是那意思 只是你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.80,0:39:56.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你提得太突然
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.71,0:39:58.58,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 你得给我点儿时间 行不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.65,0:40:00.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是说 你不能说风就是雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.89,0:40:02.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们行动要快
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.36,0:40:08.96,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 那就动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.91,0:40:13.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们先干段时间看看
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.77,0:40:15.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你手里有几个案子？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.70,0:40:19.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 我 我有三个
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.46,0:40:21.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把它们拿出来 带回家
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.42,0:40:23.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可别让人抓住 明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.54,0:40:27.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有人监视我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.18,0:40:28.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,联邦政府
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.28,0:40:32.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我吃得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.03,0:41:03.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.42,0:41:07.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨 听着 今天早上我去了办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.67,0:41:09.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局把大门给封了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.00,0:41:11.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,伯鲁瑟到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.55,0:41:12.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我估计不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.97,0:41:14.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,伯鲁瑟和
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.34,0:41:15.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,普林斯已经被通缉了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.91,0:41:16.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.84,0:41:18.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,放松点儿 你可以
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.75,0:41:20.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不过是个提案 继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.88,0:41:22.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 我？- 对 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.25,0:41:23.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.35,0:41:25.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你熟悉这个案子 你会处理好的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.42,0:41:26.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,听我说 我还没领到执照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.71,0:41:28.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们用不着执照 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.13,0:41:38.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我对勃拉克的案子了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.15,0:41:41.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我读过所有法学书
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.24,0:41:43.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,了解取证和证物的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.64,0:41:45.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但当我环顾法庭
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.99,0:41:48.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我才明白自己还乳臭未干
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.57,0:41:54.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 先生 尊敬的法官 哦 呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.84,0:41:58.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我来参加 勃拉克状告巨大福利保险公司的听证
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.20,0:42:00.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.66,0:42:01.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 鲁迪拜勒
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.84,0:42:05.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我为简李曼斯通律师事务所工作
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.24,0:42:07.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 你为简李曼工作
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.84,0:42:14.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,斯涛切是烟草的忠实支持者
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.57,0:42:18.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,斯通先生在哪儿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.57,0:42:24.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,老实讲 尊敬的法官 我 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.66,0:42:26.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他本来该在这里和我汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.35,0:42:27.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但我不知道他现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.58,0:42:30.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 我倒不怎么奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.15,0:42:33.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么你想干什么？你想继续么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.35,0:42:34.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不是 尊敬的法官
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.66,0:42:37.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我 我准备参加提案的辩论
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.68,0:42:39.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是个律师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.41,0:42:42.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 我刚通过了律师执照考试
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.75,0:42:44.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而这些人 是我的委托人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.88,0:42:46.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,斯通先生 只是代理我提交诉讼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.95,0:42:48.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,以便等我通过执照考试
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.15,0:42:50.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哼 你怎么这么大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.15,0:42:52.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没有执照就敢迈进我的法庭
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.88,0:42:54.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,立即从这里滚出去 拿了执照
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.76,0:42:55.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,然后再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.08,0:42:57.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,去拿个执照！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.51,0:42:59.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,等你有了该死的执照再回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.55,0:43:01.67,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如果法庭许可
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.73,0:43:05.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是 莱奥 富楚门
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.04,0:43:07.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,来自霆雷博瑞特律师事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.87,0:43:09.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是巨大福利保险公司的法律顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.34,0:43:10.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我要说
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.84,0:43:14.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要是这个年轻人 已经通过了律师执照考试
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.41,0:43:16.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,尊敬的法官 就让他 参加本案的辩论吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.18,0:43:21.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们欢迎他加入律师的行业
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.29,0:43:23.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你没有意见吧 楚门先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.96,0:43:25.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如果法庭许可
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.13,0:43:29.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我将很荣幸 介绍拜勒先生
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.28,0:43:31.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,成为大田纳西州的实习律师
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.86,0:43:35.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官 您是可以现在就让他宣誓的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.15,0:43:37.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而我也很愿意支持他
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.00,0:43:40.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你确定你准备好了继续么 拜勒先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.82,0:43:43.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,绝对--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.59,0:43:45.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 尊敬的法官 是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.39,0:43:49.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很好 那么 举起你的右手
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.73,0:43:51.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是否庄严地宣誓 鲁迪拜勒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.67,0:43:54.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你将忠实地 正直地维护美国
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.06,0:43:57.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,和田纳西州的宪法和法律
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.27,0:43:59.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在职业中竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.34,0:44:02.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,尽心尽责么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.15,0:44:05.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.68,0:44:09.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 很好 那就让我们继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.18,0:44:10.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 恭喜 - 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.97,0:44:11.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,欢迎投入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.89,0:44:15.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,一个白痴主持宣誓 还有一个无赖来做担保
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.62,0:44:16.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哈维
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.62,0:44:17.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我终于是个律师了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.08,0:44:19.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.22,0:44:26.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请允许我 哈维？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.08,0:44:27.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.17,0:44:29.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.61,0:44:39.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这场官司让我很烦 拜勒先生
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.46,0:44:41.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不想用"无聊"这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.62,0:44:45.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,坦白地说 它没什么价值
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.91,0:44:49.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 我利用休闲时间
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.64,0:44:51.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,事实上 我真是厌倦了这类官司
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.12,0:44:53.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不是在推脱
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.22,0:44:57.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我倾向于驳回诉讼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.88,0:45:02.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,现在 你可以 向联邦法院提起上诉 明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.80,0:45:04.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,到别的地方去打这个官司
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.37,0:45:08.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别来烦我了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.09,0:45:11.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请原谅 我去一下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.46,0:45:12.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你也要去趟
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.82,0:45:17.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.37,0:45:21.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是个价码不菲的律师
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.26,0:45:24.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,属于一个价码不菲的律师事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.71,0:45:26.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我手里有很多案子要办
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.91,0:45:29.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,玩飞镖也没失过手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.04,0:45:31.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我告诉我的委托人 巨大福利保险公司
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.00,0:45:35.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,打这个官司要花很多的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.46,0:45:38.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而对于你和你的委托人 也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.55,0:45:41.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,现在 他们授权我
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.57,0:45:45.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,给你和你的委托人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.68,0:45:50.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,五万美元来和解这桩案子
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.17,0:45:54.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我甚至还可以让他们再加点
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.88,0:45:58.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,比如七万五千美元
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.98,0:46:02.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,然后就不再承担责任 你明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.60,0:46:05.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.22,0:46:07.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要是你拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.48,0:46:10.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么就会引发第三次世界大战
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.96,0:46:14.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,轮到我了 可以吧 哈唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.93,0:46:16.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.35,0:46:26.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我看这儿没多少官司好打 我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.26,0:46:30.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可也许我能依靠莱奥
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.31,0:46:31.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为和解出个价
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.17,0:46:33.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们也许愿意付些钱给你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.86,0:46:36.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,总比一分钟付莱奥好几千块划算
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.82,0:46:42.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可他已经代表辩方向我开价了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.46,0:46:45.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 真的吗？多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.16,0:46:48.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 七万五
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.48,0:46:52.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的天 嗯 仔细想想 我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.46,0:46:56.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你要是不接受的话 一定是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.51,0:46:58.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,您这么认为吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.15,0:47:00.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,七万五？天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.75,0:47:03.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这可是一大笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.08,0:47:05.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这可真不像是莱奥干的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.51,0:47:07.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 我也这么想 他是个大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.29,0:47:17.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.32,0:47:18.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,房间里没有在开会
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.79,0:47:20.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那是一场伏击
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.32,0:47:20.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.97,0:47:22.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们插标把我卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.31,0:47:23.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.42,0:47:24.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你以为他们敢这么对待伯鲁瑟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.80,0:47:26.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不会 伯鲁瑟太了解这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.33,0:47:28.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.75,0:47:30.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们许给我七万五
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.40,0:47:31.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好啊 接过来
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.08,0:47:34.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们应得的三分之一就是两万五 我们正需要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.93,0:47:36.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,海尔法官的态度是驳回上诉
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.02,0:47:38.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他又老又暴躁
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.81,0:47:40.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,大概是在那个位置时间久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.31,0:47:42.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我说 我们所能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.57,0:47:44.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就是减轻他父母的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.06,0:47:47.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,保险公司愿意出钱和解
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.14,0:47:49.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,什么价钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.88,0:47:52.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,七万五千美金
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.26,0:47:56.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们算过 那是打官司
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.40,0:47:58.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要付的律师费
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.33,0:48:02.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,该死的 他们以为这样就能收买我们
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.58,0:48:05.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们确实这么以为
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.46,0:48:11.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你最好和他谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.73,0:48:18.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你要和解吗 鲁迪？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.05,0:48:23.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 你能拿到其中一部份钱
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.91,0:48:29.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,决不
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.91,0:48:34.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想让他们曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.48,0:48:38.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,妈妈 能请给我一杯水吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.10,0:48:41.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.45,0:48:50.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不管你能从这个案子拿回什么
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.84,0:48:52.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,用它来照顾我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.42,0:48:57.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我真的爱他们
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.95,0:48:59.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我止不住要想
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.37,0:49:02.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们这些人 你争我夺 每日奔命
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.40,0:49:04.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好像我们永远都不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.31,0:49:06.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这个孩子却直视着它
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.13,0:49:08.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,独自与命运抗争
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.67,0:49:10.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我无法想象
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.47,0:49:12.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这要有多大的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.68,0:49:20.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.15,0:49:23.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,猜猜昨晚谁死了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.18,0:49:24.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.18,0:49:25.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你根本没睡过吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.04,0:49:27.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哈维 海尔
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.73,0:49:28.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,62岁
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.80,0:49:30.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,出身名门
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.66,0:49:31.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,海尔法官？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.64,0:49:33.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是他 心脏病突发
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.66,0:49:35.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,死在游泳池里
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.04,0:49:37.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.19,0:49:38.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯哼
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.20,0:49:39.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你一定是开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.35,0:49:41.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,猜猜新任法官
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.08,0:49:44.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如何处理巨大福利保险公司案？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.35,0:49:46.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,见鬼 这我怎么会知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.57,0:49:47.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,泰荣 开普勒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.91,0:49:50.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,黑人 哈佛毕业 民权捍卫者
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.62,0:49:52.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他不会支持霆雷-博瑞特律师事务所的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.88,0:49:54.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他对保险公司毫不留情
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.57,0:49:56.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他一直都在控诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.22,0:49:57.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们交好运了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.18,0:49:58.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,慢着 慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.13,0:49:59.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,小子 你知道什么是造雨人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.73,0:50:01.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,天上要掉钱了！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.72,0:50:03.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,现在是五点 你什么时候到？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.37,0:50:04.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,立马就到
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.69,0:50:06.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,赶快来 我们要讨论一下紧急上诉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.53,0:50:07.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.69,0:50:08.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.54,0:50:12.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,楚门先生
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.18,0:50:15.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你对这个案子的紧急上诉有异议
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.24,0:50:18.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,理由是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.20,0:50:20.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 尊敬的法官 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.19,0:50:23.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这个案子已被海尔大法官 裁决好了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.22,0:50:28.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我认为紧急上诉所需的准备工作
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.70,0:50:31.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对于当事人双方 都是不必要的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.91,0:50:33.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.35,0:50:36.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想问问你 楚门先生
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.97,0:50:38.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,作为一个辩护律师
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.48,0:50:42.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你以前是否同意过紧急上诉案件？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.75,0:50:44.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 尊敬的法官 我想我同意过
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.00,0:50:47.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.18,0:50:49.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哪件案子 在哪个法庭审理的？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.13,0:50:53.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.46,0:50:54.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 尊敬的法官
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.84,0:50:56.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我得回去找一下才能告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.33,0:50:59.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 下午三点前给我电话
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.49,0:51:03.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想三点钟之前我到不了办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.63,0:51:06.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 好吧 等你到办公室后 就给我个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.23,0:51:10.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我很想了解你同意紧急上诉的那个案子
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.48,0:51:11.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.40,0:51:14.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那个孩子正面临死亡 先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.74,0:51:17.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你们同意我们去为他的证词录音么
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.78,0:51:19.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.25,0:51:20.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然 尊敬的法官
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.97,0:51:22.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只不过 我的日程安排得相当紧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.25,0:51:27.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,下周四下午怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.49,0:51:29.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我没问题 尊敬的法官
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.16,0:51:32.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不行 尊敬的法官
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.66,0:51:34.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,还有整整一个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.26,0:51:36.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我可能要外出
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.84,0:51:38.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对的 星期四我得到外地去
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.30,0:51:43.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,取证时间就定在
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.94,0:51:46.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,下周四下午两点
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.84,0:51:49.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,假如辩方不大不方便 那对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.94,0:51:54.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但你们应该还有其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.98,0:51:56.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好了 下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.02,0:51:58.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 哦 尊敬的法官
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.75,0:52:01.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,驳回上诉的请求还悬而未决
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.15,0:52:04.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.19,0:52:07.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那个请求已被否决了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.60,0:52:08.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.68,0:52:10.50,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想结论就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.28,0:52:13.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,先生们 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.00,0:52:15.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,尊敬的法官 祝贺您的上任
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.97,0:52:17.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.04,0:52:21.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,楚门先生
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.62,0:52:25.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别忘了打电话告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.00,0:52:28.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你同意了哪个案子的紧急上诉
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.33,0:52:30.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我会找的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.91,0:52:42.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你知道怎么做了吧 我的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.60,0:52:46.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,绝对是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.25,0:52:53.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,狄克想在当地饶舌音乐电台做个广告
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.00,0:52:55.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,虽然我一直爱听那个台 但我们负不起广告费
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.93,0:52:59.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,家具 出庭费 传真机花了七百五
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.73,0:53:01.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,租电脑花了四百块
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.91,0:53:03.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,一辆二手车交完首付
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.13,0:53:05.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们一文不名了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.09,0:53:09.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,狄克说 他对这种运作很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.94,0:53:41.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪 嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.27,0:53:42.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨 达特
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.47,0:53:44.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请进 你好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.94,0:53:46.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我很好 你好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.44,0:53:47.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.68,0:53:50.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,听我说 星期三晚上我要到克利夫兰去
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.48,0:53:51.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,巨大福利保险公司的总部在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.82,0:53:54.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我要收集所有董事的证词
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.29,0:53:56.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.62,0:53:58.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不用担心开销
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.35,0:53:59.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们会处理的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.86,0:54:02.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你 鲁迪 - 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.51,0:54:07.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,真不好用
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.67,0:54:12.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是我的合伙人 狄克谢佛来尔
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.31,0:54:13.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 你好 - 嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.02,0:54:27.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.22,0:54:29.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,泰荣来了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.82,0:54:31.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.35,0:54:32.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,大法官到了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.37,0:54:35.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哎 等一下 达特 把这给我
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.36,0:54:37.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.82,0:54:40.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.02,0:54:41.96,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.13,0:54:43.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.26,0:54:45.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.11,0:54:46.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是勃拉克女士
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.31,0:54:47.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他就是大法官泰荣 开普勒
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.82,0:54:49.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,非常荣幸见到您
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.37,0:54:50.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,应该是我感到荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.33,0:54:53.78,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 哦 请过来
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.44,0:54:56.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这地方太小
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.40,0:54:57.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,挤得很
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.73,0:54:58.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们到室外去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.60,0:55:01.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你可以吗 我的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.52,0:55:04.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然 可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.71,0:55:06.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.52,0:55:07.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.11,0:55:22.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我看着每小时赚一千美金的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.62,0:55:24.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,律师班子
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.02,0:55:26.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我恨他们
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.80,0:55:28.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们居高临下
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.48,0:55:31.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对整个司法体系肆意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.40,0:55:35.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我以前恨他们 是因为我不是对手
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.40,0:55:38.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而现在 是因为他们代表的人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.41,0:55:40.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,和行为
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.84,0:55:42.36,中文简体,,0,0,0,,尊敬的法官 您好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.43,0:55:43.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很好 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.49,0:55:45.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但愿这些狗没有吓着你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.50,0:55:46.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们要在室外采集证据
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.93,0:55:48.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,室内稍微挤了点
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.26,0:55:49.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,找个位子坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.68,0:55:50.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.75,0:55:52.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 你好 - 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.20,0:56:12.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.42,0:56:20.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你好吗 丹尼雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.82,0:56:23.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.68,0:56:26.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你已经见过大法官开普勒了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.84,0:56:27.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.70,0:56:30.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是 莱奥富楚门
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.77,0:56:32.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,和他的同事们
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.36,0:56:36.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是谭密 她是法庭书记员
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.86,0:56:38.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.87,0:56:40.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让他起誓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.75,0:56:42.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是否发誓 你将给出的证词
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.06,0:56:44.67,中文简体,,0,0,0,,都是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.74,0:56:46.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只有事实 绝无虚假
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.22,0:56:47.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是 我起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.66,0:56:54.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我告诉过他了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.71,0:56:56.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道过来 过来 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.26,0:56:58.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别担心 别担心 这只是个听证
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.72,0:57:00.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,丹尼雷 我是莱奥楚门
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.66,0:57:02.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我代表巨大福利保险公司
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.84,0:57:04.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我非常非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.61,0:57:06.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.24,0:57:07.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在这种情形之下来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.26,0:57:09.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 我们本不该坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.31,0:57:11.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只要你的委托人做了他们份内之事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.86,0:57:13.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起 我没听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.51,0:57:15.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嘿 孩子 要块口香糖吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.28,0:57:16.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 当然了 - 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.28,0:57:18.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你胳膊断了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.57,0:57:19.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.62,0:57:21.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你遭遇事故了？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.12,0:57:22.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,干嘛问哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.09,0:57:24.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 我是个律师 并且 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.26,0:57:26.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把这交给你的母亲 您是他母亲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.76,0:57:29.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这种意外事故 也许我能帮你们找回些钱来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.31,0:57:45.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,帮忙介绍下好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.00,0:57:48.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的 我先帮一下这位先生
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.29,0:57:50.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 不不 我来 这样挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.46,0:57:57.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我能为您做点儿什么 先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.29,0:57:58.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 我只是看看
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.83,0:58:23.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,旁边有家电影院
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.30,0:58:25.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,买张后排 中间的票
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.31,0:58:26.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我三十分钟后到
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.31,0:58:29.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.51,0:59:09.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,克利夫想让我生个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.69,0:59:15.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那 你得做个决定
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.52,0:59:19.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他跟着了迷似的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.56,0:59:21.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他认为这样 就能把我们栓在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.89,0:59:24.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,听我说 我真的不想讨论这些
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.17,0:59:28.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我只是想见见你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.03,1:00:17.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,去克利夫兰的一路上 我好像都能闻到她的香水味
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.07,1:00:21.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这让我无法集中精力去想 莱奥楚门的那帮人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.30,1:00:23.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们会乘头等舱飞过来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.67,1:00:25.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,酒足饭饱之后
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.37,1:00:26.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在某个会议室里碰头
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.57,1:00:28.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,商量怎么来对付我
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.21,1:00:31.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当我在汽车旅馆开房间的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.25,1:00:33.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们却正在高级套房里呼呼大睡
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.82,1:00:36.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,养精蓄锐之后
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.38,1:00:37.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,准备开战
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.35,1:00:40.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是我要的听证会
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.39,1:00:42.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,却在他们的地盘上举行
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.73,1:00:45.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,啊 年轻的鲁迪拜勒
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.23,1:00:46.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,真是准时
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.70,1:00:47.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,楚门先生
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.70,1:00:49.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,泰勒 给这个孩子弄杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.76,1:00:50.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,贾克安德豪尔
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.80,1:00:51.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪拜勒
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.83,1:00:53.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,年轻律师永远是饥渴的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.60,1:00:55.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这些都是理赔部和保险受理部的人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.37,1:00:58.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这张桌子边 一定聚集了上百年的法律经验
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.82,1:01:02.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而我的搭档 却考了六次律师执照考试都失败了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.61,1:01:04.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,噢 鲁迪 别让
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.08,1:01:06.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,桌子这边这么多人给吓着
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.35,1:01:08.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我保证 要是你在高尔夫球场 碰到他们
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.66,1:01:10.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你一定能打败他们
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.59,1:01:14.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让我们看看这是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.33,1:01:17.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想也许该从
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.61,1:01:20.58,中文简体,,0,0,0,,公司设计师贾克安德豪尔
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.06,1:01:22.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这里开始是合适的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.06,1:01:24.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我 我并不这样认为
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.32,1:01:26.58,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.65,1:01:27.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你听清楚了的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.75,1:01:30.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想从贾奇莱曼奇科开始 她是索赔处理人员
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.33,1:01:39.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我觉得最好还是 从安德豪尔先生开始
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.11,1:01:42.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我应该得到尊重 楚门先生
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.88,1:01:43.58,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是我要求的听证会
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.65,1:01:46.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我得按我认为合适的顺序 召见这些证人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.57,1:01:49.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所以最好是从贾奇莱曼奇科开始
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.51,1:01:54.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也许我们需要打个电话给大法官
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.48,1:01:59.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 我不认为这么一大早
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.42,1:02:00.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们就得开始厮杀
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.24,1:02:03.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我没有想要和你厮杀
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.29,1:02:06.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们只是有那么点儿小问题
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.62,1:02:08.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,关于贾奇莱曼奇科
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.80,1:02:10.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 这位波兰女士身上
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.66,1:02:12.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,什么样的问题呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.50,1:02:16.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她已经不在这里工作了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.47,1:02:18.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她被开除了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.33,1:02:22.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她辞职了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.77,1:02:25.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 那么 她现在在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.20,1:02:30.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她不再为我们的委托人工作 所以 嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.42,1:02:33.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们不能再把她作为证人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.40,1:02:37.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让我们继续下去
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.06,1:02:40.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 鲁塞尔 克劳凯特
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.06,1:02:43.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在座的谁是 鲁塞尔克劳凯特？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.90,1:02:47.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他也离开了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.97,1:02:49.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,被裁员了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.60,1:02:51.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,裁员？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.51,1:02:53.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.44,1:02:55.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们的委托人进行了 阶段性的裁员
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.91,1:02:57.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是啊 这难免的 不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.92,1:03:07.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么艾沃特 鲁富肯
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.40,1:03:09.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那个理赔部副总经理呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.96,1:03:11.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他也被裁员了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.79,1:03:14.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 他在这儿
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.43,1:03:19.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是 艾沃特 鲁富肯？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.31,1:03:23.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我祝贺你
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.62,1:03:26.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁富肯先生
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.88,1:03:28.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在巨大福利保险公司的大屠杀中
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.71,1:03:30.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,奇迹般地幸存下来
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.13,1:03:42.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我也许没有百分百的努力 但我精神抖擞
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.48,1:03:49.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我很好奇
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.62,1:03:51.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好奇什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.60,1:03:54.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我只想知道
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.17,1:03:58.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你还记得是什么时候第一次出卖自己的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.34,1:04:08.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你小子很狂啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.55,1:04:13.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我建议你注意礼貌
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.15,1:04:15.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你可是律师
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.72,1:04:17.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你在乎我的态度？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.59,1:04:21.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我大老远从孟菲斯来
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.80,1:04:24.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,来为四个人取证
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.80,1:04:26.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,居然有两个不在
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.15,1:04:29.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而你让我注意礼貌？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.53,1:04:31.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这个 是你运气不好
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.77,1:04:33.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么样啊 小子？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.94,1:04:37.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我要从他那里取证
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.68,1:04:39.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,坐那里的那位 拉佛金先生
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.91,1:04:41.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,然后我会收拾行李
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.55,1:04:43.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,回孟菲斯去
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.79,1:04:49.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没有保险的人就这么死去
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.75,1:04:52.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有这么多好医生
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.26,1:04:54.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,科技如此发达
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.26,1:04:57.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就这么让这个孩子死去 太可耻了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.96,1:04:59.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他有保单在身
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.93,1:05:02.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她母亲也付了保险金
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.30,1:05:05.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也许钱不是很多 但是足够了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.30,1:05:07.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我在这个案子中孤立无援
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.95,1:05:10.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我被人耍 我也很怕
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.74,1:05:12.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是我是正确的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.02,1:05:15.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我坐在这个可怜的孩子旁边 看着他受苦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.17,1:05:18.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我发誓 一定要报复
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.83,1:05:30.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.80,1:05:32.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪 是我
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.30,1:05:33.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.80,1:05:36.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,求你帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.33,1:05:38.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.30,1:05:39.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,店里
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.80,1:05:42.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好 待那里别动 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.35,1:05:43.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我马上就来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.34,1:05:44.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.96,1:06:01.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是鲁迪贝勒
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.86,1:06:06.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.37,1:06:14.50,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你能来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.37,1:06:26.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,发生什么事？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.71,1:06:28.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,快点 让他看看
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.64,1:06:46.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我扶着你呢 别怕
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.94,1:06:50.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪 我真高兴你能打电话来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.38,1:06:51.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,快进来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.88,1:06:53.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可怜的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.88,1:06:55.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我会照顾你的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.91,1:06:57.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.05,1:07:00.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别担心 我们能应付
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.08,1:07:02.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的 你知道在哪儿找我
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.62,1:07:04.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,知道 知道
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.11,1:07:07.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我对自己说 我一定要尽我所能
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.51,1:07:08.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把她拯救出来
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.06,1:07:11.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不然 那家伙肯定会把她打死
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.08,1:07:13.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.40,1:07:36.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.07,1:07:39.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他本来死不了的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.91,1:07:41.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.28,1:07:42.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,迭克
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.45,1:07:51.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,多特 我真难过
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.10,1:08:43.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,真谢谢你能来
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.51,1:08:45.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.22,1:09:16.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,会没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.46,1:09:24.36,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.52,1:09:32.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,窃听器？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.58,1:09:56.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.91,1:09:58.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.25,1:09:59.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.05,1:10:02.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这个窃听器
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.55,1:10:05.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有中级电路
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.59,1:10:09.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可以传送很微弱的信号
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.89,1:10:14.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可能是捷克制的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.08,1:10:18.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我认为警察或者联邦调查局不会用这种型号
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.90,1:10:23.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,肯定是其他什么人在窃听
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.07,1:10:25.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,还有谁想窃听我们？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.57,1:10:28.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想到了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.75,1:10:33.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.13,1:10:34.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.15,1:10:36.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我只是随便打个电话
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.08,1:10:38.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 你要我从城里带什么吗？- 不用
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.12,1:10:41.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嘿 猜猜谁打算庭外和解了？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.12,1:10:42.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.29,1:10:43.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,多特布莱克
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.79,1:10:45.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,多特布莱克？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.49,1:10:47.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我今天过去了一下
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.13,1:10:48.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,顺便看了看她
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.71,1:10:50.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我给她买了个水果蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.60,1:10:53.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她说已经没有力气
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.60,1:10:56.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,打这种耗时的官司了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.14,1:10:57.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.11,1:10:58.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她要多少？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.11,1:10:59.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她说17万5就行
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.04,1:11:01.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该同意
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.81,1:11:04.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,先这么着吧 明天见
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.66,1:11:05.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 不过我建议你同意
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.98,1:11:07.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我知道 我听见你的话了 我想想看
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.78,1:11:08.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 再见
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.95,1:11:11.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.15,1:11:13.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.49,1:11:16.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这个家庭已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.79,1:11:19.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我觉得那女人会接受庭外和解的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.53,1:11:22.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我会问问她的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.08,1:11:26.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你现在就给她打电话吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.35,1:11:28.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我就在这等着
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.62,1:11:30.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好 我一会打给你 德拉门德先生
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.82,1:11:32.36,中文简体,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.32,1:11:45.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我对这男孩的死很难过
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.32,1:11:49.36,中文简体,,0,0,0,,听着 我的客户 呃
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.42,1:11:50.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,想要和解 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.36,1:11:52.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们这么说吧 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.83,1:11:55.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只是讨论一下数目而已
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.33,1:11:56.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,假设这个保险被赔付了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.86,1:11:59.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的客户大概要付
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.83,1:12:02.50,中文简体,,0,0,0,,15万到17万5的样子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.37,1:12:05.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你这么认为？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.42,1:12:06.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们的确窃听了我们的电话
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.94,1:12:09.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的确这么认为 所以 呃 我们打算给你们
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.88,1:12:12.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我看我们该 告诉开普勒法官这事
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.68,1:12:15.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 我反对
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.77,1:12:16.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.75,1:12:21.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我有个主意
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.52,1:12:25.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有点疯狂的主意
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.60,1:12:27.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,妨碍司法公正？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.40,1:12:28.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这样
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.70,1:12:31.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这样
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.00,1:12:33.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们最大的恶梦是谁？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.60,1:12:36.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官给了我们陪审团的预选名单
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.37,1:12:38.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,一共92人
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.88,1:12:40.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们调查了他们的背景
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.44,1:12:42.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,确定了他们对我们有利还是不利
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.71,1:12:44.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你打算让我怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.41,1:12:45.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 好吧 - 什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.00,1:12:48.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,任何与他们的直接接触 毫无疑问就是犯罪
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.68,1:12:50.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们在干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.84,1:12:52.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们要这么做
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.22,1:12:54.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 照我说的做 - 好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.76,1:12:59.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.95,1:13:02.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对 我找鲁迪贝勒
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.51,1:13:04.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我就是
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.31,1:13:07.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是比利波特
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.42,1:13:09.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你今天来我店里了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.24,1:13:10.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 波特先生
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.81,1:13:12.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很感谢你给我回电话
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.20,1:13:14.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你要干什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.28,1:13:17.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,呃 和一个案子有关
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.68,1:13:19.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你知道的 你是那个案子的陪审团成员
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.60,1:13:20.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是那个案子一方的律师
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.93,1:13:23.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,呃 这这合法吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.08,1:13:25.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,呃 当然 当然合法 波特先生
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.94,1:13:28.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不过千万别告诉其他人
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.53,1:13:31.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我代表那位女士 她孩子死了 是白血病
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.22,1:13:34.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而这都是因为 巨大利益保险公司
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.22,1:13:36.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不给他们动手术的钱
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.28,1:13:39.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 天啊 这太恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.95,1:13:42.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我也有个婶婶得这个病
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.27,1:13:45.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,花了很多钱 我叔叔很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.44,1:13:50.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我会尽力的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.11,1:13:50.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的 先生
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.97,1:13:53.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢您 波特先生 祝你下午愉快
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.61,1:13:55.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.38,1:13:57.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那个 那个婶婶是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.60,1:13:58.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那婶婶是哪冒出来的？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.97,1:13:59.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.96,1:14:01.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你让我装得同情些嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.46,1:14:03.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我知道 可是你也不用说这么详细吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.00,1:14:05.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,拿着你的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.46,1:14:06.96,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们回去
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.16,1:14:09.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我只是想帮忙而已
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.00,1:14:10.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.97,1:14:12.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我就在你后面
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.50,1:14:16.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.53,1:14:18.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我下面要问的问题
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.77,1:14:21.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是今天最重要的问题
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.48,1:14:23.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不过也很简单
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.01,1:14:25.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,回答是或否就行
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.66,1:14:28.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请听仔细
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.85,1:14:32.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你们是否有人已经就此案被联系过？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.46,1:14:36.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是非常严重的事件
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.04,1:14:38.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.01,1:14:41.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们现在要知道
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.68,1:14:44.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让我换种方法提问吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.45,1:14:49.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你们之中是否有人最近与
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.64,1:14:51.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪贝勒先生
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.96,1:14:54.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,或者他后面那位迭克席夫列特先生谈过话？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.31,1:14:55.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对 法官大人！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.69,1:14:56.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是侮辱！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.00,1:14:58.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你在做什么 德拉门德先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.15,1:15:00.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.35,1:15:01.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们有证据表明
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.82,1:15:03.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有人试图控制陪审团
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.42,1:15:05.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他说的是我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.68,1:15:07.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不明白你在做什么 德拉门德先生
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.08,1:15:09.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我也不知道 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.51,1:15:10.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.51,1:15:12.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请上前
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.33,1:15:18.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人 有人试图控制陪审团
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.50,1:15:19.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我要证据 立奥
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.82,1:15:22.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不能
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.54,1:15:24.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,泄露秘密情报 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.27,1:15:25.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.37,1:15:26.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你看起来不正常
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.01,1:15:28.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 我能证明的 - 怎么证明？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.05,1:15:31.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,控告我们这种罪名
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.01,1:15:33.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,控制陪审团
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.38,1:15:34.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,真可笑
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.98,1:15:36.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请允许我先问完陪审团
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.02,1:15:38.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我相信您会明白事实的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.69,1:15:40.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你反对吗 贝勒先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.29,1:15:42.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 我不反对
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.80,1:15:44.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那好 继续
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.33,1:15:46.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.83,1:15:51.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.68,1:15:53.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没什么 律师的小伎俩
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.04,1:15:56.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,波特先生
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.46,1:16:00.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想直接问你个问题
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.64,1:16:03.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我希望你
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.73,1:16:05.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可以诚实地回答我
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.35,1:16:08.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只要你的问题是诚实的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.62,1:16:09.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我就诚实地回答
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.13,1:16:11.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.14,1:16:14.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,波特先生 几天前你有没有
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.27,1:16:16.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,和鲁迪贝勒先生
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.51,1:16:17.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,通过电话吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.94,1:16:19.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,废话 当然没有
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.31,1:16:22.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我本以为你会给我个诚实的回答
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.68,1:16:24.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我就是实话实说
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.35,1:16:26.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你肯定吗 波特先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.15,1:16:28.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我非常肯定
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.06,1:16:30.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,波特先生
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.14,1:16:31.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在法庭上
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.57,1:16:33.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在美国法庭上
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.34,1:16:35.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在田纳西州公正的法庭上
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.68,1:16:37.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我说你在说谎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.64,1:16:39.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你怎么敢说我说谎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.30,1:16:40.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,德拉门德先生
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.48,1:16:42.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你个婊子养的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.55,1:16:46.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嘿 把他拉出去！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.15,1:16:47.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,保持法庭秩序！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.42,1:16:50.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,贝立夫
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.96,1:16:52.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把波特先生带出法庭
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.89,1:16:56.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,比利波特先生 你被驱逐出陪审团了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.85,1:17:00.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.51,1:17:03.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我要求解散整个陪审团
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.99,1:17:07.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,否决
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.24,1:17:08.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,陪审团已经被控制了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.18,1:17:17.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.55,1:17:21.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你掉了你的鞋
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.29,1:17:25.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们可以按现在的陪审团
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.93,1:17:28.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,继续吗 德拉门德先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.68,1:17:32.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可以 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.30,1:17:34.67,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.64,1:17:59.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们今天就提出诉讼
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.68,1:18:00.78,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他会疯的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.85,1:18:01.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他已经疯了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.75,1:18:04.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他会干掉你的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.28,1:18:06.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我正盼着呢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.15,1:18:08.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这火鸡烤的不错
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.37,1:18:13.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我 我得去法庭了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.28,1:18:15.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我已经迟到了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.68,1:18:17.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你的三明治怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.20,1:18:19.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我边走边吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.73,1:18:21.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.02,1:18:23.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,待会见
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.42,1:18:25.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,再见？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.90,1:18:35.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.35,1:18:38.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,克立佛去吃午饭时 我把文件给他了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.20,1:18:41.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他说他要打架
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.64,1:18:42.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我说 打群架的人我有的是
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.88,1:18:43.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他就软了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.95,1:18:46.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不过 老兄 你最好小心点
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.28,1:18:50.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.66,1:18:52.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 布奇 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.75,1:18:54.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你庄严宣誓
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.06,1:18:57.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你下面要做的证供
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.39,1:18:58.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,全部都是事实
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.49,1:19:00.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没有丝毫谎言吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.46,1:19:01.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 我宣誓
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.76,1:19:03.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你可以作证了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.65,1:19:12.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请告诉法庭你的名字 以便记录
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.68,1:19:16.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,玛嘉丽布莱克夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.45,1:19:19.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好 布莱克夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.12,1:19:21.36,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是丹尼雷布莱克的母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.43,1:19:23.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你儿子是否最近因白血病而死去
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.76,1:19:24.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而这些都是因为被告 巨大福利保险公司
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.00,1:19:26.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.40,1:19:27.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,诱导证人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.60,1:19:31.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对有效
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.12,1:19:35.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.55,1:19:38.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 丹尼雷 需要做手术 - 反对
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.43,1:19:39.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,诱导证人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.17,1:19:41.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对有效
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.73,1:19:46.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,布莱克夫人 你买这个医疗保险
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.40,1:19:48.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是不是想要为你的儿子提供医疗保障？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.79,1:19:49.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.79,1:19:50.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.22,1:19:52.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,诱导证人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.62,1:19:54.79,中文简体,,0,0,0,,贝勒先生
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.20,1:19:56.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你干嘛不出示一下保单
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.66,1:19:57.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,然后问问她 干嘛要买这个？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.17,1:19:58.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.66,1:20:04.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,贝勒先生
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.62,1:20:06.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你必须先得到许可 才能上前询问证人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.73,1:20:09.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.66,1:20:12.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我请求询问证人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.68,1:20:13.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.31,1:20:19.50,中文简体,,0,0,0,,放轻松点
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.57,1:20:22.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,放轻松点
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.27,1:20:25.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,巨大利益保险公司 1996年7月7日
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.54,1:20:34.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,回复 7849909886号保单
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.15,1:20:36.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,亲爱的布莱克夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.48,1:20:38.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,本公司已经7次
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.72,1:20:42.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,以书面方式拒绝了你的赔付要求
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.59,1:20:48.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是第八次拒绝 也是最后一次
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.23,1:20:53.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你实在是蠢 蠢 蠢！
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.77,1:20:57.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,诚挚的 埃佛莱特拉佛金
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.20,1:20:59.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,理赔部副总经理
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.59,1:21:03.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请再读一遍
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.76,1:21:04.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.96,1:21:06.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,无意义的重复 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.40,1:21:07.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对有效
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.51,1:21:10.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我问完了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.86,1:21:13.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,德拉门德先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.10,1:21:14.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.17,1:21:17.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请收起那个投影
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.15,1:21:20.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,现在 布莱克夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.02,1:21:25.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把它关掉
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.97,1:21:31.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,布莱克夫人 你为什么要控告巨大福利保险公司
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.91,1:21:33.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,索赔1000万美元呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.78,1:21:35.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就这么点吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.55,1:21:38.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起 您说什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.68,1:21:41.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我认为该索赔更多呢
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.62,1:21:42.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.71,1:21:45.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 先生 你的委托人有十亿美元
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.06,1:21:47.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而且你的委托人杀了我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.69,1:21:50.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我打算索赔更多
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.35,1:21:54.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你拿这笔钱打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.11,1:21:57.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如果陪审团判给你1000万
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.11,1:21:58.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么花？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.62,1:22:01.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我会把它们捐给美国白血病研究学会
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.55,1:22:03.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,全部捐掉
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.68,1:22:08.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不要你的臭钱
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.46,1:22:12.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请注意你是宣誓过的 布莱克夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.86,1:22:15.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请求上前盘问证人 法官大人？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.35,1:22:16.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.35,1:22:19.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,布莱克夫人 我希望你可以读一下保单
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.74,1:22:23.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,第16页 第K项 第14段 第E款
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.08,1:22:25.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,保险公司
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.44,1:22:27.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,用浅显的英语说
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.08,1:22:30.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,它不负责赔付实验性治疗
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.37,1:22:33.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你的起诉书中说
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.42,1:22:35.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如果你的儿子接受骨髓移植
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.59,1:22:36.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他就能够得救
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.99,1:22:38.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,布莱克夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.06,1:22:40.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,美国每年这种骨髓移植
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.52,1:22:42.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只有七千次
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.08,1:22:45.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而田纳西州只有不到200次
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.75,1:22:46.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.98,1:22:48.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他诱导证人
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.25,1:22:50.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是在互证 诱导是允许的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.28,1:22:52.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就诱导而言
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.62,1:22:54.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对无效
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.59,1:22:59.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所以这不是保单赔付范围
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.09,1:23:00.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,还有 布莱克夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.16,1:23:02.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谁是
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.96,1:23:06.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谁第一个诊断你儿子病情的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.52,1:23:09.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,最开始
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.22,1:23:12.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是贝奇医生
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.06,1:23:15.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你的家庭医生？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.73,1:23:17.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 先生
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.19,1:23:18.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他是个好医生吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.66,1:23:20.36,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他是个很好的医生
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.37,1:23:22.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么 布莱克夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.00,1:23:24.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这个诚恳而能力卓著的医生
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.50,1:23:28.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是不是反复告诉过你
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.46,1:23:29.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为你儿子所患的白血病类型特殊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.56,1:23:32.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,骨髓移植对你儿子的病情不利？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.93,1:23:35.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.76,1:23:37.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他没有说过
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.15,1:23:38.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他没这么说过
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.18,1:23:40.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他不是那么对我说的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.25,1:23:43.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请求上前询问证人 法官大人？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.49,1:23:44.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.32,1:23:50.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,布莱克夫人 这是不是贝奇医生的信签？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.73,1:23:53.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他是不是在底下签字了？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.80,1:23:55.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.63,1:23:57.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.10,1:23:58.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为他不能这么
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.17,1:24:00.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,提出证据 更何况那只是道听途说
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.47,1:24:02.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.37,1:24:06.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,布莱克家庭医生给德拉门德先生的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.34,1:24:08.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,信是不可接受的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.48,1:24:10.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很正确 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.45,1:24:12.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我没有要求此信
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.35,1:24:13.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,被作为呈堂证供
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.82,1:24:16.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我只是想知道 证人是否
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.52,1:24:17.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可以读一下这封信
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.65,1:24:19.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是根据田纳西州
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.46,1:24:20.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,取证法第612条
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.79,1:24:22.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是为了让她恢复回忆
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.66,1:24:25.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,贝勒先生 你觉得呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.16,1:24:26.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不知道 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.80,1:24:27.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但我反对这样
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.00,1:24:31.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而且在预审举证时
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.84,1:24:33.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这封信并未被提出
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.30,1:24:35.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对此你有何解释 德拉门德先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.84,1:24:37.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我当时不知道会用到这封信
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.64,1:24:39.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我本来以为这位女士 会真实的告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.39,1:24:41.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她的医生对她说了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.05,1:24:45.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,还有什么事吗 贝勒先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.28,1:24:48.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.89,1:24:52.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,德拉门德先生
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.12,1:24:54.79,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不反对
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.86,1:24:56.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是最好别扯太远了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.93,1:24:58.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没问题 法官大人 现在 布莱克夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.18,1:25:01.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这封信有没有让你回忆起
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.82,1:25:04.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,丹尼雷的那种白血病类型
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.12,1:25:05.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,到底能不能通过
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.49,1:25:06.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,骨髓移植治疗呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.72,1:25:08.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可是 他不是专家
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.93,1:25:10.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但他是持照医师
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.09,1:25:13.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很有经验 年富力强
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.56,1:25:16.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而且反覆告诉过你
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.25,1:25:19.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你理智上无法接受的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.52,1:25:22.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不管怎么治疗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.42,1:25:25.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你的儿子仍然会因为白血病而死
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.29,1:25:26.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.72,1:25:29.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是他不是这方面的专家
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.36,1:25:30.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不相信他
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.83,1:25:33.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不仅是信不信他的问题 夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.96,1:25:35.58,中文简体,,0,0,0,,更重要的是你失去了我
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.65,1:25:37.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,及陪审团的信任
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.79,1:25:39.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你可是发过誓的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.30,1:25:42.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,刚才你说贝奇医生没有说过
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.37,1:25:44.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你儿子的白血病类型
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.63,1:25:46.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,无法通过骨髓移植治疗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.09,1:25:48.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我相信你的原话是
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.23,1:25:50.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他没这么说过
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.46,1:25:51.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他不是那么
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.67,1:25:53.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对我说的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.50,1:25:55.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他不是专家
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.47,1:25:58.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我只是希望丹尼雷
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.84,1:26:02.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可以接受最好的治疗
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.02,1:26:06.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,换了你 也会这么做的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.70,1:26:08.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然 夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.48,1:26:11.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.94,1:26:13.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我问完了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.97,1:26:17.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你可以退席了 布莱克夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.00,1:26:27.78,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是不是做的不好？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.85,1:26:29.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 不 你做的很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.62,1:26:31.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没关系 陪审团会
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.88,1:26:34.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,明确知道他想干什么的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.28,1:26:35.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,陪审团会知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.93,1:26:36.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想抽烟
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.96,1:26:37.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我知道你需要
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.93,1:26:38.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们过会再抽
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.45,1:26:44.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我希望他没有换过锁
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.00,1:26:47.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你害怕吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.60,1:26:49.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.22,1:26:52.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们干吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.75,1:27:21.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,真成猪窝了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.42,1:27:23.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.69,1:27:26.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,快点 凯莉 快点
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.85,1:27:31.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的东西基本都在衣橱里
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.01,1:27:42.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这儿的东西你是拿不光的 凯莉
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.89,1:28:00.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 不
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.89,1:28:03.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嘿 你好啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.46,1:28:05.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我回家啦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.90,1:28:07.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哇 真没想到？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.87,1:28:10.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,看看什么人来了？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.50,1:28:12.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你们俩在这里干嘛 啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.41,1:28:14.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嘿 别激动 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.29,1:28:14.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,过来 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.37,1:28:16.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是你的丈夫 还记得吗 啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.45,1:28:17.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,老兄 放轻松点
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.11,1:28:18.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.48,1:28:19.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嘿 听着 别激动
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.86,1:28:20.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我才不听你废话呢！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.86,1:28:22.67,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别激动
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.08,1:28:24.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你让我心痛啊 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.51,1:28:25.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你让我很难受
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.00,1:28:28.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你干嘛要这么对我？！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.44,1:28:30.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 克立佛！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.15,1:28:36.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.43,1:29:11.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪 鲁迪！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.16,1:29:12.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,克立佛！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.23,1:29:13.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋 你在干嘛？！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.37,1:29:14.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你看到了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.53,1:29:15.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,凯莉！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.02,1:29:17.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这就是你想要的？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.02,1:29:19.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不是我的错哦！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.22,1:29:21.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是爱你的！我爱你！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.94,1:29:35.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.18,1:29:42.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别打了 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.81,1:29:44.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别打
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.32,1:29:48.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,给我那根棒子 快走
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.60,1:29:50.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.82,1:29:54.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,给我那根棒子 快走
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.22,1:29:56.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你今天晚上没有来过
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.89,1:29:58.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,给我那根棒子
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.18,1:30:14.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,快走 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.21,1:30:16.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你今天晚上没有来过
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.28,1:30:55.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他最终杀了她
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.25,1:30:57.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 是男的死了 她把他杀了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.25,1:30:58.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你肯定？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.36,1:30:59.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我刚刚看过她的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.39,1:31:00.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,怎么发生的？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.62,1:31:01.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.69,1:31:03.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有人说 当你谋杀一个人时
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.46,1:31:04.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你起码犯了25项错误
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.83,1:31:07.96,中文简体,,0,0,0,,过后 你要是能记住其中5项就不错了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.03,1:31:09.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是自卫行为
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.17,1:31:11.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是我没法忘记他死了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.27,1:31:13.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这个错误充斥了我的大脑
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.77,1:31:15.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我没法思考了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.24,1:31:18.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是凯莉知道
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.51,1:31:20.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她知道该做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.14,1:31:21.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她知道这是好机会
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.37,1:31:24.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当那些事情
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.62,1:31:26.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,一起发生的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.45,1:31:28.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她只想到我的安全
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.24,1:31:33.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而我把她一个人扔在那里
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.59,1:31:36.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,该死的！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.44,1:31:37.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,该死 凯莉！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.71,1:31:39.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这到底发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.45,1:31:41.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你到底做什么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.86,1:31:50.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你杀了我的儿子！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.56,1:31:51.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你去死！
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.63,1:32:29.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起 我是她的律师
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.18,1:32:32.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我要求她被问讯时 我能在场
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.22,1:32:33.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是你的律师？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.68,1:32:35.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 长官
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.15,1:32:40.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我希望能够保释她 由我来监管
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.16,1:32:41.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不能这样做
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.39,1:32:43.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不知道你是哪种律师
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.36,1:32:44.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不过这是人命官司
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.93,1:32:47.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只有法官才能作出是否保释的决定
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.86,1:32:49.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我会进监狱吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.47,1:32:52.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你们能给她安排个单间吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.07,1:32:54.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我说 小子 我又不是监狱长
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.37,1:32:56.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你知道该怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.41,1:32:58.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,去和监狱长谈谈？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.61,1:33:00.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们可喜欢律师了 是不？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.05,1:33:03.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.45,1:33:05.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要是你的律师管用的话
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.40,1:33:06.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,明天你就能离开这里
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.90,1:33:09.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只要你交了保释金
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.65,1:33:12.96,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.21,1:33:18.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 你们只有5分钟 - 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.22,1:33:27.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们从窗口那里看着我们
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.91,1:33:31.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而且这个房间可能安了窃听器
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.48,1:33:33.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所以你说话要小心
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.91,1:33:35.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,一般杀人罪 是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.81,1:33:38.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就是说非故意杀人
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.75,1:33:40.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我还能活多久？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.68,1:33:42.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 不 你得先被定罪才可能判刑
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.29,1:33:44.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而我不会让你定罪的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.60,1:33:47.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不可能定罪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.97,1:33:53.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,夫人 请把双手交叉在身后放好
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.64,1:34:01.67,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这边走 夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.55,1:34:10.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,拉佛金先生
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.51,1:34:13.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是巨大福利保险公司理赔部的副总经理 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.48,1:34:14.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.59,1:34:15.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我请求询问证人 法官大人？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.82,1:34:17.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.01,1:34:20.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你认得这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.49,1:34:22.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.42,1:34:27.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,读过陪审团听
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.60,1:34:30.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,亲爱的布莱克夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.77,1:34:32.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,本公司已经7次
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.17,1:34:34.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,以书面方式拒绝了你的赔付要求
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.10,1:34:35.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是第八次拒绝 也是最后一次
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.81,1:34:37.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你实在是蠢 蠢 蠢！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.94,1:34:39.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,诚挚的 埃佛莱特拉佛金
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.68,1:34:41.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,索赔部 副总经理
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.56,1:34:42.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是你写的？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.63,1:34:44.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.48,1:34:49.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你打算作何解释？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.36,1:34:56.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当时我个人遇到了很多困难
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.06,1:34:59.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我有很多压力
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.66,1:35:03.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们已经7次拒赔了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.42,1:35:05.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我只是想强调一下
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.89,1:35:07.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我有点用词不当
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.55,1:35:09.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我很后悔写了这封信
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.16,1:35:11.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我愿意道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.00,1:35:14.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你不觉得现在道歉太晚了点吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.98,1:35:17.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也许
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.78,1:35:18.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也许？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.82,1:35:20.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那个孩子已经死了 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.22,1:35:25.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.89,1:35:28.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么 拉佛金先生
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.88,1:35:31.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,杰琪莱曼切克 是谁？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.24,1:35:37.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,杰琪莱曼切克 曾经是理赔审核员
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.22,1:35:39.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她在你的部门工作？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.25,1:35:40.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.91,1:35:43.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她什么时候离开公司的？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.94,1:35:46.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,确切日期我记不得了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.16,1:35:48.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是不是10月30日？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.16,1:35:49.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好像差不多
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.70,1:35:51.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那就是在她将要为此案
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.02,1:35:53.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,出庭作证的两天前？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.95,1:35:55.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我真的记不得了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.71,1:35:58.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我希望能让证人恢复一下记忆
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.35,1:36:01.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也即根据第612条法令
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.69,1:36:05.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是10月30日
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.13,1:36:06.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很明显是的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.33,1:36:07.50,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而这正是她将为此案出庭的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.56,1:36:09.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,两天前？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.54,1:36:09.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.00,1:36:11.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而正是她
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.82,1:36:13.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,处理丹尼雷的理赔申请
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.39,1:36:14.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.40,1:36:16.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.22,1:36:17.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你把她辞了？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.56,1:36:21.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然不是我
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.51,1:36:24.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么 你怎么把她赶走的？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.16,1:36:25.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她是自己提出辞职的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.33,1:36:27.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就在你给我的信中就能看到
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.87,1:36:29.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 那么她干嘛要辞职？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.99,1:36:33.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我在此 因个人原因辞职
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.72,1:36:35.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所以是她自愿
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.22,1:36:36.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,放弃工作的？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.08,1:36:38.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她就是那么写的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.46,1:36:40.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我问完了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.62,1:36:42.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你可以退席了 先生
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.49,1:36:50.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.57,1:36:55.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨 我是杰琪莱曼切克的兄弟 我叫詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.48,1:36:56.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我能看看她吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.98,1:36:58.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 詹姆斯莱曼切克？- 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.48,1:37:01.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.82,1:37:21.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,全体起立
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.51,1:37:26.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请让我解释一下 莱曼切克小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.99,1:37:28.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,其实我不是你的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.05,1:37:35.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.72,1:37:38.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,来见见 杰琪莱曼切克
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.05,1:37:48.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是 杰琪莱曼切克
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.95,1:37:52.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是卡尔 他一定要跟着她
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.99,1:37:55.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是我的合伙人
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.69,1:37:57.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪 S 贝勒
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.52,1:37:59.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请把你告诉过我的 再和他说一遍
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.83,1:38:01.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,莱曼切克小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.93,1:38:03.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.51,1:38:05.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我可以坐下吗
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.90,1:38:07.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.88,1:38:09.67,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很好 莱曼切克小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.97,1:38:12.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想和你谈谈 布莱克的理赔申请
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.57,1:38:13.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那是由你处理的？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.94,1:38:15.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.88,1:38:19.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,布莱克夫人的申请 最开始是由我处理的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.37,1:38:21.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,根据公司当时的规定
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.30,1:38:23.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我给她发了一封拒赔信
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.77,1:38:25.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.65,1:38:27.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.87,1:38:31.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为所有的索赔请求 一开始都是拒绝的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.81,1:38:36.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所有的索赔请求？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.38,1:38:38.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所有的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.35,1:38:46.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,听着 他们是这么干的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.02,1:38:48.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,保单
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.73,1:38:52.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是挨家挨户在穷人区兜售的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.00,1:38:55.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,每周用现金结款
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.25,1:39:02.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如果有理赔申请 就交给某个业务员处理
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.22,1:39:05.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所谓的处理 其实就是低级的打字
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.77,1:39:09.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不管是什么申请 业务员看过申请后
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.30,1:39:14.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就马上给投保人回信
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.13,1:39:15.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,拒绝赔付
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.30,1:39:17.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,然后理赔部会把档案发给保险部
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.11,1:39:22.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,保险部会给理赔部复函
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.61,1:39:25.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,注明 未经保险部同意 不得赔付
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.81,1:39:28.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对了 你要记住
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.28,1:39:31.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,虽然这些人都是为这个大公司干活
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.18,1:39:32.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,即使他们都在同一大楼里工作
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.49,1:39:33.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们却互不相识
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.82,1:39:36.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也不知道彼此的部门打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.66,1:39:37.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这些都是有意如此的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.82,1:39:40.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,部门之间互相敌视 互不关心
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.09,1:39:42.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,同时
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.26,1:39:45.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,保险的客户们
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.50,1:39:49.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不停的接到这种拒付信
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.54,1:39:53.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有些来自理赔部 有些来自保险部
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.34,1:39:56.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,大多数人就此放弃了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.21,1:40:01.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而这些 当然
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.98,1:40:03.78,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也是经过精心设计的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.18,1:40:17.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你的下一个证人 贝勒先生
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.98,1:40:21.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,原告方传召 杰琪莱曼切克
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.71,1:40:23.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他说什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.67,1:40:29.78,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对 法官大人！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.94,1:40:30.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我可以过来和您说话吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.88,1:40:32.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.56,1:40:34.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是突然袭击 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.51,1:40:36.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,为什么？她是可传召的证人之一啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.32,1:40:37.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但我们应该提前得到通知的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.77,1:40:38.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你什么时候找到她的？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.91,1:40:39.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我从来不知道她失踪了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.17,1:40:41.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你得回答这个问题 贝勒先生
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.01,1:40:44.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是我第一个案子
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.07,1:40:45.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.77,1:40:47.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这事关公平 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.69,1:40:49.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们应该事前知道你要传召的证人
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.00,1:40:51.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我同意
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.36,1:40:52.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是说 她不能出庭作证？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.08,1:40:55.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在预审名单中有她的名字 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.60,1:40:58.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,根据第26条法律第6款
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.40,1:41:00.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们有权传召她为证人
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.14,1:41:04.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对无效
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.17,1:41:11.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,去背一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.26,1:41:25.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请告诉法庭你的姓名 以便记录
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.37,1:41:28.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,杰琪 莱曼切克
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.00,1:41:29.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,莱曼切克小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.04,1:41:31.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你为巨大福利保险公司工作了多久？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.01,1:41:33.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,6年
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.81,1:41:35.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,什么时候结束的？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.61,1:41:37.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,10月30日
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.71,1:41:38.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你为什么不干了？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.98,1:41:40.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.37,1:41:43.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是说你不是辞职的？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.18,1:41:44.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 我是被辞退的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.74,1:41:47.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我可以上前询问证人吗 法官大人？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.15,1:41:49.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要求批准
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.16,1:41:50.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我有些疑惑啊 莱曼切克小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.59,1:41:51.59,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我这里有封信
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.66,1:41:54.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,上面说 你因为私人原因辞职的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.63,1:41:55.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.40,1:42:00.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是被辞退的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.22,1:42:01.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这样公司就可以说我不在那里干了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.94,1:42:03.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你可以向法庭指出
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.87,1:42:05.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是谁让你写了这封信的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.60,1:42:14.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,杰克安德霍尔
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.60,1:42:20.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他告诉我我必须马上离开
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.67,1:42:22.67,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当时我有两个选择
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.74,1:42:25.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我可以说这是开除 而我就一无所获
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.31,1:42:27.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不然我就可以写那封信
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.34,1:42:28.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,说这是辞职
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.91,1:42:32.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而公司会给我1万美元现金
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.25,1:42:34.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让我保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.15,1:42:38.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而且我当时 必须马上在他面前做出选择
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.69,1:42:44.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请继续
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.20,1:42:47.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我拿了钱
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.63,1:42:52.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而且我还签了一份保证书
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.53,1:42:54.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,保证不和任何人谈论我经手的理赔申请
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.02,1:42:56.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,包括布莱克家的理赔申请么？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.75,1:42:58.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,特别是布莱克的申请
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.49,1:43:02.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那你知道那个申请应该得到赔付？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.78,1:43:05.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谁都知道
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.68,1:43:08.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但公司玩的是赌赔率
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.65,1:43:11.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,赌什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.54,1:43:15.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,赌投保人不会去请律师
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.33,1:43:26.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就是说 在那段时间内
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.67,1:43:31.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是高级理赔审核员么？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.11,1:43:33.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.38,1:43:35.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么在那段期间 你有没有
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.78,1:43:36.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,得到任何指示
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.98,1:43:38.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,告诉你该如何处理这些申请？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.50,1:43:41.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,一年之内拒绝一切赔付
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.44,1:43:43.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,把省下来的钱加起来
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.05,1:43:46.09,中文简体,,0,0,0,,扣除庭外和解所需的开销
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.44,1:43:47.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,还会剩下一大笔
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.62,1:43:49.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请允许我接近书记员 法官大人？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.04,1:43:50.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.51,1:43:51.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.48,1:43:53.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请给我第6号证物
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.35,1:43:56.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是被标记为
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.22,1:43:58.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,第6号证物的文件
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.99,1:44:00.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你认得它吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.69,1:44:03.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 这是巨大福利保险公司的理赔手册
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.24,1:44:06.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请你帮我个忙
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.97,1:44:08.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,翻到第U项吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.83,1:44:16.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这里没有第U项
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.70,1:44:18.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是你在做高级理赔审核员的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.40,1:44:20.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你记得那里有第U项？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.37,1:44:22.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 我记得
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.24,1:44:26.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,第U项是附加条款
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.15,1:44:28.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,位于高级审核员的工作手册中
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.75,1:44:29.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.38,1:44:31.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.32,1:44:35.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是杰琪莱曼切克真正的高级理赔手册
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.82,1:44:37.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这里面有一项附加条款
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.62,1:44:38.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,被列为第U项
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.99,1:44:39.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我请求上前询问
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.06,1:44:41.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对 法官大人 我们可以过来说话吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.40,1:44:47.10,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人 我们得到的文件不全
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.17,1:44:48.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人 这份文件中的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.47,1:44:50.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,附加条款部分是非法窃取的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.67,1:44:52.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不能作为证据
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.07,1:44:52.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不能作为证据？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.82,1:44:54.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,立奥 你能够证明吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.09,1:44:56.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人 我请求你禁止他宣读该材料
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.56,1:44:59.78,中文简体,,0,0,0,,并且不要使用任何存在嫌疑的证据
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.85,1:45:03.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不理解这为什么不能作为证据
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.45,1:45:05.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,它不是在正确的时间内获得的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.15,1:45:06.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们不知道他怎么得到它的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.35,1:45:08.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我昨天晚上才知道 存在这个东西
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.25,1:45:10.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,假设我现在不接受这项证物
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.24,1:45:12.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你还有其他问题要问证人吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.88,1:45:13.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没了 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.48,1:45:16.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你现在可以询问了 德拉门德先生
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.71,1:45:17.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.25,1:45:34.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,莱曼切克小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.80,1:45:38.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请问你最近是否
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.50,1:45:40.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,入院治疗很多疾病？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.06,1:45:42.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我没有入院
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.28,1:45:46.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我只是喝了很多酒 精神压抑
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.44,1:45:49.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我是自愿去医院检查的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.04,1:45:53.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我本应享受巨大福利保险公司的集体保险
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.62,1:45:56.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,当然 现在他们拒赔了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.10,1:45:57.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这大概就是你来这里的原因吧？莱曼切克小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.31,1:46:00.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为你很气愤巨大福利保险公司？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.47,1:46:01.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,莱曼切克小姐？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.64,1:46:03.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我恨这个保险公司
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.18,1:46:06.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我也恨大多数在那工作的蛀虫
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.60,1:46:09.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那你和拉佛金先生上床的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.32,1:46:10.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是不是觉得他也是蛀虫之一？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.92,1:46:13.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.09,1:46:15.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.36,1:46:17.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,德拉门德先生可能对这个很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.69,1:46:19.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但这个与本案无关
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.96,1:46:21.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 我可不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.48,1:46:23.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对无效
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.55,1:46:24.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让我们看看究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.77,1:46:28.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是否承认和拉佛金先生有特殊关系？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.55,1:46:36.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,莱曼切克小姐？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.11,1:46:47.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只要我和公司的高层保持性关系
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.02,1:46:53.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的工资就会增加 就会得到提拔
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.11,1:46:57.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,否则 我就会被降职
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.64,1:46:58.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,莱曼切克小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.98,1:47:00.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,作为巨大福利保险公司的雇员
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.88,1:47:02.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你承诺过不会泄露
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.79,1:47:05.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,属于机密的理赔信息
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.19,1:47:06.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 是不是？- 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.06,1:47:10.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,事实上 你说过要保守秘密
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.94,1:47:13.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,并索要1万美元作为报酬 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.01,1:47:16.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那笔钱不是我要求的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.31,1:47:17.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是你接受了 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.58,1:47:19.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你收了钱
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.95,1:47:21.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可你心里
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.11,1:47:23.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,却丝毫没有要保守这些秘密的意思
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.28,1:47:25.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,事实上 你对巨大福利保险公司
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.04,1:47:28.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,和拉佛金先生切齿痛恨 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.26,1:47:30.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你知道 他们在欺负我
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.48,1:47:34.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为我穷 单身一人带着2个孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.22,1:47:35.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而你告诉他 你打算去见他的妻子
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.91,1:47:36.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要在报纸上公开这事
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.93,1:47:40.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而那一万美元就是勒索 对不对？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.32,1:47:43.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只是你向你痛恨的公司 敲诈的钱财！
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.38,1:47:44.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.58,1:47:45.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.46,1:47:48.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,事实上 你今天的作证完全是一场谎言
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.11,1:47:49.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你偷窃了公司的文件
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.91,1:47:53.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,还有机密材料 藉以进行敲诈
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.64,1:47:57.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,恶魔也不过如此吧 莱曼切克小姐？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.59,1:48:00.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,真是个卑鄙的女人！
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.13,1:48:03.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我法官大人 我要求将所有这些
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.83,1:48:07.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,莱曼切克小姐提供给控方的文件
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.33,1:48:08.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,都作为窃取的文件
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.00,1:48:10.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,禁止列为证物
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.42,1:48:22.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,根据法庭所看到的事实
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.68,1:48:25.46,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这些文件不予接受
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.19,1:48:31.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我没有问题了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.79,1:48:33.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 德拉门德先生
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.46,1:48:35.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,贝勒先生
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.53,1:48:39.70,中文简体,,0,0,0,,莱曼切克小姐 你可以下来了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.22,1:48:48.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.16,1:49:07.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 你好 - 这是迭克席夫列特
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.60,1:49:09.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我要找大个儿雷诺 你能帮我接一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.37,1:49:11.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,大个儿雷诺？稍等
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.23,1:49:12.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.30,1:49:18.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.44,1:49:19.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嘿 老板 我是迭克
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.05,1:49:21.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗨 迭克 你怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.71,1:49:22.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,很好 你呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.67,1:49:23.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 我也很好
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.81,1:49:24.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你还在吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.61,1:49:27.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我无处不在
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.15,1:49:29.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,啊 对
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.31,1:49:33.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,听着 我有个案子 证据是窃取的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.55,1:49:36.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,窃取的证据
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.76,1:49:38.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,让我想想看 呃
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.56,1:49:40.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你查一下德索托的案子
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.06,1:49:42.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,德索托？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.09,1:49:45.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,卡尔曼德索托 记得他吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.60,1:49:46.50,中文简体,,0,0,0,,红宝石俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.57,1:49:47.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.00,1:49:49.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我在哪能找到这案子？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.00,1:49:53.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,呃 大概在92年那卷
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.51,1:49:55.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想想看 好像是650
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.97,1:49:57.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,西南第二上诉庭
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.41,1:49:58.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,老板 你真救了我的命了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.88,1:49:59.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,92年？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.88,1:50:01.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 红宝石俱乐部的案子
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.58,1:50:03.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,92年
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.48,1:50:04.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,卡尔曼德索托
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.58,1:50:05.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,卡尔曼德索托
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.72,1:50:06.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,红宝石俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.72,1:50:07.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,红宝石俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.69,1:50:08.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那是上诉法庭的案子
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.02,1:50:10.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对 对 我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.34,1:50:16.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.38,1:50:18.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,从布鲁泽那里弄来的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.51,1:50:20.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,布鲁泽？我还以为你不知道布鲁泽在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.52,1:50:23.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我 我是不知道 但是我有个紧急联络号码
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.55,1:50:25.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我给他们打了个电话 他们给我接通了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.79,1:50:26.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.06,1:50:29.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,布鲁泽最清楚窃取证据的事情了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.36,1:50:31.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这算他的看家本领了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.88,1:50:34.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 喂？- 鲁迪贝勒先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.62,1:50:36.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 是我 - 我是谢尔比郡地区检察官
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.63,1:50:38.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你今晚能来下我们法庭吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.13,1:50:39.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想和你谈谈凯莉莱克的案子
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.95,1:50:41.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 当然 - 到6号房间来
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.54,1:50:47.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们有办法对付这群混蛋啦
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.28,1:50:50.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在卡尔曼德索托 起诉红宝石俱乐部的案子里
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.31,1:50:52.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有好多的窃取而来的证据
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.31,1:50:54.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,布鲁泽自己搞的这个案子
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.38,1:50:56.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,现在不行 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.92,1:50:58.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你要走？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.22,1:51:00.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,巨大福利公司的首席执行官明天就要来了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.72,1:51:04.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我说 我们得给他好看的
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.64,1:51:17.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,祝你好运 凯莉
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.21,1:51:18.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.21,1:51:25.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我和地区检察官谈过了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.18,1:51:27.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她不打算起诉
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.15,1:51:29.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,她认为你没有罪
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.32,1:51:32.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这只是自卫 凯莉
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.11,1:51:48.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,控方打算传召维尔佛莱德奇利上庭作证
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.19,1:51:50.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请举起你的右手
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.91,1:51:52.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你愿意庄严宣誓
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.88,1:51:54.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你在此所作证供
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.11,1:51:55.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,全是事实
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.54,1:51:57.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,并无丝毫虚言吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.51,1:51:58.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.22,1:51:59.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你可以作证了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.46,1:52:04.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请告诉法庭你的名字 以便记录
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.99,1:52:06.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,维尔佛莱德奇利
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.26,1:52:08.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我可以上前询问证人吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.19,1:52:09.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.69,1:52:13.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,奇利先生 呃 在这个巨大福利公司的册子里面
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.10,1:52:14.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这个是不是你？这是你的名字吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.96,1:52:15.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.97,1:52:18.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那这些缩写指什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.33,1:52:19.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是说CEO？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.80,1:52:22.74,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 它们指什么 CEO 指什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.80,1:52:24.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,首席执行官
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.31,1:52:27.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,首席执行官 谢谢你 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.33,1:52:29.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就是说 你是你是头儿了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.51,1:52:32.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你是主要人物 你说了算
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.31,1:52:33.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,权力由你掌控
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.31,1:52:35.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 你可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.95,1:52:37.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是吗 好 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.37,1:52:40.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,呃 法官大人 我希望把询问奇利先生的权利
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.44,1:52:43.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,交给我的合伙人鲁迪贝勒
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.56,1:52:46.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.21,1:52:47.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你还没有执照呢
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.38,1:52:49.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我有的选吗 你干嘛去了？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.38,1:52:50.78,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你迟到了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.11,1:52:52.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,早上好 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.22,1:52:54.19,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.20,1:52:56.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请求上前询问证人 法官大人？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.67,1:52:58.36,中文简体,,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.93,1:53:02.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是杰琪莱曼切克给我的理赔手册
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.40,1:53:03.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.51,1:53:04.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,窃取的文件不足为凭
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.02,1:53:05.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,您已经说过了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.91,1:53:06.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对有效
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.93,1:53:08.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们可以上前说话吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.64,1:53:14.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想这个问题已经裁定了 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.93,1:53:18.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人 我刚找到了一个
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.38,1:53:19.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,类似案例
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.78,1:53:21.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.21,1:53:23.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如果你看看这个判决
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.78,1:53:26.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是关于卡尔曼德索托和红宝石俱乐部的案子
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.42,1:53:28.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我给您和德拉门德先生都复印了一份
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.89,1:53:31.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,585号案 西南部第二上诉法庭 第431页
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.92,1:53:34.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,由布鲁泽 不 由小莱曼斯通事务所辩护
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.76,1:53:36.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这里面清楚地表明
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.26,1:53:38.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,窃取而得的文件 事实上 是可以接受的
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.44,1:53:40.87,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只要该文件并非由律师窃取的即可
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.68,1:53:43.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嗯 根据这个案例
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.00,1:53:45.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你的反对无效
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.80,1:53:47.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起 立奥
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.72,1:53:50.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好吧 我想你是对的 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.76,1:53:52.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但请记录下来我对此强烈反对
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.56,1:53:53.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你的反对已经被记录了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.71,1:53:55.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我可以上前询问了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.75,1:53:57.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.92,1:54:00.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,呃 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.50,1:54:03.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人 我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.57,1:54:07.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起 让您久等了 奇利先生
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.33,1:54:08.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们得谈谈这个
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.62,1:54:10.36,中文简体,,0,0,0,,巨大福利保险公司的理赔手册
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.66,1:54:14.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是一份完整的手册吗 先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.47,1:54:17.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.67,1:54:19.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,其中有第U项吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.21,1:54:27.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.91,1:54:29.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那我们谈谈这个神秘的第U项 好不好
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.02,1:54:31.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你干嘛不向陪审团解释一下呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.05,1:54:33.92,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们来看一看
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.02,1:54:36.99,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请读出第三段
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.08,1:54:44.36,中文简体,,0,0,0,,理赔审核员应该在接到任何申请三日内
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.43,1:54:48.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,毫无例外地 拒绝赔付
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.62,1:54:51.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你怎么解释这第U项？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.51,1:54:54.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 我们有时会收到一些
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.51,1:54:57.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,无意义和虚假的索赔
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.31,1:55:00.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有时 我们用这一方法
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.55,1:55:02.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,使我们可以更关注那些
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.88,1:55:05.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,合法和必需的赔付
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.55,1:55:09.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,奇利先生 你真的认为本法庭
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.29,1:55:11.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,会相信你这个解释吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.39,1:55:12.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这一段不过是段
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.88,1:55:15.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,内部处理指示而已
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.88,1:55:17.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,内部处理指示？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.41,1:55:19.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不 奇利先生 事实并非如此
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.72,1:55:21.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,第U项所作的远不只如此而已
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.55,1:55:23.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,孩子 我可不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.39,1:55:25.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,奇利先生 这里面是不是很明确的指出了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.95,1:55:28.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,申请应该怎么被传递 推诿 再传递
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.54,1:55:30.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,用尽各种方法 就是为了拒绝赔付？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.57,1:55:31.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我没看到
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.77,1:55:32.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人 请求上前询问证人？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.90,1:55:34.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.42,1:55:40.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那么 奇利先生
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.88,1:55:47.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在1995年 巨大福利公司有多少份保单生效？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.63,1:55:53.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.97,1:55:55.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们来看看怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.68,1:56:01.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,9万8千份 这个数字是否正确？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.99,1:56:04.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.59,1:56:06.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可能就是这么多 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.46,1:56:07.63,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.70,1:56:11.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,好 那么在这些保单中 有多少人提出了索赔？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.14,1:56:15.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这个 这我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.31,1:56:18.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,1万1千4 对不对
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.37,1:56:21.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,多还是少了？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.42,1:56:22.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可能对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.73,1:56:26.75,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是 我得确认一下才行
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.82,1:56:28.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 我懂了 就是说我要的信息
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.66,1:56:29.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,都在那本书里了？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.48,1:56:31.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.37,1:56:32.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,那你可不可以告诉陪审团
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.22,1:56:34.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在这1万1千多份索赔申请中
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.80,1:56:36.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有多少份被拒绝了？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.63,1:56:41.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我可能找不到 这需要更多时间
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.22,1:56:43.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,奇利先生 你已经找了两个月了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.77,1:56:45.67,中文简体,,0,0,0,,现在回答这个问题！
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.22,1:56:52.04,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这个 我
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.97,1:56:54.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我觉得
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.95,1:57:02.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,9141件
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.09,1:57:07.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,11462份理赔申请
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.01,1:57:12.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,9141份被拒赔
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.76,1:57:16.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.37,1:57:19.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我还有一份文件
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.37,1:57:20.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是巨大福利保险公司医学委员会
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.70,1:57:23.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,提供的一份报告
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.00,1:57:28.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,依照先例 请求将此文件
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.66,1:57:29.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,呈送给奇利先生
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.08,1:57:31.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对 同样的理由 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.51,1:57:35.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对无效 不过记录下这一反对
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.33,1:57:36.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.73,1:57:46.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,呃 奇利先生 这是巨大福利保险公司
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.08,1:57:47.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,自己的医学委员会写的报告
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.63,1:57:49.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而你是这个委员会的主席
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.91,1:57:54.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请你从第18行读起好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.11,1:58:00.83,中文简体,,0,0,0,,由于骨髓移植
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.89,1:58:03.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,已经成为标准治疗方式
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.50,1:58:06.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,巨大福利公司投资骨髓临床治疗的决定
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.80,1:58:09.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,将是有利可图的
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.04,1:58:12.30,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请求上前询问证人 法官大人？
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.06,1:58:14.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.64,1:58:15.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.91,1:58:19.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:19.77,1:58:20.97,中文简体,,0,0,0,,再读大声一点
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.02,1:58:23.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对 法官大人 无意义重复
Dialogue: 0,1:58:23.22,1:58:24.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,反对无效
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.60,1:58:27.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我希望陪审团成员都能听到这些
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.48,1:58:31.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,由于骨髓移植
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.91,1:58:34.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,已经成为标准治疗方式
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.44,1:58:37.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,巨大福利公司投资骨髓临床治疗的决定
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.18,1:58:40.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,将是有利可图的
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.48,1:58:41.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,有利可图
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.87,1:58:45.37,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这就是巨大福利公司的真相 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.54,1:58:47.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我问完了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.93,1:58:50.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,德拉门德先生
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.68,1:58:53.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没有问题 但是我们坚持反对意见
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.71,1:58:56.00,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你可以下去了 奇利先生
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.35,1:58:58.23,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.24,1:59:18.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.62,1:59:20.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,快点 起床了 快点 到时间了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.84,1:59:22.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,快点 快点
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.64,1:59:28.48,中文简体,,0,0,0,,赔付1000万美元意味着什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.87,1:59:34.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所有的保险公司都会提高售保门槛
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.34,1:59:36.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这将造成
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.30,1:59:40.01,中文简体,,0,0,0,,政府垄断医疗保险的局面
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.31,1:59:43.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,陪审团成员们 你们的职责重大
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.60,1:59:47.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要明智
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.65,1:59:49.52,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要谨慎
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.59,1:59:51.06,中文简体,,0,0,0,,要公正
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.93,1:59:56.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,公正地作出判决
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.14,1:59:59.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.96,2:00:04.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,贝勒先生 你可以作结案陈词了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.87,2:00:06.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.32,2:00:09.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,陪审团的女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,2:00:12.72,2:00:15.43,中文简体,,0,0,0,,每当我想起丹尼雷布莱克
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.40,2:00:20.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,呼出最后一口气 慢慢死去的时候
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.47,2:00:24.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我就痛恨自己
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.26,2:00:27.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我学了这么多法律
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.82,2:00:29.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但却无法挽救他
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.46,2:00:33.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我觉得我是个不称职的律师
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.82,2:00:35.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我没有资格作这个结案陈词
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.58,2:00:42.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所以 我希望由丹尼雷来做
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.22,2:00:45.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请展示16号证物
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.56,2:00:52.88,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我现在体重110磅
Dialogue: 0,2:00:53.60,2:00:57.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而11个月前 我还重160磅
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.32,2:01:03.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我的白血病确诊很久了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.77,2:01:07.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我在医院治疗的时候
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.93,2:01:09.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,医生发现
Dialogue: 0,2:01:09.26,2:01:11.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,唯一可以挽救我的生命的
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.28,2:01:13.67,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就是骨髓移植
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.35,2:01:20.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,可我只能出院
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.24,2:01:23.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,因为我家无力承担
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.26,2:01:26.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 这笔费用 - 为什么
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.53,2:01:33.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,- 巨大福利保险公司拒绝了我们的理赔请求 - 过来吧
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.17,2:01:35.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.39,2:01:40.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如果我能接受骨髓移植
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.05,2:01:44.21,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我有90％的机会存活下来
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.65,2:01:52.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我希望你们和我一样感到震惊
Dialogue: 0,2:01:52.88,2:01:55.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在被告这样一家财力雄厚的大公司
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.19,2:01:56.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,的长期运作中
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.33,2:01:58.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们一直从低收入家庭中吸金
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.86,2:02:01.82,中文简体,,0,0,0,,通过拒赔合理的赔付请求 把钱据为己有
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.67,2:02:06.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,难怪他们请得起那么贵的律师
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.04,2:02:09.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,花重金游说和公关
Dialogue: 0,2:02:09.84,2:02:12.78,中文简体,,0,0,0,,来让我们相信 法律需要改革
Dialogue: 0,2:02:12.84,2:02:15.42,中文简体,,0,0,0,,需要停止惩罚性的赔偿
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.04,2:02:27.31,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在此 我恳求陪审团
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.23,2:02:29.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,作出
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.00,2:02:35.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你们内心深处 认为正确的决定
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.23,2:02:39.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如果你们不对巨大福利保险公司作出惩罚
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.77,2:02:43.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你们可能就是下一个受害者
Dialogue: 0,2:02:47.51,2:02:49.05,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我说完了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.10,2:03:10.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,别紧张
Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.79,2:03:33.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,陪审团有结论了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.86,2:03:35.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的 我们已经作出结论了 法官大人
Dialogue: 0,2:03:35.68,2:03:37.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你们已经按我的要求 写在纸上了么？
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.48,2:03:39.65,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,2:03:39.71,2:03:41.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,请读出你们的结论
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.95,2:03:47.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们陪审团 认为原告方
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.29,2:03:49.79,中文简体,,0,0,0,,应被赔偿 实际损失
Dialogue: 0,2:03:49.86,2:03:53.96,中文简体,,0,0,0,,15万美元
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.30,2:04:02.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,并且 我们陪审团 认为被告方
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.69,2:04:05.16,中文简体,,0,0,0,,应付与原告 惩罚性赔偿
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.22,2:04:09.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,5000万美元
Dialogue: 0,2:04:24.94,2:04:26.81,中文简体,,0,0,0,,全体起立
Dialogue: 0,2:04:28.05,2:04:29.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这些人试图隐瞒事实
Dialogue: 0,2:04:29.61,2:04:32.28,中文简体,,0,0,0,,逃避责任
Dialogue: 0,2:04:32.35,2:04:33.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,最后他们都被抓到了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:33.62,2:04:35.25,中文简体,,0,0,0,,更引人注目的是
Dialogue: 0,2:04:35.32,2:04:37.54,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这个案子的主律师 鲁迪贝勒
Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.61,2:04:39.24,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这是他主打的第一场案子
Dialogue: 0,2:04:39.31,2:04:40.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不管从什么人的观点来看
Dialogue: 0,2:04:40.68,2:04:42.61,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这都是个惊人的判决
Dialogue: 0,2:04:42.68,2:04:44.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这肯定是金额最高的
Dialogue: 0,2:04:44.15,2:04:46.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,呵呵 我的小帮工干的不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:04:46.58,2:04:48.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,其实 这没什么难的
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.45,2:04:50.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们只是有个很好的陪审团
Dialogue: 0,2:04:50.62,2:04:52.69,中文简体,,0,0,0,,然后事实纷纷出现
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.75,2:04:54.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,5000万美元的惩罚性赔偿
Dialogue: 0,2:04:54.36,2:04:55.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,5000万美元？
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.69,2:04:56.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,2:04:56.73,2:04:58.29,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你能挣多少？
Dialogue: 0,2:04:58.36,2:05:00.39,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你快抓住重点了 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:05:00.46,2:05:01.96,中文简体,,0,0,0,,对不起 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.03,2:05:02.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我知道你不是这个意思的
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.88,2:05:06.35,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们能拿三分之一 不过钱还没有到帐
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.07,2:05:09.50,中文简体,,0,0,0,,待会见
Dialogue: 0,2:05:09.57,2:05:11.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你就把这女孩这么一个人扔在这？
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.57,2:05:13.14,中文简体,,0,0,0,,不会很久的
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.61,2:05:17.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,2:05:17.41,2:05:20.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我打算把你列入我的遗产名单
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.78,2:05:22.02,中文简体,,0,0,0,,真的？你真是
Dialogue: 0,2:05:22.44,2:05:24.66,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你真是对我太好了 伯迪夫人
Dialogue: 0,2:05:29.17,2:05:30.94,中文简体,,0,0,0,,热点新闻
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.01,2:05:35.58,中文简体,,0,0,0,,维尔佛莱德奇利先生 巨大福利公司首席执行官
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.65,2:05:38.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,昨天下午在肯尼迪国际机场被捕
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.18,2:05:41.18,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他当时正登上一架去伦敦的飞机
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.25,2:05:43.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,和她夫人一起
Dialogue: 0,2:05:43.20,2:05:45.56,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们说是去度假
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.62,2:05:47.76,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是他们却无法说出
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.99,2:05:50.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,他们打算去的欧洲旅店的名字
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.33,2:05:53.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,今天下午5时 巨大福利保险公司
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.10,2:05:55.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,依据破产法
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.10,2:05:56.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,在克立夫兰联邦法庭提出破产保护
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.67,2:05:59.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,多个州政府正在调查巨大福利 公司
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.47,2:06:01.89,中文简体,,0,0,0,,还有很多连锁赔偿案已经被提起诉讼
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.20,2:06:06.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,2:06:06.51,2:06:08.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,鲁迪 我是立奥德拉门德
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.98,2:06:12.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,看来整个公司已经被洗劫一空了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:13.59,2:06:15.55,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,2:06:16.13,2:06:18.26,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我希望你能拿到你的那份
Dialogue: 0,2:06:18.96,2:06:21.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这场官司没人赚到便宜
Dialogue: 0,2:06:21.94,2:06:24.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我想让你知道
Dialogue: 0,2:06:25.25,2:06:27.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 德拉门德先生
Dialogue: 0,2:06:28.32,2:06:30.53,中文简体,,0,0,0,,巨大福利公司就像是个坏了的赌博机
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.60,2:06:32.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,从不吐钱
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.20,2:06:35.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们要是拿那17万5就好啦
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.91,2:06:37.77,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们到底在想什么？
Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.38,2:06:44.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这事简直乱套了 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.45,2:06:46.40,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这种法律
Dialogue: 0,2:06:47.39,2:06:48.44,中文简体,,0,0,0,,美国的每个律师 现在都在谈论我
Dialogue: 0,2:06:50.91,2:06:52.17,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但这些却没有让我觉得
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.24,2:06:54.22,中文简体,,0,0,0,,自己已经是法律事业的一员了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:55.44,2:06:57.34,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如果我全身心的投入工作
Dialogue: 0,2:06:57.41,2:06:59.60,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我可能能继续从事法律工作
Dialogue: 0,2:07:00.04,2:07:01.85,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是这样我没法照顾凯莉
Dialogue: 0,2:07:03.06,2:07:05.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而她现在需要非常多的照顾
Dialogue: 0,2:07:08.48,2:07:11.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,所以尽管我还是热爱法律 我会永远热爱它
Dialogue: 0,2:07:11.33,2:07:12.71,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也许我可以去教法律
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.80,2:07:14.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而不是做律师
Dialogue: 0,2:07:16.51,2:07:18.08,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我需要时间搞定这事
Dialogue: 0,2:07:18.72,2:07:21.32,中文简体,,0,0,0,,巨大福利公司现在一文不名
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.82,2:07:25.91,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这曾经好像天上掉下的馅饼
Dialogue: 0,2:07:25.95,2:07:27.12,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是现在我们一分钱也没捞到
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.62,2:07:29.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,2:07:30.08,2:07:31.68,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你让他们破产了
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.75,2:07:34.72,中文简体,,0,0,0,,田纳西孟菲斯的一个小女人
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.78,2:07:37.95,中文简体,,0,0,0,,就把这群混蛋弄破产了？
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.60,2:07:43.64,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我明天会去丹尼雷的墓前
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.73,2:07:45.20,中文简体,,0,0,0,,告诉他这个事情
Dialogue: 0,2:07:52.00,2:07:54.15,中文简体,,0,0,0,,哦 凯莉和我大概
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.22,2:07:56.57,中文简体,,0,0,0,,明天一早就要走了
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.39,2:08:00.49,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们创造了历史 鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,2:08:01.89,2:08:03.33,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:08:05.93,2:08:07.96,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我们可以吹牛一辈子了
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.97,2:08:11.47,中文简体,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,2:08:12.54,2:08:14.27,中文简体,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问我已经达到了事业的顶峰
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.84,2:08:16.41,中文简体,,0,0,0,,事实上 由于这个案子把我送到顶峰
Dialogue: 0,2:08:16.47,2:08:18.84,中文简体,,0,0,0,,以后怎么走都是下坡路了
Dialogue: 0,2:08:19.34,2:08:20.38,中文简体,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.45,2:08:22.78,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我以后碰到的每一个客户都会期盼
Dialogue: 0,2:08:22.85,2:08:25.98,中文简体,,0,0,0,,这种奇迹 一点都不能少
Dialogue: 0,2:08:26.05,2:08:28.13,中文简体,,0,0,0,,也许我确实做得到
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.55,2:08:30.62,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如果我不择手段
Dialogue: 0,2:08:31.24,2:08:32.51,中文简体,,0,0,0,,但是那样的话 有个早上当我醒来
Dialogue: 0,2:08:32.57,2:08:35.11,中文简体,,0,0,0,,我会发现自己已经变成了立奥德拉门德
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.28,2:08:39.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,嘿 你通过律考以后给我个电话 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:08:41.11,2:08:42.80,中文简体,,0,0,0,,没问题 小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,2:08:45.59,2:08:48.45,中文简体,,0,0,0,,每个律师都至少会在某个案子中
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.52,2:08:51.73,中文简体,,0,0,0,,发现自己越过了 自己不愿越过的界线
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.79,2:08:52.86,中文简体,,0,0,0,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,2:08:52.93,2:08:54.93,中文简体,,0,0,0,,如果你一次又一次地跨越界线
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.00,2:08:57.03,中文简体,,0,0,0,,你会发现界线不存在了
Dialogue: 0,2:08:58.20,2:09:00.90,中文简体,,0,0,0,,而这时的你 什么都不是 只不过是个律师笑话
Dialogue: 0,2:09:00.97,2:09:04.07,中文简体,,0,0,0,,只不过 是脏水中的又一条鲨鱼


